18.18: weig zu'g apg-laa-ham xij penj Lo Eei, henq Eei kua'q. luvb Diaq maang kua'q myenb xij weig ninb tu'q fu'q.
18.8: apg-laa-ham zx'q teij vovb Exb Mei Zauj vovb Exj cvj Zauj liug leid zyavj Eei vovb xq Beng ninb Bua pua taub. Eang uaq zang, ninb kanb c'q, sruq Jyenq Dyavj ka'Diaq, ninb Bua Eei ka'Len.
18.33: zyruq Zauj apg-laa-ham kxvq liud waag, zyrug mivb mig a'q. apg-laa-ham yaag Rwrnj mig a'q.
18.3: ninb kxvq, “yia Eei zyruq aag, sij kxvq ziuj meib pwatg yia hxpg meib Eei Hruq nx, maiq tuvq pcv za'g Eei Jiaj yia, meib Eei pru, Eei kcvb Daavg.
18.32: apg-laa-ham kxvq, “zyruq aa'b! Toq maiq tuvq Qiaj Jiad. pun yia cvj kxvq Du'g Rung Navq. sij kxvq yem uaq pwatg maaib zyepg taub Navq ni?”   zyruq tau, “weig naaiq teij zyepg taub yia yaag maiq myetg.”
18.21: yia xij zu'g Fiag mivb mavg kaaj ninb Bua zruj Eei sig Dovg yia haid koj yia uaq teij waag fai? sij kxvq maiq zeid nx, yia zyrug hiuq a'q.”
18.14: maiq maaib haiq Euvg Dovg haaij a'g  zyruq maiq haib zruj. ta'Eeig Havj Tauj naaiq nxm zyavb hog yia cvj Rwrnj taaib. Tauj uaq zang saa-laa zyrug tu'q taub txn taaib a'q.”
18.23: apg-laa-ham zyrug mivb fatq Eei naaig zyruq, “meib myetg x'q myenb, meib xij lyemb Kuq myenb Zauj Jyenq yetg Fiag myetg fai?
18.6: apg-laa-ham kaanq Jyenq pia'g Dopg liub Buaj saa-laa, “kaanq syepq teij zx'q yetg Tovq Bwrnb mwrng Zaij taaib zruj Fuaq.”
18.2: apg-laa-ham Zau Myen pwatg pua taub mJavg txn sruq Jyenq uaq. ninb yetq pwatg, zyrug yem Dopg liub Tiuj mivb zipq yaag Pua'q Fiag Dau.
18.20: zyruq zyrug kxvq Buaj apg-laa-ham, “maaib koj soj-Dom Zauj ko-mo-laa zivb Eei waag Tauj yia Eei mnxmb Zamq haig a'q. ninb Bua Eei zwid Niaq haig.
18.24: sij kxvq uaq nxm zivb maaib Mmd zyepg taub Kuq myenb ni? meib Zxg xij myetg, maiq weig uaq teij Mmd zyepg taub myenb lyrub uaq nxm zivb?
18.28: sij kxvq maiq kauj Mmd zyepg taub Kuq myenb, Zaa pyaa taub Navq ni? laaij zo'g naaiq teij pyaa taub Kuq myenb meib Zxg myetg naaiq nxm zivb Eei?”   zyruq kxvq, “sij kxvq yem naaig pwatg maaib feij zyepg Mmd taub Kuq myenb, yia maiq myetg naaiq nxm zivb a'q lx'g.”
18.7: kxvq liud, apg-laa-ham Tiuj mivb vovb kwanb uaq, zx'q taub vovb txn lunj Eei, Jung Eei, pun pru. pru zyrug kaanq liug leid.
18.29: apg-laa-ham cvj kxvq Rung, “sij kxvq yem uaq Kuvj maaib feij zyepg taub ni? Navq haiq nx?”   zyruq tau, “weig naaiq teij feij zyepg taub, yia yaag maiq myetg.”
18.19: yia kinq ninb taaib weig pun ninb Faauj ninb Eei fu'Jweiq Zauj ninb Eei hod txig zeib fun, zruj hxpg zruj pcvb fim Eei, zyrug kruj lovj yia Eei tod. Navq naaig, zyruq haib zruj zyavj ziuj ninb lcvd pun apg-laa-ham Eei waag.”
18.17: zyruq yem Hruq Namq. “yia xij zruj Eei sig yia xij zu'g pivj, maiq pun apg-laa-ham hiuq fai?
18.31: apg-laa-ham kxvq, “yia Dovg naaiq puvj laavg Zauj zyruq kxvq. sij kxvq yem naaig Kuvj maaib Eig zyepg taub Navq ni?”   zyruq kxvq, “weig naaiq teij Eig zyepg taub yia yaag maiq myetg uaq nxm zivb a'q.”
18.30: apg-laa-ham kxvq, “zyruq aa'b! maiq tuvq kcvb Qiaj Jiad og. Toq pun yia kxvq. sij kxvq yem uaq Kuvj maaib faab zyepg taub Navq haiq nx?”   zyruq cvj tau, “sij kxvq yem uaq yia pwatg maaib faab zyepg taub yia yaag maiq myetg.”
18.27: apg-laa-ham cvj kxvq, “yia Navq naaiq nx puvj laavg Zauj zyruq kxvq maiq kunq yia se Kuvj penj niab Buv Zauj saaiq Navq.
18.11: apg-laa-ham Bua i Mwavq zuvq koj haig. saa-laa Eei sin yaag Gaai mig a'q.
18.5: yia mivb lxd teij paaq ka'naaiq pun meib Bua Eang, Tevj meib Bua maaib teij Qa'q cvj yavb Jauq mivb. meib Bua Tauj meib Bua Eei pru naaiq taaib a'q.” ninb Bua tau, “lovj a'q. kunq ziuj meib Eei waag zruj.”
18.9: uaq teij myenb naaig apg-laa-ham, “meib Eei auq, saa-laa, yem haaij?” apg-laa-ham tau, “yem uaq, Dopg liub ka'Euad.”
18.16: uaq teij myenb yem naaig Zwrtq Jauq mivb Tauj nxm txvj mavg tu'q pwatg soj-Dom zivb. apg-laa-ham yaag fuvj Jyenq ninb Bua mivb.
18.4: yia zyrug txb teij uam taaib pun meib Bua Raauj zauj, cvj yem naaiq Dyavb kxn hitq tavb Kwrnj.
18.10: uaq teij pua taub myenb maaib taub kxvq, “ta'Eeig Havj Tauj naaiq nxm zyavb hog yia zuvq cvj Rwrnj Tauj naaiq. Tauj uaq zang meib Eei auq, saa-laa, zyrug tu'q taub txn taaib a'q.” saa-laa yem ninb Bua Ga'haaq Gaav Dopg liub kcvb Daavg mwavj.
18.22: uaq teij i taub myenb leib Gxi uaq nxm txvj huvj Jyenq soj-Dom zivb mivb mig a'q. mq paag apg-laa-ham Zxg yem uaq sruq Jyenq zyruq Eei Ra'Myen.
18.12: saa-laa yem Hruq yetg ping Jyetq yetg ping Namq, “yia koj Revg a'q. yia Eei Goj yaag koj haig a'q. yia Zxg cvj haib a'Neiq yia Eei Goj fai?”
18.15: saa-laa kamb Riaj Eei, maiq lcvd ninb Jyetq. ninb kxvq, “yia maiq Jyetq nyaa.”   zyruq kxvq, “meib za'kevb Jyetq Eei.”
18.13: zyruq naaig apg-laa-ham, “saa-laa weig haiq tiug Jyetq yaag kxvq, ‘yia Dovg naaiq koj za'kevb haib maaib kub vwaad Eei nxb?’
18.1: apg-laa-ham yem mam-le Eei tomb Ba'ov zwei Dyavb lomg zweid Jyenq Dopg liub kcvb Daavg luvb Nxi zang kaub yua'q Jiaj Eei zyavb hog, zyruq hing Zwrtq pun ninb pwatg.
18.26: zyruq kxvq, “sij kxvq yia pwatg Mmd zyepg taub Kuq myenb yia zyrug weig naaiq teij Mmd zyepg taub siaj Zwrtq naaiq nxm zivb.”
18.25: zyruq za'kevb maiq haib zx'q Kuq myenb Zauj x'q myenb yetg Fiag taij kwavg saa'b? meib kevb maiq haib zruj pun Kuq myenb Zauj x'q myenb fib Navq Eei. syemq luvb Diaq Eei Jyen xij zruj pcvb fim Eei maiq zeid?”

45.18: pyenb meib Bua Eei tia Zauj meib Bua Eei Mwavq txig taaib yia naaiq. yia xij pun i-yipq teib puv kaub lovj Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq ninb Bua. naaiq nxm teib puv maaib haiq Euvg lovj Jiaj ninb Bua tu'q Eang a'q.’
45.8: “Navq naaiq se maiq zeid kxj Bua pun yia taaib naaiq. se Tinb huvb kanb Paaiq yia taaib. ninb pun yia Navq faa-lo huvb Eei tia, zruj ninb Eei pyauq zov Eei zyruq, yaag kunq Revg i-yipq teib puv.
45.3: yo-sepq Buaj ninb Eei muab txig, “yia se yo-sepq. yia Eei tia Zxg yem Eei fai?” ninb Eei muab txig haid ninb Navq naaiq nx kxvq, ninb Bua Hruq waaig Revg, zuvq maiq haib tau.
45.21: i-saa-laa-en Eei txn Bua zyrug ei Jyenq zruj. yo-sepq yaag ei Jyenq faa-lo huvb Paaiq Eei waag pun vovb Zia ninb Bua, yaag pun Jyenq Daamb Jauq Eei pyenb fwij.
45.14: yo-sepq Qam Jyenq ninb Eei yrud, Ben-yaa-min, Eyemq. Ben-yaa-min yaag Qam Jyenq ninb Eei kxj Eyemq.
45.23: yo-sepq fuvj zyepg taub lxb Tx Jyenq i-yipq teib puv lovj Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq mivb pun ninb Eei tia. cvj fuvj zyepg taub lxb Eeid Tx Byaub Zauj Fuaq Zauj pun ninb Eei tia yem Daamb Jauq Eang Eei pyenb fwij.
45.6: teib puv vxg tu'q i Havj a'q. Zxg cvj maaib pyaa Havj maiq haib zwavj, maiq haib syru.
45.2: yo-sepq Qa'q Eyemq Bwi Eei, i-yipq myenb zyrug haid mig a'q, cvj siv mivb Tauj huvb ting uaq.
45.20: meib Bua maiq tuvq Kxb fi'q meib Bua Eei ka'naaiq weig zu'g i-yipq teib puv maaib kaub lovj Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq se penj meib Bua Eei.’+”
45.24: yo-sepq zyrug fuvj ninb Eei muab txig Zwrtq Jauq Rwrnj. xij mivb uaq zang ninb kxvq, “Daamb Jauq meib Bua maiq tuvq ta'hauq oj!”
45.28: i-saa-laa-en kxvq, “pwavq Hruq a'q. yia Eei txn, yo-sepq, yem Eei. yia maiq kcvb taig, yia xij mivb pwatg yetg mweig ninb.”
45.7: Tinb huvb Paaiq yia taaib Daavg meib Bua, weig meib Bua lyrub teij myenb yem naaiq luvb Diaq, yaag lovg naaiq Euvg tomb za'eij Fruj kxj Bua Zwrtq.
45.19: “meib yaag xij zu'g Buaj ninb Bua, ‘meib Bua xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx zruj. txb i-yipq teib puv Eei vovb Zia mivb pyenb meib Bua Eei fu'Jweiq Zauj meib Bua Eei auq, yaag xij zu'g txb meib Bua Eei tia taaib.
45.17: faa-lo huvb kxvq Buaj yo-sepq, “Buaj meib Eei muab txig, ‘xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx zruj. zx'q ka'naaiq pun meib Bua Eei lxb Tx Jyenq Rwrnj Kaa-naa-an teib puv.
45.27: ninb Eei txn Bua kxvq Revg yo-sepq Eei waag pun ninb mwavj. yaa-Kopq yaag pwatg yo-sepq pun taaib zipq ninb mivb i-yipq uaq teij vovb Zia, ninb Eei Hruq zyrug fivq taaib a'q.
45.11: Navq naaiq yia haib kruj tia, weig zu'g cvj maaib pyaa Havj tomb vxg. maiq zeid nx c'q, tia Zauj tia Eei pyauq zov myenb Zauj tia maaib Eei yetg zuvq Dxtq naang Kruq.’+”
45.5: meib Bua maiq tuvq Hruq mun, winj kanb zruj txvg laaij maaig yia taaib naaiq. se Tinb huvb Paaiq yia taaib Daavg meib Bua weig Fruj myenb Zamq Eei mcvg.
45.9: ib zang kaanq Rwrnj mivb Buaj yia Eei tia, ninb Eei txn, yo-sepq, Navq naaiq nx kxvq, ‘Tinb huvb pun yia zruj i-yipq teib puv Eei zyruq. tia xij zu'g syepg syepq Eei taaib yia naaiq, maiq tuvq vaib.
45.16: yo-sepq Eei muab txig taaib Eei fyenj siv Tauj huvb ting. faa-lo huvb Zauj ninb Eei zwavj Jyen a'Neiq haig a'q.
45.4: yo-sepq zyrug Buaj ninb Bua, “Toq meib Bua taaib fatq teij maa'b!” ninb Bua zyrug mivb fatq. yo-sepq kxvq, “yia se meib Bua Eei yrud, yo-sepq, tovb kxj Bua maaig mivb i-yipq teib puv uaq taub.
45.10: tia haib yem naaiq, ko-sen teig, nitq fatq teij yia, tia kanb Zauj tia Eei txnb Jweiq funb fa'q, vovb kwanb, pa'ki yuvb kwanb, yuvb kwanb, lyemb yetg zuvq maaib Eei ka'naaiq.
45.22: ninb Eei kxj Bua, ninb pun yetg taub yetg yemg lwib hruj yeng. mq paag Ben-yaa-min ninb pun i Jxib Zyetq luvd Eaanb Zauj pyaa yemg lwib hruj.
45.12: yo-sepq cvj kxvq, “meib Bua taub taub kxj cvj Zauj yia Eei yrud, Ben-yaa-min, zia'q tu'q ib zang Zauj meib Bua kxvq waag se yia, yo-sepq.
45.15: yo-sepq cvj zom ninb Eei taub taub kxj cvj Eyemq. Ga'haaq ninb Eei muab txig Zauj ninb kxvq waag.
45.13: kxvq Buaj tia, yia yem i-yipq teib puv tu'q Eei yetg zuvq Favb laavg. kxvq Revg meib Bua pwatg Eei Jaub lrug pun tia mwavj. yaag xij zu'g kaanq Jyenq txb yia Eei tia taaib naaiq.”
45.1: yo-sepq haid Eyend maiq Jyenq, uamb mweig xij Zwrtq haig a'q, zyrug pe'q sruq ninb Eei ka'Len Eei myenb, “meib Bua yetg zuvq Zwrtq mivb maa'b!” yo-sepq pun ninb Eei muab txig hiuq tu'q ninb uaq zang, maiq maaib yetg taub ka'Len myenb yem.
45.26: ninb Bua Buaj ninb Bua Eei tia, “aa tia aa'b! yo-sepq Zxg yem Eei cj! ib zang ninb kunq Revg yetg nxm i-yipq teib puv.” yaa-Kopq mrub mevb mrub pc'g Eei, maiq syenj ninb Bua Eei waag.
45.25: uaq teij muab txig zyrug yem i-yipq teib puv Rwrnj Tauj Kaa-naa-an teib puv, ninb Bua Eei tia uaq.

3.18: Dau xij weig meib Zwrtq miaq Zwrtq Fimq. meib yaag xij zu'g Eang yem Dau Zwrtq Eei laib miaq.
3.8: uaq Nxi, luvb maanb Mwavj Eei zyavb hog, ninb Bua haid zyruq Tinb huvb yem Wivj ka'Euad yavb Jauq. uaq taub mJavg txn Zauj ninb Eei auq zyrug pia'g Wivj Eei Dyavb lomg mivb pivj Jyenq zyruq.
3.3: mq paag Tinb huvb kxvq, ‘yem Wivj Bu'Dovj uaq zuvb Dyavj Eei pyruq Zinb maang maiq tuvq Eang, lyemb maiq tuvq mua'q. maiq zei c'q, meib Bua zuvq zu'g taig a'q.’+”
3.21: zyruq Tinb huvb lovg scvb Kuq Eei Dopq zruj lwib hruj pun aa-Dam Zauj ninb Eei auq, haa-waa, zu'q.
3.14: zyruq Tinb huvb Buaj uaq tiub naav, “laaij meib Navq naaiq nx zruj, “meib zyrug zu'g hruq kaub Niaq yetg zuvq scvb Kuq, kaub Zamq yetg zuvq Yiab zxib. meib xij zu'g lovg ka'sia lwib Jyenq kan Dau mivb, yetg seij xij zu'g Eang niab Buv.
3.23: zyruq Tinb huvb zyrug zung ninb Zwrtq e-Den Wivj yaag pun ninb zruj lyavb Deig yem Tinb huvb lovg nanq ninb taaib uaq teij nia.
3.6: uaq taub msia'q txn mavg pwatg uaq zuvb pyruq Rweig Eei, taaij Eang Kuq Eei. ninb yaag Namq taaib sij kxvq haib pun myenb kwai nx, za'kevb lovj haig. ninb zyrug kc'q taaib Eang a'q. cvj pun teij ninb Eei Goj Eang.
3.2: uaq taub msia'q txn tau naav, “yem Wivj ka'Euad Eei zuvb zuvb pyruq yia Bua Eang tu'q Eei.
3.20: aa-Dam Tevj ninb Eei auq Zwrtq Buaj heug haa-waa, weig zu'g ninb zruj luvb Diaq myenb Eei maa.
3.24: zyruq zung ninb Zwrtq liud, yem e-Den Wivj Eei tov puv mcvj, zyruq pun Ke-lu-Bim zuaq Jyenq. cvj maaib zuv maaib trud Eei Ru'g Daauq kwinb kwinb pyei puv Eei, tavq Jyenq mivb zyavb mcvg pyruq Eei Dyavj uaq tiub Jauq.
3.7: ninb Bua Eang liud, ninb Bua haib Namq tu'q Tov. ninb Bua hiuq tu'q kanb lcvb kcvq Eei yem, zyrug zx'q vovb Exj Dyavb nxmb lunb taaib Povj Jyenq a'q.
3.19: meib xij zu'g zruj kov Kruq Zwrtq ziaj sin hang uaq teij Dau Zivj taaib haib Zwrtq teij ka'naaiq. zruj Tauj meib cvj Rwrnj penj nia, weig zu'g meib se nia penj taaib. meib se nia, meib xij zu'g cvj penj Rung nia a'q.”
3.17: Tinb huvb yaag kxvq Buaj aa-Dam, “laaij meib mwavj meib Eei auq Eei waag, Eang tovb yia hatg meib, ‘maiq tuvq Eang uaq zuvb pyruq,’ Dau zyrug laaij meib zruj Eei sig zu'g hruq. meib yetg seij xij zu'g pavg Dau zruj kov Kruq Zivj tu'q Eang.
3.11: Tinb huvb naaig kaaj, “haiq taub Buaj meib, meib Eei sin lcvb kcvq Eei? meib Eang tovb yia hatg meib maiq tuvq Eang uaq zuvb pyruq mig a'q saa'b?”
3.5: Tinb huvb Navq naaiq kxvq weig zu'g ninb hiuq tu'q meib Bua Eang liud, meib Bua haib Namq tu'q Tov, meib Bua zyrug Navq Tinb huvb nx, haib hiuq tu'q lovj hiuq tu'q Zyruq.”
3.9: mq paag zyruq Tinb huvb heug uaq taub mJavg txn, “meib yem haaij lcb?”
3.16: Tinb huvb yaag kxvq Buaj uaq taub msia'q txn, “maaib sin Eei zyavb hog yia xij Jaa Tipq pun meib Kruq. Dutq sin Eei zyavb hog meib xij zu'g mun. mq paag meib Zxg xij lovg meib Eei Goj. meib Eei Goj yaag xij kunq Jyenq meib.”
3.4: naav kxvq Buaj msia'q txn, “meib Bua maiq taig lx'g.
3.10: uaq taub mJavg txn tau, “yia haid meib yem naaiq Wivj. yia kamb Riaj haig weig zu'g yia lcvb kcvq Eei yem zyrug pivj meib.”
3.22: zyruq Tinb huvb cvj kxvq, “ib zang uaq laanb myenb se Navq Bua nx, hiuq tu'q lovj, hiuq tu'q Zyruq. xij zu'g maiq tuvq pun ninb suv puad mivb kc'q zyavb mcvg Eei pyruq Eang zyrug yetg liud tu'q zyavb Jyenq.”
3.12: uaq taub mJavg txn tau, “tovb meib pun taaib Zauj yia yem naaiq uaq taub msia'q txn, ninb pun naaiq zuvb Dyavj Eei pyruq yia, yia zyrug Eang mig a'q.”
3.15: yia xij pun meib Zauj naaiq taub msia'q txn taaq win, yaag pun meib Eei zeib fun Zauj ninb Eei zeib fun zruj winb wavq. ninb Eei zeib fun xij Bx'q meib Eei mGxvq huq, meib yaag xij Ex'q ninb Eei zaub Go.”
3.13: zyruq Tinb huvb naaig kaaj uaq taub msia'q txn, “meib zruj Zwrtq haiq Euvg sig mig a'q?” uaq taub msia'q txn tau, “naav kanb Duaq yia, yia zyrug Eang.”
3.1: zyruq Tinb huvb zeij taaib Eei yetg zuvq lomg zavg ka'naaiq se naav kaub kwaij Jiaj. naav naaig kaaj uaq taub msia'q txn, “Tinb huvb za'kevb kxvq maiq pun meib Bua Eang yem naaiq Wivj ka'Euad Eei haiq Euvg pyruq fai?”

43.18: pru txb Jyenq ninb Bua pia'g yo-sepq Eei pyauq uaq zang, ninb Bua kamb Riaj haig, yem Hruq Namq, “ninb txb yia Bua taaib naaiq se laaij taaub Rung tapq Jyenq yia Bua Eei Bua'g Rwib uaq teij Eaanb. ib zang ninb Bua xij lxd sig pun yia Bua, zx'q yia Bua zruj nrub, cvj zx'q yia Bua Eei lxb mq pei.”
43.8: yu-Daa kxvq Buaj ninb Eei tia, i-saa-laa-en, “Toq pun uaq taub txn Zauj yia mivb maa'b! yia Bua zyrug Zwrtq Jauq mivb a'q. tia Zauj yia Bua Zauj yia Bua Eei fu'Jweiq yaag maiq zu'g vxg taig.
43.33: yo-sepq pun zwavj muab txig zweid Jyenq Myen Win mivb yo-sepq Eei tiab uaq puv, yaag ziuj ninb Bua Eei Havb Jeiq zweid Baib yem txnb Lo Baib mivb Tauj txnb faij. ninb Bua kanb pwatg Navq naaiq nx zweid Jyenq, ninb Bua Bua'g hxvb haig, laanb mavg laanb.
43.3: yu-Daa kxvq Buaj ninb Eei tia, “uaq laanb myenb kxvq Niaq Eei Buaj yia Bua, sij kxvq yia Bua maiq txb yia Bua Eei yrub laai Zauj Jyenq mivb nx, yia Bua lyemb maiq tu'q pwatg ninb Eei Myen.
43.32: pru weig yo-sepq kanb Beng nxm tiab, weig uaq teij muab txig cvj kanb Beng nxm tiab. cvj maaib Zauj yo-sepq Eang Naavj uaq teij i-yipq myenb kanb Za'levg Beng nxm tiab, weig zu'g i-yipq myenb haid maiq Kub Zauj hipq-lu myenb Jwavg tiab Eang Naavj.
43.21: Rwrnj mcvj, Tauj yia Bua hitq Eei txvj, yia Bua Kxi Bua'g pwatg kx'g myenb maaid Byaub Eei Eaanb yetg zuvq yem kx'g myenb Eei Bua'g Rwib. Eaanb Eei Niab taaub yaag fib Navq Eei. naaiq teij yetg zuvq Eaanb yia Bua cvj txb Jyenq taaib Twij Rwrnj.
43.14: Toq nrnb Jiaj Eei Tinb huvb pun meib Bua yem uaq laanb myenb Eei Ra'Myen tu'q ninb Kxb lyenb meib Bua, pun meib Bua tu'q Ben-yaa-min Zauj si-me-on txb Rwrnj. yia kanb c'q, maiq kunq xij zu'g kwavg yia Eei fu'Jweiq yaag Zinb ninb a'q.”
43.23: uaq taub pru tau, “maiq tuvq Raub, maiq tuvq kamb Riaj. taaij meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, meib Bua Eei tia Eei Tinb huvb, zx'q naaiq teij Eaanb tapq Bua'g pun meib Bua. meib Bua maaid taaub Rung Byaub Eei Eaanb yia tu'q syru mig a'q.” kxvq liud, ninb cvj txb si-me-on taaib.
43.6: i-saa-laa-en kxvq, “meib Bua zruj haiq Euvg hxig yia Dovg naaiq Kruq? weig haiq tiug Buaj uaq laanb myenb meib Bua cvj maaib taub yrud?”
43.34: ninb Bua Eang Eei ka'naaiq, pru yem yo-sepq Eei tiab zx'q taaib pun ninb Bua. mq paag Ben-yaa-min tu'q Zamq pyaa kruq. ninb Bua Zauj yo-sepq Fyenb yrub Eei Eang, Fyenb yrub Eei hopq.
43.2: yaa-Kopq Eei Mwavq txig Eang Revg mivb i-yipq teib puv maaid taaib Eei Byaub mig a'q. yaa-Kopq zyrug kxvq Buaj ninb Eei txn, “meib Bua xij zu'g cvj mivb maaid teij Byaub maa'b!”
43.20: “tomb kxj aag, yia Bua Toq Buaj Jruj waag meib og. yia Bua taaib maaid taaub Rung Byaub.
43.24: uaq taub pru txb uaq teij muab txig pia'g pyauq lxd uam pun ninb Bua Raauj zauj yaag lxd miaq pun ninb Bua Eei lxb Eang.
43.28: ninb Bua tau, “meib Eei pru, yia Bua Eei tia, yem lovj Eei.” ninb Bua cvj Do'q Fiag paaij.
43.7: ninb Eei txn Bua tau, “uaq laanb myenb naaig mwrng Tauj yia Bua Zauj yia Bua Eei Mwavq txig. ninb naaig kaaj, ‘meib Bua Eei tia Zxg yem Eei fai? cvj maaib yrud Eei?’ yia Bua Kuvj ziuj ninb naaig Eei waag tau Navq. yia Bua fuvg hiuq tu'q ninb xij kxvq, ‘xij zu'g txb yrub laai taaib?’+”
43.29: yo-sepq pwatg Zauj ninb Jwavg maa uaq taub yrud, Ben-yaa-min, ninb zyrug naaig, “zinb Daavg meib Bua kxvq Buaj yia, meib Bua maaib taub yrub laai, tovb naaiq taub saa'b? txn aag, Toq Tinb huvb Zeij en pun meib.”
43.19: Tauj kcvb Daavg ninb Bua zyrug kxvq Buaj kruj yo-sepq Eei pyauq uaq taub tomb pru,
43.17: uaq taub pru ei Jyenq yo-sepq Eei waag zruj, txb Jyenq uaq teij muab txig mivb yo-sepq Eei pyauq.
43.31: Raauj liud Myen, ninb Zwrtq taaib Eyend Jyenq uamb mweig, cvj heug ninb Eei pru Beng Naavj.
43.30: kxvq liud, yo-sepq xij zu'g pyauj. ninb haid Namq! haig ninb Eei yrud, Eyend maiq Jyenq uamb mweig, zyrug pia'g uaq pyauq ken Eyemq.
43.27: yo-sepq naaig ninb Bua, “meib Bua yem lovj Eei saa'b?” cvj naaig ninb Bua, “zinb Daavg meib Bua kxvq meib Bua Eei tia koj haig a'q. ninb Zxg yem Eei fai? ninb lovj Eei saa'b?”
43.11: i-saa-laa-en kxvq Buaj ninb Eei txn Bua, “sij kxvq za'kevb xij zu'g txb ninb mivb nx, meib Bua xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx zruj. xij zu'g txb teij naaiq nxm teib puv kaub lovj Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq mivb zruj zivb Eeig pun uaq laanb myenb. zx'q teij Dyavb zuv Daav Zauj teij mweib txvb, Diab Daav, mu-yxg Zauj Euvg pyrub vanb Daav Zauj an-man pyruq, tapq Jyenq ka'naaiq txb mivb.
43.5: mq paag sij kxvq maiq pun yrub laai Zauj yia Bua mivb, yia Bua maiq haib mivb a'q. weig zu'g uaq laanb myenb Buaj yia Bua, ‘meib Bua maiq txb yrub laai taaib nx, meib Bua lyemb maiq tu'q pwatg yia Eei Myen.’+”
43.9: yia lovg yia kanb Eei mcvg zruj Daamb taaub. tia heug yia kanb peu naaiq taub txn tu'q Eei. sij kxvq yia maiq txb ninb Rwrnj Tauj meib naaiq, yia lcvd yetg seij Daamb txv.
43.16: yo-sepq pwatg Ben-yaa-min Zauj Jyenq taaib zyrug Buaj kruj ninb Eei pyauq Eei tomb pru, “txb naaiq teij myenb mivb yia Eei pyauq. xij zu'g taij taub scvb Kuq Beng taaib Eang weig zu'g naaiq teij myenb xij zu'g Zauj yia Eang luvb aanj.”
43.4: sij kxvq tia pun yrub laai Zauj yia Bua mivb, yia Bua zyrug mivb Tevj tia maaid Byaub.
43.10: sij kxvq maiq Navq naaiq zuaq laub, yia Bua zuvq mivb tu'q i Rung Rwrnj taaib a'q.”
43.22: yia Bua kanb Za'levg txb Jyenq Eaanb taaib maaid Byaub. zinb Daavg uaq Rung Eei Eaanb, maiq hiuq tu'q haiq taub tapq yia Bua Eei Bua'g ka'Euad.”
43.12: meib Bua yaag xij zu'g txb Eaanb kaub Zamq mivb Daavg uaq Rung i kruq. xij zu'g txb tovb yem Bua'g uaq teij Eaanb Twij Rwrnj, Riaj ninb Bua tapq txvg mq pei.
43.15: ninb Bua muab txig zyrug Zwrtq Jauq mivb i-yipq teib puv, cvj txb Jyenq zivb Eeig Zauj Eaanb kaub Zamq mivb Daavg uaq Rung Eei i kruq, yaag txb Jyenq Ben-yaa-min mivb. mivb Tauj i-yipq teib puv, ninb Bua pia'g mivb lxd yo-sepq.
43.13: kunq txb Jyenq meib Bua Eei yrud mivb lxd uaq laanb myenb.
43.1: yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv maaib tomb Waav tomb vxg Kruq haig.
43.26: yo-sepq Tauj pyauq, ninb Bua zx'q ninb Bua txb taaib Eei zivb Eeig yem uaq pyauq pun yo-sepq, yaag Pua'q Tauj Dau paaij.
43.25: uaq teij muab txig Beng zyavj ninb Bua Eei zivb Eeig zuaq Jyenq yo-sepq Rwrnj, weig zu'g ninb Bua hiuq tu'q ninb Bua xij zu'g Zauj ninb yem uaq Eang luvb aanj.

50.18: ninb Eei kxj Bua zyrug mivb Tauj yo-sepq Eei Ra'Myen kweig Fiag Dau paaij cvj kxvq, “yia Bua yem meib Eei Ra'Myen Toq zruj meib Eei nrub.”
50.8: yo-sepq Eei Mwavq txig Zauj ninb Eei muab txig cvj Zauj ninb Eei tia Eei pyauq zov myenb yetg zuvq kan Jyenq mivb. Kuvj zevg fu'Jweib faij Zauj pa'ki yuvb, yuvb Zauj vovb yem uaq ko-sen Navq.
50.3: Diab sai zyrug lovg feij zyepg Nxi zruj, weig zu'g naaiq teij kov Qyemj zu'g feij zyepg Nxi. i-yipq myenb yaag Tevj Jyenq Raub Eyemq Zyetq zyepg Nxi.
50.21: Navq naaig, kxj Bua maiq tuvq kamb Riaj. yia yaag xij kruj meib Bua Zauj meib Bua Eei Mwavq txig.” ninb kxvq waag lovj Eei pun ninb Bua, xn ninb Bua Eei Hruq.
50.14: zavj liud ninb Eei tia, yo-sepq Zauj ninb Eei muab txig cvj Zauj ninb mivb Eei myenb yetg zuvq Rwrnj i-yipq teib puv a'q.
50.23: yaag tu'q pwatg e-faa-im Eei fu'Jweiq Tauj ta'faam txig. cvj tu'q zipq maa-natq-sej Eei txn, maa-Ki, Eei fu'Jweiq pia'g ninb Eei myenb hrud.
50.6: faa-lo huvb tau, “kunq txb meib Eei tia mivb zavj ziuj meib Zauj ninb lcvd Jiad Eei waag.”
50.2: ninb Paaiq Tevj ninb zruj kov uaq teij Diab sai lovg Diab uam zyemj Jyenq ninb Eei tia, i-saa-laa-en, Eei sei pun sei maiq haib huq, maiq haib zweij.
50.20: meib Bua taaq za'eij hxig yia, mq paag Tinb huvb lovg uaq Euvg za'eij zruj lovj Eei sig. Navq ib zang Bua pwatg Jyenq nx, ninb lovg naaiq Euvg za'eij Fruj myenb Zamq Eei mcvg.
50.24: yo-sepq kxvq Buaj ninb Eei muab txig, “kwei seij Eei zyavb hog aaq lamb teij Tauj a'q. mq paag Tinb huvb zuvq xij taaib Tevj meib Bua, txb meib Bua Zwrtq naaiq nxm teib puv, mivb Tauj zinb Daavg ninb lcvd Jiad vcvg waag pun apg-laa-ham, i-sakg Zauj yaa-Kopq, uaq nxm teib puv.”
50.7: yo-sepq zyrug txb ninb Eei tia mivb zavj a'q. faa-lo huvb Eei yetg zuvq Jyen yaag Zauj Jyenq mivb. se yem huvb ting zruj kaub Lo uaq teij Jyen, Zauj yem i-yipq teib puv haiq taub zruj Lo Eei myenb, yaag kan Jyenq yo-sepq mivb.
50.19: mq paag yo-sepq kxvq Buaj ninb Eei kxj Bua, “maiq tuvq kamb Riaj. yia se maiq zeid Tinb huvb.
50.17: ‘xij zu'g Buaj yo-sepq, Toq kwavg Gxi meib Eei kxj Bua zruj txvg hxig meib uaq teij sig.’ ib zang yia Bua, meib Eei tia Eei Tinb huvb Eei pru, Toq meib kwavg Gxi yia Bua zruj txvg meib Eei zwid.” yo-sepq haid Zwrtq naaiq teij waag ninb zyrug Eyemq a'q.
50.11: yem uaq nxm txvj Eei Kaa-naa-an myenb pwatg myenb yem aa-Taatq Bx'q Byaub Eei Zyavq Raub Eyemq, ninb Bua kxvq, “naaiq teij i-yipq myenb Raub Eyemq, zruj nxm Janb taig yinb Lo Eei.” weig naaiq ninb Bua zyrug Zwrtq Buaj heug uaq nxm txvj aa-Ben-mitq-laa-im. uaq nxm txvj yem Jx-Dcn Daaib Eei tov puv mcvj.
50.5: Buaj ninb, ‘yia Eei tia xij kwei seij uaq zang, ninb xij yia lcvd Jiad vcvg waag txb ninb Eei sei mivb Kaa-naa-an teib puv zavj Jyenq ninb kanb zu'g zyavj Eei zrub mrub.’ Navq naaiq, Toq pun yia txb yia Eei tia mivb zavj. zavj liud, yia cvj Rwrnj naaiq.”
50.9: maaib maab Zia, maaib myenb keb maad Zauj Jyenq mivb. naaiq teij myenb yetg zuvq penj yetg kwanb Zamq Eei.
50.16: ninb Bua zyrug pun myenb mivb Buaj yo-sepq, “Bua Eei tia maiq kcvb kwei seij uaq zang ninb kxvq,
50.4: naaiq teij Raub Eyemq Eei zyavb hog Jiaj liud, yo-sepq kxvq Buaj faa-lo huvb Eei Jyen, “sij kxvq yia zruj tu'q hxpg meib Bua, Toq meib Bua txb yia naaiq teij waag mivb Buaj faa-lo huvb og.
50.10: mivb Tauj Jx-Dcn Daaib Eei tov puv mcvj, aa-Taatq Eei Bx'q Byaub Zyavq, ninb Bua Qa'q Eyemq Bwi Eei. yo-sepq yaag yem naaig weig ninb Eei tia Raub Eyemq siag Nxi.
50.22: yo-sepq Zauj ninb Eei tia Eei Mwavq txig yem i-yipq teib puv, ninb zyavb tu'q yetg pc'q zyepg Havj,
50.12: yaa-Kopq Eei txn Bua zyrug ei Jyenq ninb Bua Eei tia Paaiq Eei waag zruj.
50.15: ninb Bua Eei tia kwei seij mig a'q, yo-sepq Eei kxj Bua kxvq, “Riaj yo-sepq xij Rxv Bua mq pei, ziuj Bua zinb Daavg zruj hxig ninb Eei sig xij winb pun Bua.”
50.13: ninb Bua txb sei mivb Kaa-naa-an teib puv, zavj Jyenq yem makq-pe-laa uaq Rov Dau Eei Bcvb Kwrtq, leib mam-le maiq ko. tovb zinb Daavg apg-laa-ham Tevj hitq-Tai myenb, e-fo-lon, maaid zruj zrub kemb uaq Rov Dau.
50.1: yo-sepq pwatg ninb Eei tia tavj Qiaj, ninb zyrug Pua'q Jyenq ninb Eei tia kub vwaaig Qa'q Eyemq yaag zom ninb Eei tia Eei Myen.
50.26: yo-sepq zyavb yetg pc'q zyepg Havj yem uaq i-yipq teib puv kwei seij mig a'q. ninb Bua zx'q sei zyemj Jyenq Diab uam pun maiq haib huq, maiq haib zweij, yem uaq i-yipq teib puv tapq Jyenq penq a'q.
50.25: yo-sepq cvj heug i-saa-laa-en Eei txn lcvd vcvg waag. ninb kxvq, “Tinb huvb zuvq xij taaib Tevj meib Bua. meib Bua xij zu'g txb Jyenq yia Eei Buvq pyenb Jyenq mivb.”

14.18: cvj maaib saa-lem zivb Eei huvb, men-Ki-se-Dekg, txb teij Fuaq Zauj a'vung tiuq pun apg-laam. men-Ki-se-Dekg zruj yem Lav Jiaj Eei Tinb huvb Eei sai myenb.
14.8: Ga'haaq soj-Dom zivb Eei huvb, ko-mo-laa zivb Eei huvb, atg-maa zivb Eei huvb, sej-Bo-yim zivb Eei huvb, Zauj Be-laa zivb (naaiq se soj-aa) Eei huvb Zwrtq mivb sitg-Dim hxvg Daub pcvb Eei txvj
14.3: naaiq teij pyaa taub huvb kapq Jyenq Qa'q yem sitg-Dim hxvg (se Kxib Rauq Eei txvj) Bx'q Jaaj.
14.21: soj-Dom zivb Eei huvb kxvq Buaj apg-laam, “Twij myenb Rwrnj pun yia. ka'naaiq meib kanb lovg a'q.”
14.14: apg-laam haid kxvq ninb Eei Zyen fun zu'g Zaavq mivb, ninb zyrug tiug Rxib yem ninb Eei pyauq zov Zwrtq seij, haib Bx'q Jaaj Eei mJavg txn, faamb pc'q zyepg petq taub, zung Jyenq mivb Tauj Daan zivb.
14.23: yia lcvd ta'faanb meib Eei haiq Euvg ka'naaiq yia maiq lovg yetg teij. lyemb yetg tiub swij fai yetg tiub heb Laav yia zuvq maiq lovg weig pun meib Ga'haaq hivq maiq tu'q kxvq, ‘yia Zeij apg-laam putq zxib.’
14.6: cvj Zauj sej-i teib puv Bov zavg txvj Eei ho-li myenb, cvj Bx'q hivb Tauj en-paa-laan zivb nitq teib puvb Waav uaq.
14.2: naaiq teij huvb tiaj mivb Zauj soj-Dom zivb Eei huvb, Bei-laa, ko-mo-laa zivb Eei huvb, Bin-saa, atg-maa zivb Eei huvb, si-naapq, sej-Bo-yim zivb Eei huvb, se-me-Be, Zauj Be-laa zivb (naaiq se soj-aa zivb) Eei huvb Bx'q Jaaj.
14.20: Zev yem Lav Jiaj Eei Tinb huvb, weig zu'g ninb pun meib Eei winb wavq zu'g yem meib Eei puab Diaq.” apg-laam zyrug zx'q ninb tu'q Rwrnj taaib Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq, zyepg kruq Eei yetg kruq pun men-Ki-se-Dekg.
14.24: yia kanb maiq lovg yetg Euvg Zwrtq liud yia Eei myenb Eang liud hopq liud Eei. maaib kan yia mivb Eei myenb, aa-ne, etg-Ko Zauj mam-le, xij zu'g pun ninb Bua tu'q ninb Bua Eei pwrng Navq.”
14.7: ninb Bua cvj Rwrnj Tauj en-mitq-fatq, (naaiq se Kaa-Detg) Bx'q hivb Revg yem haa-saa-son Taa-maa Eei aa-maa-lekq myenb, lyemb aa-mo-lai myenb.
14.19: ninb yaag pwav waag pun apg-laam, “Toq yem Lav Jiaj Eei Tinb huvb, zeij luvb zeij Dau uaq taub, Zeij fu'q pun apg-laam.
14.17: apg-laam Bx'q hivb Ke-Do-laa-o-me huvb cvj Zauj ninb tovb Hruq Bx'q Jaaj uaq teij huvb, ninb zyrug Rwrnj. Tauj saa-we hxvg, (cvj maaib Buaj heug “huvb hxvg”), soj-Dom zivb Eei huvb Zwrtq taaib zipq.
14.11: uaq teij pyei taub huvb Zaavq Revg soj-Dom Zauj ko-mo-laa zivb Eei Euvb Euvg ka'naaiq Zauj yetg zuvq Eang hopq zyrug mivb mig a'q.
14.5: zyepg feij Havj uaq Havj, Ke-Do-laa-o-me huvb cvj Zauj ninb kapq Qa'q Bx'q Jaaj uaq teij huvb mivb Bx'q hivb yem atg-Taa-lotq-Kaan-naa-im Eei le-faa-im myenb, yem haam zivb Eei suj-sim myenb, yem saa-we Ki-li-yaa-Taa-im Eei Daub pcvb Eei e-mim myenb,
14.9: Zauj uaq teij pyei taub huvb Bx'q Jaaj. maaib e-laam zivb Eei huvb, Ke-Do-laa-o-me, maaib ko-yim zivb Eei huvb, Ti-Daan, maaib si-naa teib puv Eei huvb, am-laa-fen, yaag maaib en-laa-saaj zivb Eei huvb, aa-le-okg. pyei taub huvb Zauj pyaa taub huvb Bx'q Jaaj.
14.16: ninb Bua zx'q yetg zuvq Zaavq mivb Eei ka'naaiq Rwrnj. lyemb ninb Eei fun, lotq, Zauj lotq Eei Euvb Euvg ka'naaiq, cvj Zauj msia'q txn Zauj pc'g fivj yetg zuvq txb Rwrnj Revg taaib a'q.
14.4: ninb Bua zu'g Ke-Do-laa-o-me huvb kunq ninb Bua zyepg Eeig Havj mq paag Tauj zyepg faam Havj uaq Havj ninb Bua vcvg Jyenq.
14.10: sitg-Dim hxvg maaib Erub haig Eei zuv Eei Kwrtq pwavq Revg. soj-Dom Zauj ko-mo-laa zivb Eei huvb Tiuj pyauj, ninb Bua maaib teij myenb Dxtq naaiq teij zuv Eei Kwrtq mig a'q. zevg Fiag Eei myenb pyauj faauj Bov.
14.22: apg-laam tau soj-Dom zivb Eei huvb, “yia suv Jyenq puad txv Jyenq zyruq, tovb yem Lav Jiaj, zeij luvb zeij Dau Eei Tinb huvb, lcvd Jiaj vcvg waag.
14.12: ninb Bua yaag Zaavq apg-laam Eei fun, lotq, Zauj ninb Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq txb mivb Revg, weig zu'g ninb yem soj-Dom zivb.
14.15: Tauj uaq apg-laam zx'q ninb kanb Eei myenb pun Gxi zruj yetg kwanb yetg kwanb Eei, luvb mwrnd zang Bx'q uaq teij myenb cvj zung Jyenq mivb Tauj ho-Baa zivb yem Daa-matq-katg zivb Eei pa'q puv mcvj.
14.13: maaib taub myenb pyauj Dutq zyrug txb naaiq teij sig mivb Buaj hipq-lu myenb, apg-laam. apg-laam yem aa-mo-lai myenb, mam-le, Eei tomb Ba'ov zwei Dyavb lomg. mam-le Zauj ninb Eei i taub yrud, etg-Ko Zauj aa-ne, zruj apg-laam Eei lob kcv txig.
14.1: txij uaq zang Eei luvb Diaq maaib si-naa teib puv Eei huvb, am-laa-fen, maaib en-laa-saaj zivb Eei huvb, aa-li-okg, maaib e-laam zivb Eei huvb, Ke-Do-laa-o-me, cvj maaib ko-yim zivb Eei huvb, Ti-Daan.

48.18: ninb kxvq Buaj ninb Eei tia, “tia aa'b! maiq zeid Navq naaiq lx'g. txnb Lo tovb naaiq taub. xij zu'g lovg meib Eei Byaaug Jia'q puad maan naaiq taub Eei mGxvq.”
48.8: i-saa-laa-en pwatg yo-sepq Eei txn Bua, ninb naaig kaaj, “naaiq haiq taub?”
48.3: yaa-Kopq kxvq Buaj yo-sepq, “nrnb Jiaj Eei Tinb huvb yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv, lutq teig, hing Zwrtq taaib pwav waag tia.
48.21: pwav liud waag, i-saa-laa-en kxvq Buaj yo-sepq, “yia kwei seij Eei zyavb hog aaq lamb Tauj a'q. mq paag Tinb huvb zuvq Zauj meib Bua yem, yaag xij txb meib Bua Rwrnj meib Bua Eei ovb Taaij Eei teib puv.
48.14: mq paag i-saa-laa-en Jiuq Jyenq puad. Byaaug Jia'q maan Jyenq e-faa-im Eei mGxvq maiq kunq ninb zruj txnb faij. zaaij Jia'q cvj maan Jyenq maa-natq-sej Eei mGxvq maiq kunq maa-natq-sej zruj txnb Lo.
48.6: Ga'haaq meib cvj tu'q fu'Jweiq nx, zyrug funj penj meib kanb Eei pwrng. ninb Bua Ripg Eei pwrng se kan ninb Bua Eei kxj Eei Buaj Ripg Navq.
48.2: myenb Buaj yaa-Kopq, “meib Eei txn, yo-sepq, taaib mavg meib a'q.” yaa-Kopq zyrug Zcvj Jiad sin taaib zweid Jyenq uaq Zruj.
48.20: uaq Nxi yaa-Kopq pwav waag ninb Bua. ninb kxvq, “i-saa-laa-en myenb xij txb meib Eei Buaj mivb pwav waag. ninb Bua xij kxvq, ‘Toq Tinb huvb pun meib Navq e-faa-im Zauj maa-natq-sej nx.’+” i-saa-laa-en zyrug Navq naaiq nx pun e-faa-im tu'q zruj kaub Lo maa-natq-sej.
48.7: yia yem patg-Daan-aa-lam Rwrnj uaq zang, yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv leib e-faa-laa-Taa muvq maiq navg ko, meib Eei maa, laa-sen, kwei seij, pun yia Raub haig. yia zavj ninb mivb e-faa-laa-Taa muvq uaq tiub Jauq Eei ka'Len.” (e-faa-laa-Taa cvj maaib nxm Buaj heug Betg-le-hem.)
48.19: mq paag ninb Eei tia maiq Kavq. ninb kxvq, “txn aa'b! yia hiuq Eei. maa-natq-sej Eei zeib fun yaag xij penj yetg fivj. ninb yaag tu'q zruj Lo. mq paag ninb Eei yrud xij tu'q zruj kaub Lo. yrud Eei zeib fun xij penj Zamb fivj Lo Eei.”
48.17: yo-sepq pwatg ninb Eei tia Navq naaiq nx zx'q Byaaug Jia'q puad maan Jyenq e-faa-im Eei mGxvq, ninb maiq hxpg Hruq. ninb zyrug zx'q ninb tia Eei puad yem e-faa-im Eei mGxvq waan Gxi, xij pun ninb maan maa-natq-sej Eei mGxvq.
48.11: i-saa-laa-en kxvq Buaj yo-sepq, “yia Namq taaib yetg liud maiq tu'q pwatg meib, mq paag Tinb huvb pun yia lyemb meib Eei txn tu'q pwatg.”
48.5: yaa-Kopq cvj kxvq, “yo-sepq aag, tovb yia maiq kcvb taaib, meib yem naaiq i-yipq teib puv tu'q uaq teij i taub txn, e-faa-im Zauj maa-natq-sej, xij zu'g funj penj yia Eei pwrng txn Navq lu-Ben Zauj si-me-on nx.
48.9: yo-sepq Buaj ninb Eei tia, “naaiq se Tinb huvb pun yia yem naaiq tu'q taaib Eei txn.” i-saa-laa-en kxvq, “txb taaib yia naaiq weig pun yia pwav waag ninb Bua.”
48.16: Toq Fruj yia leib Dutq yetg zuvq haib hxig yia Eei ze'g naang uaq taub finb myenb Zeij fu'q pun naaiq teij i taub txn. Toq pun naaiq teij i taub txn Ripg yia Eei Buaj Zauj yia Eei ov, apg-laa-ham, Zauj yia Eei tia, i-sakg, Eei Buaj. Toq pun ninb Bua yem naaiq luvb Diaq Yaavj Jiad taaib Zamq.”
48.4: ninb kxvq, ‘yia xij pun meib maaib txnb Jweiq funb fa'q Zamq, Yaavj taaib zruj Zamb fivj myenb. yia yaag xij zx'q naaiq nxm teib puv Jiu pun meib Eei hod txig zeib fun yetg liud Ripg.’+”
48.10: i-saa-laa-en Eei Havb Jeiq koj haig, mziv Buaq, mavg maiq navg zyen. yo-sepq zyrug txb ninb Eei txn mivb Tauj ninb Eei tia uaq, ninb Eei tia Qam Jyenq zom.
48.22: yia zx'q tovb yia lovg Ru'g Daauq Zauj Jwavb zinj Zaavq tu'q aa-mo-lai myenb Eei uaq nxm zxv Jiu pun meib, maiq zeid pun meib Eei kxj Bua.”
48.12: yo-sepq Lxpq ninb Eei txn Fiag i-saa-laa-en Eei Zamb zwib yaag yem ninb Eei Ra'Myen Pua'q Fiag Tauj Dau.
48.15: ninb zyrug pwav waag yo-sepq a'q. ninb kxvq, “Toq yia Eei ov, apg-laa-ham, Zauj yia Eei tia, i-sakg, pua'g zavg Eei Tinb huvb Zeij fu'q naaiq teij i taub txn. Toq yetg seij txb yia Tauj ib Nxi Eei Tinb huvb Zeij fu'q pun ninb Bua.
48.13: yo-sepq Ken Jyenq ninb Eei i taub txn, Byaaug Jia'q puad Ken e-faa-im mivb yem i-saa-laa-en Eei zaaij puv. zaaij Jia'q puad Ken maa-natq-sej mivb yem i-saa-laa-en Eei Byaaug puv.
48.1: Ga'haaq maiq navg laub, maaib myenb Buaj yo-sepq, “meib Eei tia maiq lovj.” yo-sepq zyrug txb Jyenq ninb Eei i taub txn, maa-natq-sej Zauj e-faa-im, mivb mavg ninb Eei tia.

34.18: haa-mo Zauj ninb Eei txn, se-Kem, haid naaiq teij waag hxpg Hruq Eei.
34.8: haa-mo kxvq Buaj yaa-Kopq Bua txnb tiaj txig, “yia Eei txn, se-Kem, Namq haig naaiq taub sia'q. Toq meib Bua pun naaiq taub sia'q yia Eei txn lovg zruj auq.
34.3: ninb haid Namq naaiq taub sia'q, Di-naa, zyrug Zauj Di-naa kxvq lovj, xij Duaq naaiq taub sia'q Namq ninb.
34.21: ninb Bua kxvq, “naaiq teij myenb Zauj Bua zruj kxb yrud txig. Bua xij zu'g pun ninb Bua Zauj Bua Jwavg teib puv yem, pia'g Zwrtq maaid maaig. Bua Eei teib puv Javq Eei, kauj tu'q pun ninb Bua yem Eei. Bua yaag haib lovg ninb Bua Eei sia'q. ninb Bua yaag haib lovg Bua Eei sia'q.
34.14: ninb Bua kxvq, “yia Bua maiq haib puvj yia Bua Eei muag pun maiq Jiaj kaatq Eei leid Eei myenb lovg. Navq naaiq zruj, yia Bua Eei mevb taub waaig Revg a'q.
34.23: ninb Bua Eei scvb Kuq, ninb Bua maaib Eei Euvb Euvg ka'naaiq zyrug penj Bua Eei maiq zeid? Toq pun Bua Navq naaiq nx zruj. ninb Bua zyrug Zauj Bua yem naaiq a'q.”
34.6: se-Kem Eei tia, haa-mo, Zwrtq mivb Zauj yaa-Kopq Zaavb laavb.
34.2: kunq uaq nxm txvj Eei hi-wai myenb, haa-mo Eei txn, se-Kem, pwatg Di-naa zyrug Eau Jyenq ninb Zaa.
34.20: haa-mo Zauj ninb Eei txn, se-Kem, zyrug mivb zivb kcvb Daavg Zauj yetg nxm zivb Eei kxb yrud kxvq.
34.24: uaq nxm zivb Eei yetg zwavj kxb yrud pwavq Hruq haa-mo Zauj se-Kem Eei waag. zivb ka'Euad Eei yetg zuvq mJavg txn zyrug Jiaj kaatq Eei leid Revg.
34.28: ninb Bua zx'q pa'ki yuvb, yuvb, vovb, lxb, yetg zuvq ka'naaiq. maiq kunq yem zivb fai yem Deig, ninb Bua zx'q Revg mig a'q.
34.7: yaa-Kopq Eei txn Bua yem uaq naab yetq haid naaiq teij sig ninb Bua zyrug Rwrnj taaib. ninb Bua haid Hruq waaig Revg, Qiaj Jiad haig se-Kem Navq naaiq nx zruj to'g Zaa yaa-Kopq Eei sia'q. se maiq hxpg zu'g zruj Eei sig yaag mavg Piaj haig ninb Bua i-saa-laa-en myenb.
34.29: haiq Euvg maaib Jaab zinb Eei ka'naaiq ninb Bua yaag zx'q Revg. lyemb msia'q txn, lyemb fu'Jweiq yaag txb Jyenq mivb. lyemb ninb Bua Eei Jaab tivb yaag luq Fav Revg mig a'q.
34.19: uaq taub txn zyrug maiq vaib, ei Jyenq yaa-Kopq Eei txn Bua Eei waag kaanq Jyenq zruj, weig zu'g ninb Namq haig yaa-Kopq Eei sia'q. ninb Bua yetg zuvq muab txig se se-Kem zruj kaub Lo Jiaj.
34.17: mq paag sij kxvq meib Bua maiq mwavj yia Bua, maiq Jiaj kaatq Eei leid Revg, yia Bua txb yia Bua Eei muag pyauj a'q.”
34.31: ninb Eei txn Bua tau, “yia Bua maiq pun ninb zruj pun yia Bua Eei muag txvj maaig pwrnb sin Eei msia'q txn.”
34.30: yaa-Kopq Buaj si-me-on Zauj le-wi, “meib Bua Navq naaiq nx zruj xij pun yia zu'g sig, zu'g Kaa-naa-an myenb, pe-litq-si myenb Zauj yetg zuvq yem naaiq nxm teib puv Eei myenb Rxv yia a'q. Bua yaag maiq maaib myenb Zamq. sij kxvq uaq teij myenb kapq Qa'q taaib Bx'q yia nx, yia Zauj yia Eei pyauq zov myenb zyrug zu'g myetg Revg.”
34.27: yaa-Kopq Eei txn Bua pia'g naaiq teij zu'g taij taig Eei myenb Eei pyauq, luq Revg uaq nxm zivb, laaij uaq nxm zivb Eei myenb zruj pun ninb Bua Eei muag Eei mevb taub waaig.
34.11: se-Kem yaag kxvq Buaj Di-naa Eei tia Zauj ninb Eei kxj Bua, “Toq meib Bua Gxi fim Gxi eij yia. meib Bua xij lovg haiq Euvg yia zyrug pun.
34.5: yaa-Kopq hiuq tu'q se-Kem zruj pun ninb Eei sia'q Eei mevb taub waaig mq paag yaa-Kopq maiq kcvb kxvq haiq Euvg weig zu'g ninb Eei txn Bua yem uaq naab puvj scvb Kuq. ninb zuaq Jyenq ninb Eei txn Bua Rwrnj.
34.9: yem naaiq mivb Bua lomb Rxib Jiu Tov. puvj meib Bua Eei sia'q pun yia Bua Eei txn lovg, yaag txb yia Bua Eei sia'q pun meib Bua Eei txn lovg.
34.16: Navq naaig yia Bua zyrug haib puvj yia Bua Eei sia'q pun meib Bua, yaag txb meib Bua Eei sia'q taaib lovg zruj auq. yia Bua yaag haib Zauj meib Bua Jwavg teib puv yem.
34.4: se-Kem Buaj ninb Eei tia, haa-mo, “Toq tia mivb Tevj yia kxvq naaiq taub sia'q og.”
34.10: Navq naaiq meib Bua haib Zauj yia Bua Jwavg teib puv yem. meib Bua xij yem haiq nxm txvj, kunq yem tu'q Eei, cvj lxd Dau lyepg kanb Eei vwaab kxn, pia'g Zwrtq zruj scvb eij.”
34.22: naaiq teij myenb a'Neiq Zauj Bua Jwavg teib puv yem, penj yetg fivj, mq paag maaib yetg tiug ninb Bua Zivj taaib lcvd, se Bua taub taub mJavg txn xij zu'g Navq ninb Bua nx, Jiaj kaatq Eei leid.
34.12: xij lovg leib kiv Zauj zivb Eeig Bu'ziaj kunq kxvq maa'b! meib Bua xij lovg haiq Euvg Bu'ziaj yia pun Revg, ta'faanb tu'q meib Bua Eei sia'q Navq.”
34.15: yia Bua maaib Du'g tiub leid Navq Zivj haib lcvd pun, se meib Bua taub taub mJavg txn xij zu'g Navq yia Bua nx, Jiaj kaatq Eei leid Revg.
34.13: laaij se-Kem zruj waaig ninb Bua Eei muag, Di-naa, Eei mevb taub, yaa-Kopq Eei txn Bua Duaq se-Kem Zauj ninb Eei tia, haa-mo.
34.1: yaa-Kopq Zauj le-aa maaib taub sia'q, Buaj heug Di-naa. maaib Nxi Di-naa Zwrtq mivb Zauj uaq nxm txvj Eei msia'q txn Ryaaug.
34.26: lyemb haa-mo Zauj se-Kem i txnb tiaj, ninb Bua yaag taij kwavg mig a'q. yaag txb Di-naa yem se-Kem Eei pyauq Zwrtq mivb mig a'q.
34.25: Jiaj liud kaatq Eei leid ta'faam Nxi uaq Nxi, uaq teij mJavg txn Zxg mun Jyenq Eei. i taub yaa-Kopq Eei txn, Di-naa Eei kxj, si-me-on Zauj le-wi, pwij Jyenq Ru'g Daauq pia'g zivb, lyemb maiq maaib haiq taub kruq Eeib. ninb Bua zyrug pia'g mivb taij Revg uaq nxm zivb Eei mJavg txn.

2.18: zyruq Tinb huvb cvj kxvq, “Du'g laanb myenb kanb yem Navq se maiq hxpg. yia cvj xij zeij taub taaib Pwij ninb, Zauj ninb zruj txig Tevj ninb.”
2.8: zyruq Tinb huvb zyrug yem tov puv, e-Den uaq, zruj nxm Wivj yaag pun ninb zeij taaib uaq taub myenb yem Wivj ka'Euad.
2.3: Tinb huvb Zeij fu'q ta'Zyetq Nxi, pun uaq nxm Nxi penj Zivb Revg Nxi, weig zu'g ninb zeij luvb zeij Dau Eei kov zyavj. ninb yaag tivb kov hitq Kwrnj.
2.21: zyruq Tinb huvb zyrug pun uaq taub myenb pweij mFxmb Do Eei. mFxmb mivb uaq zang, ninb zx'q tiub uaq laanb myenb Eei la'scvj Buvq cvj pun xq zyavb Dipg mig a'q.
2.14: ta'faam Zaaj heug Tai-kitg Daaib, lyrug kan atg-si-lia teib puv Eei tov puv mcvj mivb. ta'feij Zaaj heug yu-fe-titg Daaib.
2.23: uaq taub mJavg txn zyrug kxvq, “tovb naaiq a'q. Buvq yaag yia Eei Buvq penj taaib. xq yaag yia Eei xq penj taaib. xij zu'g Tevj ninb Zwrtq Buaj heug msia'q txn, weig zu'g ninb yem mJavg txn Zwrtq taaib.”
2.6: Kuvj maaib uam yem Daub Diaq saamj Zwrtq taaib pun Dau Dxn kxmj Revg Navq.
2.2: Tauj ta'Zyetq Nxi Tinb huvb zruj zyavj ninb zruj Eei kov. ta'Zyetq Nxi ninb zyrug tivb kov hitq Kwrnj.
2.20: naaiq laanb myenb Tevj Zwrtq Rxib Euvb Euvg scvb Kuq Eei Buaj Zauj yem Daamb luvb Eei nx'g Zauj yetg zuvq yem lomg Eei Yiab zxib Eei Buaj, Zxg pwatg maiq maaib yetg taub Pwij ninb, Zauj ninb zruj txig Tevj ninb.
2.24: weig naaiq mJavg txn txv Jaa, leib ninb Eei tiaj maag, Zauj Jyenq ninb Eei auq kapq taaib. ninb Bua zyrug penj yetg taub mig a'q.
2.7: zyruq Tinb huvb cvj zx'q teij niab Buv nanq Zwrtq taub myenb taaib yaag pyomq maaib mcvg Eei Qiaj pia'g ninb Eei Ba'zxv. ninb zyrug penj maaib mcvg Eei myenb a'q.
2.19: zyruq Tinb huvb zyrug zx'q teij nia taaib nanq Euvb Euvg yem Dau Eei scvb Kuq Yiab zxib Zauj Euvb Euvg yem Daamb luvb Eei nx'g, zyrug txb taaib pun uaq laanb myenb mavg kaaj, haiq Euvg hxpg zu'g Zwrtq haiq Euvg Buaj. uaq laanb myenb Tevj naaiq teij maaib mcvg Eei ka'naaiq Zwrtq Buaj heug haiq Euvg, uaq Euvg ka'naaiq zyrug tu'q Buaj heug uaq Euvg a'q.
2.17: mq paag pun myenb hiuq tu'q lovj hiuq tu'q Zyruq uaq zuvb, Zinb maang maiq tuvq Eang. sij kxvq meib Eang nx, tovb uaq Nxi meib za'kevb xij zu'g taig a'q.”
2.11: ta'yetq Zaaj heug pi-son Daaib, lyrug kxmj haa-wi-laa teib puv. yem naaig maaib Jyem.
2.5: Dau maiq kcvb maaib haiq Euvg miaq Dyavj. maiq kcvb maaib haiq Euvg ka'naaib Eim ku'g Eaab Zwrtq, weig zu'g zyruq Tinb huvb maiq kcvb pun Byuvg Fiag Daub peib. yaag maiq kcvb maaib myenb zyrug maiq kcvb maaib haiq taub zruj livb zruj Deig.
2.9: zyruq Tinb huvb yaag pun Euvb Euvg Dyavj yem Dau Zwrtq taaib Rweig Eei, Kub mavg haig, maaib pyruq Kuq Eei weig zruj Eang hopq. Wivj Bu'Dovj maaib i zuvb Dyavj. maaib zuvb zyavb mcvg pyruq. maaib zuvb c'q, pun myenb hiuq tu'q lovj hiuq tu'q Zyruq Eei pyruq.
2.16: zyruq hatg ninb, “yem naaiq Wivj ka'Euad, haiq zuvb pyruq yaag Eang tu'q Eei.
2.4: zeij luvb zeij Dau Eei Jaub lrug se Navq naaiq.   zyruq Tinb huvb zeij luvb zeij Dau uaq zang,
2.10: e-Den teib puv maaib tiub Daaib lyrug pia'g mivb yuvd uaq nxm Wivj. Zwrtq zi'g e-Den uaq tiub Daaib zyrug pun zruj pyei Zaaj mig a'q.
2.22: zyruq Tinb huvb lovg yem mJavg txn zx'q Zwrtq uaq tiub la'scvj Buvq zruj penj taub msia'q txn, cvj txb taaib Tauj mJavg txn uaq.
2.12: (uaq nxm teib puv Eei Jyem zyen haig. cvj maaib Euvg Dyavb zuv Daav haig Zauj Euvg Jaaij haig Eei la'pyeib si'q Rweig Eei.)
2.15: zyruq Tinb huvb zyrug pun ninb zeij taaib uaq laanb myenb yem e-Den Wivj, pun ninb fyruj yaag kruj Jyenq.
2.13: ta'Eeig Zaaj heug ki-hon Daaib, lyrug kxmj Revg Kutq teib puv.
2.1: luvb Dau Zauj maang mwrtg Navq naaiq nx zeij zyavj Revg a'q.
2.25: naaiq taub mJavg txn Zauj ninb Eei auq lcvb kcvq Eei yem mq paag laanb maiq Eaiq laanb.

36.18: maaib e-saau Eei auq, o-ho-li-Baa-maa, Eei txn, ye-utg, yaa-laam Zauj Ko-laa. naaiq se yem e-saau Eei auq, aa-naa Eei sia'q, o-ho-li-Baa-maa, Zwrtq Eei pyeiq zeiq.
36.8: e-saau (se e-Dom) zyrug pyauj mivb yem sej-i teig Eei Bovb aiq txvj.
36.33: Be-laa kwei seij, cvj maaib yem Bo-saa-laa zivb taaib uaq taub ze-laa Eei txn, yo-Bapg, tu'q Ripg zruj huvb.
36.3: e-saau cvj lovg i-saa-maa-en Eei sia'q, ne-Baa-yotq Eei muag, Baa-sej-matq.
36.32: Be-o Eei txn, Be-laa, tu'q zruj e-Dom Eei huvb. ninb Eei tomb zivb heug Din-haa-Baa.
36.21: Di-son, e-se Zauj Di-saan. naaiq teij myenb se yem e-Dom teig, sej-i Eei zeib fun, ho-li myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq.
36.35: hu-saam kwei seij, cvj maaib Be-Datg Eei txn, haa-Datg, tu'q Ripg zruj huvb. haa-Datg tovb yem mo-apg teig Bx'q hivb mi-Dyen myenb uaq taub. ninb Eei tomb zivb heug aa-witq.
36.43: makq-Di-en, i-laam. naaiq se e-Dom Eei pyeiq zeiq ziuj ninb Bua yem Eei teig lyepg ninb Bua Eei vwaab kxn Eei txvj. naaiq se e-Dom myenb Eei ovb Taaij, e-saau, Eei zeib fun.
36.40: yem naaiq mivb se yem e-saau pun Fiag Eei pyeiq zeiq ziuj ninb Bua Eei Buaj, ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng Zauj ninb Bua yem Eei txvj. maaib Tim-naa, an-waa, ye-Tetq,
36.14: e-saau Eei auq, si-Be-on Eei txn, aa-naa, Eei sia'q, o-ho-li-Baa-maa, yuvd tu'q pua taub txn pun e-saau. maaib ye-utg, yaa-laam Zauj Ko-laa.
36.23: so-Baan Eei txn maaib an-waan, maa-naa-haatq, e-Baan, Qe-fo Zauj o-nam.
36.6: e-saau txb Jyenq ninb Eei auq, ninb Eei txn, ninb Eei sia'q, ninb Eei yetg zuvq pyauq zov myenb, vovb, yuvb, scvb Kuq Zauj yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv zxng taaib Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq zyrug Zauj ninb Eei yrud, yaa-Kopq, pun Gxi txig mivb yem kanb nxm teib puv.
36.34: yo-Bapg kwei seij, cvj maaib yem Te-maan teib puv taaib uaq taub hu-saam tu'q Ripg zruj huvb.
36.2: e-saau Eei auq se Kaa-naa-an teib puv Eei sia'q. maaib taub se hitq-Tai myenb, e-lon Eei sia'q, aa-Daa. maaib taub hi-wai myenb, si-Be-on, Eei fun, se aa-naa Eei sia'q, o-ho-li-Baa-maa.
36.36: haa-Datg kwei seij, cvj maaib yem matq-le-Kaa zivb taaib uaq taub samj-laa tu'q Ripg zruj huvb.
36.20: naaiq se yem uaq nxm teib puv Eei ho-li myenb, sej-i Eei txn. maaib lo-Taan, so-Baan, si-Be-on, aa-naa,
36.24: si-Be-on Eei txn maaib ai-yaa Zauj aa-naa. tovb naaiq taub aa-naa yem teib puvb Waav Tevj ninb Eei tia, si-Be-on, puvj lxb uaq zang pwatg zivq uamb Jxm.
36.28: Di-saan Eei txn maaib utg Zauj aa-lan.
36.7: ninb Bua i muad maaib Jaab tivb Zamq haig, Jwavg txvj yem maiq tu'q. txvb taaub hepg, maiq kauj yuvd ninb Bua Eei scvb Kuq.
36.29: naaiq se ho-li myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq. maaib lo-Taan, so-Baan, si-Be-on, aa-naa,
36.19: naaiq teij yetg zuvq se e-saau (tovb e-Dom) Eei txn Zauj yem e-saau Zwrtq taaib Eei pyeiq zeiq.
36.17: maaib e-saau Eei txn, le-u-en, Eei txn naa-hatg, ze-laa, sam-maa Zauj mitq-saa. naaiq se yem e-Dom teib puv kan le-u-en Zwrtq Eei pyeiq zeiq, se e-saau Eei auq, Baa-sej-matq, Eei fun.
36.38: saa-un kwei seij, akg-Bo Eei txn, Baa-an-haa-nan, tu'q Ripg zruj huvb.
36.31: zinb Daavg i-saa-laa-en myenb maiq kcvb maaib huvb tiaj kunq, e-Dom teib puv maaib huvb tiaj kunq Eei.
36.30: Di-son, e-se Zauj Di-saan. naaiq teij yetg zuvq se yem sej-i teib puv, ho-li myenb, ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng pyeiq zeiq.
36.27: e-se Eei txn maaib Bin-haan, saaj-waan Zauj aa-Kaanj.
36.11: e-li-fatq Eei txn maaib Te-maan, o-maa, sej-fo, kaa-Taam Zauj Ke-natq.
36.5: o-ho-li-Baa-maa yuvd tu'q ye-utg, yaa-laam Zauj Ko-laa. naaiq teij se e-saau Eei txn, yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv yuvd taaib.
36.9: yem naaiq mivb kxvq yem sej-i teig Eei Bovb aiq txvj, e-Dom myenb Eei ovb Taaij, e-saau, Eei zeib fun.
36.16: Ko-laa, kaa-Taam, Zauj aa-maa-lekq. naaiq se yem e-Dom teib puv kan e-li-fatq Zwrtq Eei pyeiq zeiq, se e-saau Eei auq, aa-Daa, Eei fun.
36.37: samj-laa kwei seij, cvj maaib yem yu-fe-titg Daaib Len Eei le-hoj-Botg zivb taaib uaq taub saa-un tu'q Ripg zruj huvb.
36.39: akg-Bo Eei txn, Baa-an-haa-nan, kwei seij, haa-Daa tu'q Ripg zruj huvb. ninb Eei tomb zivb heug paa-u. ninb Eei auq heug me-he-Taa-Ben. me-he-Taa-Ben zruj matq-letq Eei sia'q, me-saa-hapg Eei fun.
36.4: aa-Daa yuvd tu'q e-li-fatq pun e-saau. Baa-sej-matq yuvd tu'q le-u-en.
36.10: naaiq se e-saau Eei txn Eei Buaj. maaib e-saau Eei auq, aa-Daa, Eei txn, e-li-fatq, Zauj e-saau Eei auq, Baa-sej-matq, Eei txn, le-u-en.
36.22: lo-Taan Eei txn maaib ho-li Zauj ho-mam. lo-Taan Eei muag heug Tim-naa.
36.12: e-saau Eei txn, e-li-fatq, cvj maaib taub aub txn, Buaj heug Tim-naa. Tim-naa yuvd tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug aa-maa-lekq, pun e-li-fatq. naaiq teij txn yetg zuvq zruj e-saau Eei auq, aa-Daa, Eei fun.
36.15: naaiq se e-saau Eei zeib fun zruj pyeiq zeiq Eei myenb. maaib e-saau Eei txnb Lo, e-li-fatq Eei txn, Te-maan, o-maa, sej-fo, Ke-natq,
36.13: le-u-en Eei txn maaib naa-hatg, ze-laa, sam-maa Zauj mitq-saa. naaiq se e-saau Eei auq, Baa-sej-matq, Eei fun.
36.1: yem naaiq mivb kxvq e-saau Eei zeib fun. e-saau cvj maaib nxm Buaj heug e-Dom.
36.26: Di-son Eei txn maaib hem-Daan, etg-Baan, itg-laan Zauj Ke-laan.
36.25: aa-naa Eei txn heug Di-son. aa-naa yaag maaib taub sia'q heug o-ho-li-Baa-maa.

35.18: laa-sen aaq lamb taig uaq zang, ninb cvj Tauq Zwrtq Rung Qiaj, Tevj ninb Eei txn Zwrtq Buaj heug Ben-o-ni. mq paag yaa-Kopq Zwrtq Buaj heug Ben-yaa-min.
35.8: tovb zinb Daavg txb le-Be-Kaa Lo taaib uaq taub pru, De-Bo-laa, kwei seij mig a'q. ninb Bua zyrug zavj Jyenq yem Betg-en Eei naamb puv, yetg tiub tomb Ba'ov zwei Dyavb kxn Len. uaq tiub Dyavj ninb Bua Zwrtq nxm Buaj heug an-lon-Baa-Kutq.
35.3: Bua xij zu'g leib Gxi naaiq nxm txvj mivb yem Betg-en. Tauj uaq yia xij Zeij nxm ziab txvb weig Tinb huvb, tovb zinb Daavg yia pwavb zu'g Kruq naang ninb Tevj yia, yia mivb Tauj haaij ninb yaag Zauj yia mivb, uaq taub Tinb huvb.”
35.21: i-saa-laa-en Bua cvj swiq mivb Zxv Dopg liub yem e-De fanb Taapq Eei uaq Daavg mcvj.
35.14: yaa-Kopq zx'q nxm la'pyeiq ton Jyenq Tinb huvb Zauj ninb kxvq waag Eei txvj, yaag zx'q a'vung tiuq Ziaq tovg kub vwaaig, yaag zx'q ka'lanq yrub toj Jyenq.
35.23: le-aa Eei txn maaib lu-Ben. lu-Ben se yaa-Kopq Eei txnb Lo. cvj maaib si-me-on, le-wi, yu-Daa, itg-saaj-Kaa, Zauj sej-Bu-lun.
35.6: yaa-Kopq Zauj yetg zuvq kan ninb Eei myenb mivb Tauj Kaa-naa-an teib puv, lutq zivb, (se Betg-en zivb).
35.2: yaa-Kopq zyrug Buaj ninb Eei Mwavq txig cvj Zauj ninb yem uaq teij myenb, “meib Bua maaib kanb fivj Eei haiq Euvg miub favj xij zu'g kwavg Tauj Revg. xij zu'g saaj Revg wij, yeng lwib hruj.
35.20: yaa-Kopq zx'q nxm la'pyeiq ton Jyenq laa-sen Eei zruq zruj Javb hog. uaq nxm la'pyeiq yem Tauj ib Jaaj Nxi.
35.24: laa-sen Eei txn maaib yo-sepq Zauj Ben-yaa-min.
35.28: i-sakg zyavb tu'q yetg pc'q petq zyepg Havj.
35.7: Tauj uaq ninb Zeij nxm ziab txvb taaib cvj Zwrtq uaq nxm txvj Eei Buaj heug en-Betg-en, weig zu'g pyauj ninb Eei kxj, e-saau, uaq zang, Tinb huvb yem uaq hing Zwrtq pun ninb pwatg.
35.29: ninb zyavb tu'q syrug Ewrnb Daauq, Havb Jeiq koj haig, zyrug tavj Qiaj, kwei seij mig a'q. ninb Eei i taub txn, e-saau Zauj yaa-Kopq, txb ninb Eei sei mivb zavj.
35.19: laa-sen taig mig a'q, zavj Jyenq mivb e-faa-laa-Taa Eei Jaub Len. (e-faa-laa-Taa cvj maaib nxm Buaj heug Betg-le-hem.)
35.17: mun Kruq Jiaj Eei zyavb hog, kruj ninb uaq taub msia'q txn kxvq, “meib maiq tuvq kamb Riaj og. naaiq taub kub vwaad se txn.”
35.27: yaa-Kopq Rwrnj Tauj ninb Eei tia, i-sakg, yem mam-le, nitq Ki-li-yaatq-aan-Baa, (se he-Bo-lon, tovb zinb Daavg apg-laa-ham Zauj i-sakg yem Eei txvj).
35.11: Tinb huvb cvj kxvq, “yia se nrnb Jiaj Eei Tinb huvb. meib xij zu'g maaib fu'Jweiq Zamq. meib Eei zeib fun xij Yaavj taaib penj yetg fivj Zauj Zamb kua'q Eei fivj. maaib teij meib Eei zeib fun yaag xij tu'q zruj huvb.
35.5: yaa-Kopq Zauj kan ninb Eei zwavj myenb Zwrtq Jauq mivb uaq zang, Tinb huvb pun Wiv Rwrnj uaq teij zivb Eei myenb kamb Riaj haig, zyrug maiq zung yaa-Kopq Eei txn Bua.
35.9: yaa-Kopq yem patg-Daan-aa-lam teig Rwrnj taaib, Tinb huvb cvj hing Zwrtq Rung, pwav waag pun ninb.
35.16: yaa-Kopq Bua yem Betg-en Zwrtq Jauq mivb. Zxg leib e-faa-laa-Taa muvq ko teij Eei, laa-sen Tauj zyavb hog Dutq sin. ninb mun Kruq, a'g tu'q yuvd haig.
35.4: ninb Bua yetg zuvq zyrug zx'q ninb Bua maaib Eei kanb fivj myenb Eei miub favj Zauj tavb Jyenq Eei mnxmb Yun, Jiu pun yaa-Kopq. yaa-Kopq zyrug pyopq Jyenq tomb Ba'ov zwei Dyavb kxn Diaq, leib se-Kem zivb maiq navg ko.
35.10: Tinb huvb Buaj ninb, “meib Eei Buaj heug yaa-Kopq mq paag yavb naaiq Jiaj meib Eei Buaj xij zu'g kxiq heug i-saa-laa-en.” Navq naaiq ninb zyrug tu'q Buaj heug i-saa-laa-en.
35.22: yem kau uaq nxm teib puv, i-saa-laa-en Eei txn, lu-Ben, Zauj ninb Eei maab faij, Bin-haa, maaib Jauq. ninb Eei tia hiuq mig a'q. yaa-Kopq maaib zyepg Eeig taub txn.
35.12: yia Jiu pun apg-laa-ham Zauj i-sakg Eei teib puv, yia yaag Jiu pun meib Zauj meib Eei hod txig zeib fun.”
35.15: ninb cvj Zwrtq uaq nxm txvj Eei Buaj heug Betg-en.
35.13: kxvq liud, Tinb huvb zyrug yem uaq nxm txvj faauj mivb mig a'q.
35.1: Tinb huvb kxvq Buaj yaa-Kopq, “ib zang meib xij zu'g swiq mivb yem Betg-en. yem uaq xij zu'g Zeij nxm ziab txvb weig yia, tovb zinb Daavg meib pyauj meib Eei kxj, e-saau, uaq zang hing Zwrtq taaib pun meib pwatg Eei Tinb huvb.”
35.26: le-aa Eei nrub peid, sinj-paa, Eei txn maaib kaatg Zauj aa-se. naaiq teij yetg zuvq txn, yaa-Kopq yem patg-Daan-aa-lam tu'q taaib.
35.25: laa-sen Eei nrub peid, Bin-haa, Eei txn maaib Daan Zauj napq-Taa-li.

24.18: uaq taub sia'q kxvq, “tomb kxj aag, kunq hopq maa'b!” sia'q zyrug puvj niab ha'lrub Fiag Ba'taub, prub Jyenq pun ninb hopq.
24.45: “yia yem Hruq tauj kauj zuvq maiq kcvb setq, le-Be-Kaa zyrug Daam Jyenq niab ha'lrub Zwrtq taaib. ninb Fiag Tauj uamb zivq zaavb uam, yia zyrug Buaj ninb, ‘Toq teij uam hopq og.’
24.3: yia xij meib zyavq Jyenq zyruq, tovb luvb Zauj Dau Eei Tinb huvb, lcvd waag meib maiq lxd ib zang yia yem Jyenq Eei Kaa-naa-an myenb Bu'Dovj Eei sia'q zruj yia Eei txn Eei auq.
24.66: uaq taub pru zyrug kxvq Revg ninb Eei Jaub lrug pun i-sakg mwavj.
24.43: ib zang yia sruq Jyenq naaiq uamb zivq Len. maaib taub sia'q Zwrtq taaib zaavb uam yia xij kxvq, “Toq teij meib Eei niab ha'lrub Eei uam hopq og.”
24.50: laa-Baan Zauj Be-Tu-en tau, “naaiq teij Jauq se yem zyruq taaib. yia Bua maiq haib Zauj meib kxvq lovj fai Zyruq.
24.14: yia xij Zauj taub sia'q kxvq, ‘Toq meib puvj meib naaig niab ha'lrub Fiag pun teij uam yia hopq og.’ sij kxvq uaq taub sia'q kxvq, ‘tomb kxj aag, kunq hopq maa'b! yia Zxg cvj xij pun uam meib Eei lxb Txb hopq’ nx, yia zyrug hiuq tu'q meib kinq uaq taub taaib zruj meib Eei pru, i-sakg, Eei auq a'q. sij kxvq Navq naaiq nx, yia hiuq tu'q meib za'kevb zruj lovj pun yia Eei zyruq.”
24.48: yia yaag kweig Fiag paaij zyruq. yia Zev zyruq, yia Eei zyruq, apg-laa-ham, Eei Tinb huvb. ninb txb yia mivb tu'q zu'g Jauq, pun yia lxd tu'q yia Eei zyruq Eei yrud Eei sia'g fun zruj yia Eei zyruq Eei Bwavd.
24.34: uaq taub pru kxvq, “yia se apg-laa-ham Eei pru.
24.2: apg-laa-ham Buaj ninb Havb Jeiq kaub koj Jiaj uaq taub pru, tovb Tevj ninb kruj Revg Jaab tivb uaq taub, “txb meib Eei puad taaib an Jyenq yia Eei Zamb zwib ka'Diaq mcvj.
24.36: yia Eei zyruq Eei auq, saa-laa, Havb Jeiq koj Eei zyavb hog, yuvd tu'q taub txn pun yia Eei zyruq. yia Eei zyruq maaib Eei Euvb Euvg ninb Jiu pun uaq taub txn mig a'q.
24.35: zyruq za'kevb Zeij fu'q yia Eei zyruq, apg-laa-ham, Zamq haig, pun ninb putq zxib haig, maaib vovb, maaib pa'ki yuvb, maaib yuvb Zamq, yaag maaib Jyem maaib Eaanb, maaib nrub kauq nrub peid, maaib lxb Txb Zauj lxb.
24.24: sia'q tau, “yia Be-Tu-en Eei sia'q. yia Eei ov heug naa-ho. kuj heug min-Kaa.”
24.61: le-Be-Kaa Zauj ninb Eei msia'q pru Bua Beng Rxib ka'naaiq, keb Jyenq lxb Txb kan Jyenq apg-laa-ham Eei pru Rwrnj. uaq taub pru zyrug Zwrtq Jauq txb Jyenq le-Be-Kaa mivb a'q.
24.67: i-sakg zyrug txb Jyenq le-Be-Kaa pia'g i-sakg Eei maa, saa-laa, Eei Dopg liub. le-Be-Kaa zyrug penj i-sakg Eei auq mig a'q. i-sakg yaag Namq haig ninb. i-sakg zyrug tu'q auq taaib Tevj Jaiq ninb Eei maa taig mivb Eei yrub Raub.
24.7: luvb zavg Eei Tinb huvb uaq taub zyruq, txb yia leib Gxi yia Eei tia Eei pyauq, kwavg Jyenq yia Zwrtq seij Eei teib puv. ninb yaag Zauj yia lcvd vcvg waag. ninb kxvq, ‘yia xij zx'q naaiq nxm teib puv pun meib Eei zeib fun.’ zyruq xij Paaiq ninb Eei finb myenb mivb Daavg, meib zyrug haib tu'q taub uaq nxm teib puv Eei sia'q zruj yia Eei Bwavd.
24.17: apg-laa-ham Eei pru zyrug Tiuj Jyenq mivb Tauj sia'q Eei ka'Len kxvq, “Toq pun teij meib naaig niab ha'lrub Eei uam yia hopq og.”
24.58: ninb Bua zyrug heug le-Be-Kaa taaib naaig, “meib za'kevb xij kan naaiq taub mJavg txn mivb Eei fai?” sia'q tau, “mivb Eei.”
24.49: ib zang sij kxvq meib a'Neiq zyepg zua'q Eei zruj txij yia Eei zyruq Eei waag, Toq Buaj yia. meib maiq xij zruj nx, Toq Buaj yia, yia Zivj hiuq tu'q xij zu'g Navq haiq nx zruj.”
24.11: Tauj zivb ka'Eiag mcvj, ninb pun lxb Txb kweig Fiag uamb Kwrtq Len. uaq zang luvb maanb Mwavj a'q, txij zu'g msia'q txn Zwrtq taaib zaavb uam Eei zyavb hog.
24.33: Beng zyavj Naavj, heug apg-laa-ham Eei pru Eang mq paag ninb kxvq, “yia maiq kcvb Eang og. zuaq yia kxvq Revg yia taaib Eei Jaub lrug Zivj Eang.” laa-Baan kxvq, “maaib haiq Euvg, kunq kxvq maa'b!”
24.16: naaiq taub sia'q zyavb tu'q Rweig haig yaag maiq kcvb Ryaaug Jiaj txn. ninb Fiag Tauj uamb zivq zaavb uam pwavq ha'lrub cvj faauj taaib.
24.40: “yia Eei zyruq tau, ‘tovb yia pua'g zavg Eei zyruq xij Paaiq ninb Eei finb myenb Zauj meib mivb Tevj meib zruj tu'q zyavj ziuj meib Zwrtq Jauq zruj Eei kov. meib xij zu'g lxd taub yia Eei Zyenb Ze'q Eei sia'q, yia Eei tia Eei zruq zavg myenb, pun yia Eei txn lovg zruj auq.
24.59: ninb Bua zyrug pun le-Be-Kaa Zauj txb le-Be-Kaa Lo taaib uaq taub pru kan apg-laa-ham Eei pru Bua mivb.
24.37: yia Eei zyruq heug yia Zauj ninb lcvd Jiaj vcvg waag kxvq, ‘maiq tuvq lxd tovb ib zang yem Jyenq naaiq nxm Kaa-naa-an teib puv Eei sia'q pun yia Eei txn lovg zruj auq.
24.4: xij zu'g Rwrnj yia Eei lob teib puv, yia Eei Zyenb Ze'q uaq, Tevj yia Eei txn, i-sakg, kxvq auq.”
24.51: le-Be-Kaa mtaaib yem naaiq Eei. kunq txb ninb mivb zruj meib Eei zyruq Eei Bwavd a'q, Navq zyruq Tinb huvb kxvq nx.”
24.62: i-sakg yem Be-e-laa-hai-lxi teib puvb Waav Rwrnj weig zu'g uaq zang ninb yem ne-kepg.
24.12: uaq taub pru tauj kauj kxvq, “o zyruq, yia Eei zyruq, apg-laa-ham, Eei Tinb huvb aa'b! Toq Tevj yia ib Nxi zruj tu'q zyavj yia lcvd Eei waag. Toq meib yaag zruj lovj pun yia Eei zyruq, apg-laa-ham.
24.46: “ninb zyrug syepg syepq Eei puvj niab ha'lrub Fiag Ba'taub yaag kxvq, ‘kunq hopq maa'b! yia cvj zaavb uam pun meib Eei lxb Txb hopq.’ yia zyrug hopq. ninb cvj zaavb uam pun lxb Txb hopq.
24.13: yia sruq Jyenq naaiq uamb zivq Len. yem naaiq nxm zivb Eei sia'q ib zang Zwrtq taaib zaavb uam.
24.26: uaq taub pru zyrug kweig Fiag Dau paaij zyruq.
24.28: sia'q Tiuj Jyenq Rwrnj mivb, zx'q naaiq teij Jaub lrug Buaj ninb Eei maa Zauj pyauq zov myenb.
24.54: apg-laa-ham Eei pru pun liud, ninb Zauj kan ninb taaib Eei myenb zyrug Eang Naavj a'q. Eang liud hopq liud, ninb Bua pweij mwrnd uaq. ta'Eeig Dxm Jiad sin taaib, uaq taub pru kxvq, “Toq pun yia Rwrnj yia Eei zyruq uaq og.”
24.63: maaib Nxi luvb maanb Mwavj, i-sakg Zwrtq mivb saau uaq Deig. ninb Zau Myen pwatg kwanb lxb Txb huvj Jyenq taaib.
24.8: sij kxvq uaq taub sia'q maiq lcvd Zauj meib taaib naaiq, yia pun meib lcvd liud Eei vcvg waag Jiaj mig a'q. mq paag meib Zinb maang maiq tuvq txb yia Eei txn Rwrnj uaq nxm teib puv og.”
24.9: uaq taub pru zyrug txb ninb Eei puad an Jyenq ninb Eei zyruq, apg-laa-ham, Eei Zamb zwib ka'Diaq mcvj hruq Jyenq lcvd ei naaiq teij waag zruj.
24.32: uaq taub pru zyrug pia'g pyauq mig a'q. laa-Baan prub lxb Txb Eei txj Fiag, cvj zx'q Byaub Gaauq zx'q miaq pun lxb Txb Eang. ninb lxd uam pun apg-laa-ham Eei pru Zauj kan apg-laa-ham Eei pru taaib Eei myenb Raauj zauj.
24.21: uaq taub pru sruq Jyenq uaq maiq Ko lo, samj mavg kaaj, zyruq Tevj ninb zruj zyavj ziuj ninb Zwrtq taaib zruj Eei kov fai ni?
24.64: le-Be-Kaa yaag Zau Myen pwatg i-sakg zyrug Fiag lxb Txb taaib
24.57: ninb Bua tau, “uaq Euvg, heug sia'q taaib naaig kaaj ninb Navq haiq nx kxvq.”
24.23: uaq taub pru naaig, “Toq Buaj yia, meib haiq taub Eei sia'q? meib Eei tia Eei pyauq maaib txvj pun yia Bua pweij mwrnd fai?”
24.6: apg-laa-ham kxvq, “Zinb maang maiq tuvq fuvj yia Eei txn Rwrnj uaq nxm teib puv.
24.55: sia'q Eei kxj Zauj ninb Eei maa kxvq, “Toq pun sia'q Zauj yia Bua yem zyepg paaq Nxi liud, Ga'haaq mivb tu'q Eei.”
24.44: sij kxvq ninb kxvq, “kunq hopq maa'b! yia yaag xij zaavb uam pun meib Eei lxb Txb hopq” nx, yia zyrug hiuq tu'q tovb uaq taub sia'q zyruq tivg taaib zruj yia Eei zyruq Eei txn Eei auq.’
24.20: ninb zyrug kaanq Jyenq toj niab ha'lrub Eei uam an uaq zob pun lxb Txb hopq. cvj Tiuj mivb uamb Kwrtq uaq zaavb uam pun ninb Eei taub taub lxb Txb hopq.
24.5: pru naaig kaaj, “sij kxvq sia'q maiq Kavq kan yia taaib naaiq nxm teib puv ni? yia xij zu'g fuvj meib Eei txn Rwrnj meib Zwrtq taaib uaq nxm teib puv saa'b?”
24.56: uaq taub pru kxvq, “Toq meib Bua maiq tuvq zxq yia weig zu'g zyruq Tevj yia zruj suv yia Eei Jauq mig a'q. Toq pun yia Rwrnj yia Eei zyruq uaq a'q.”
24.53: ninb yaag zx'q lovg Jyem lovg Eaanb taaq taaib Eei syrub setq Zauj lwib hruj pun le-Be-Kaa. ninb cvj zx'q Jaaij Eei zivb Eeig pun sia'q Eei kxj Zauj maa.
24.19: ninb hopq liud uam, sia'q cvj kxvq, “yia Zxg xij mivb zaavb uam pun meib Eei lxb Txb hopq peuq.”
24.38: xij zu'g Rwrnj yia Eei tia Eei zruq zavg myenb Zauj yia Eei Zyenb Ze'q Tevj yia Eei txn lxd taub sia'q zruj auq.’+”
24.31: laa-Baan kxvq, “taaib og. meib se zyruq Zeij fu'q Eei myenb. meib fuvg sruq Jyenq ka'Eiag Navq? yia zuvq liug leid pyauq yaag liug leid zyavj lxb Txb yem Eei txvj.”
24.52: apg-laa-ham Eei pru haid ninb Bua Eei waag zyrug Pua'q Fiag Dau paaij zyruq.
24.65: naaig kaaj apg-laa-ham Eei pru, “yem uaq Deig huvj Jyenq Bua taaib uaq taub myenb se haiq taub?” uaq taub pru kxvq, “ninb zruj yia Eei zyruq.” le-Be-Kaa zyrug zx'q Kwaaiq Dia pwav Jyenq kanb Eei Myen.
24.27: ninb kxvq, “Zev zyruq, yia Eei zyruq, apg-laa-ham, Eei Tinb huvb. zyruq maiq kwavg lcvd Jiaj Eei vcvg waag, zuvq zyepg zua'q Eei zruj lovj pun yia Eei zyruq. yia kanb c'q, zyruq txb Jauq Tauj yia Eei zyruq, apg-laa-ham, Eei Zyenb Ze'q Eei pyauq.”
24.60: ninb Bua pwav waag le-Be-Kaa, kxvq Buaj ninb, “yia Bua Eei muag aag, Toq pun meib zruj ziaj Zin ziaj waang myenb Eei maa. Toq pun meib Eei zeib fun haib tu'q Ripg ninb Bua Eei winb wavq Eei zivb.”
24.41: meib mivb Tauj yia Eei Zyenb Ze'q uaq, meib Zauj yia lcvd Eei vcvg waag zyrug Jiaj mig a'q. maiq kunq ninb Bua maiq pun sia'q meib, meib Zauj yia lcvd Eei vcvg waag Jiaj mig a'q.’+”
24.1: apg-laa-ham Eei Havb Jeiq Lav, koj haig a'q. yem ninb zruj Eei Euvb Euvg zyruq yaag Zeij fu'q pun ninb.
24.39: “yia cvj naaig kaaj yia Eei zyruq, ‘sij kxvq uaq taub sia'q maiq Kavq kan yia taaib ni?’+”
24.47: “yia cvj naaig ninb, ‘meib haiq taub Eei sia'q?’ “ninb tau, ‘yia Be-Tu-en Eei sia'q. yia Eei ov heug naa-ho. kuj heug min-Kaa.’ “yia zyrug zx'q Ba'zxvb Yun tavb Jyenq ninb Eei Ba'zxv, cvj zx'q Jyemb tavb Jyenq ninb Eei puad.
24.10: uaq taub pru zyrug txb Jyenq zyepg taub ninb Eei zyruq Eei lxb Txb Zauj ziaj Euvg maaib Jaab zinb Eei ka'naaiq Zwrtq Jauq mivb me-soj-po-te-mia teig, naa-ho Eei zivb.
24.25: ninb cvj kxvq, “yia Bua Eei pyauq maaib miaq maaib Byaub Gaauq Zamq Eei wij scvb Kuq. yaag maaib txvj pun meib pweij.”
24.22: lxb Txb hopq liud uam, uaq taub pru zx'q nxm Jyemb Ba'zxvb Yun, Niab taaub yetg zinb faamb pwrn, cvj zx'q txij Jyem Eei Jyemb, Niab taaub faamb luvd, pun uaq taub sia'q.
24.42: “ib Nxi yia Tauj uaq uamb Kwrtq Len, yia tauj kauj kxvq, ‘zyruq, yia Eei zyruq, apg-laa-ham, Eei Tinb huvb aa'b! Toq Tevj yia zruj zyavj yia Zwrtq Jauq taaib zruj Eei kov.
24.15: tauj kauj zuvq maiq kcvb setq, maaib taub sia'q, Buaj heug le-Be-Kaa, Daam Jyenq niab ha'lrub Zwrtq taaib. le-Be-Kaa se Be-Tu-en Eei sia'q. le-Be-Kaa Eei kuj heug min-Kaa. min-Kaa zruj naa-ho Eei auq. naa-ho zruj apg-laa-ham Eei yrud.
24.29: le-Be-Kaa maaib taub kxj, Buaj heug laa-Baan. laa-Baan kaanq Jyenq mivb uaq uamb zivq lxd uaq taub myenb.
24.30: laa-Baan pwatg liud ninb Eei muag tavb Jyenq Eei Ba'zxvb Yun Zauj puab Jyemb, yaag haid ninb kxvq Revg uaq taub myenb kxvq Eei waag, ninb zyrug Zwrtq mivb lxd uaq taub myenb. pwatg ninb sruq Jyenq lxb Txb ka'Len nitq uamb zivq.

7.18: uam pwavq Jyenq faauj, Ravq Byrub Jyenq uamb ming mivb.
7.8: maaib wij fai maiq maaib wij Eei scvb Kuq Zauj nx'g Zauj Exv Daub peib Eei ka'naaiq
7.3: yem Daamb luvb Eei nx'g yetg Euvg xij zu'g txb siag txij, yetg txij maaib nxm kxvj maaib nxm Eeid. xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx siaj Zwrtq nx'g Zauj scvb Kuq Eei mcvg weig pun yem luvb Diaq trug pwrnq.
7.21: Euvb Euvg yem Daub peib maaib mcvg, haib tovd Eei ka'naaiq, se nx'g Zauj scvb Kuq Yiab zxib, haib Exv Dau Eei ka'naaiq Zauj myenb maanb taig Revg mig a'q.
7.14: ninb Bua txb Euvb Euvg Yiab zxib, Euvb Euvg scvb Kuq Zauj Euvb Euvg Exv Daub peib Eei ka'naaiq. ninb Bua yaag txb Euvb Euvg nx'g, se yetg zuvq maaib Daatq Eei ka'naaiq, yetg Euvg ziuj yetg Euvg Eei pwrnq.
7.23: yem Daub peib maaib mcvg Eei ka'naaiq yetg zuvq zu'g kwaatq zu'g myetg Revg. lyemb myenb maanb, scvb Kuq, haib Exv Dau Eei ka'naaiq Zauj yem Daamb luvb Eei nx'g zu'g kwaatq zu'g myetg Revg. Kuvj zevg no-yaa cvj Zauj ninb yem Ravq ka'Euad uaq teij Navq.
7.6: Byuvb swib imj yemj luvb Diaq uaq zang, no-yaa tu'q lua'g pc'q Havj.
7.2: ta'faanb maiq maaib wij Eei scvb Kuq, xij zu'g txb yetg Euvg siag txij, siag taub kruq siag taub Eeid, pia'g Ravq. maaib wij Eei scvb Kuq xij zu'g txb yetg Euvg yetg txij, yetg taub kruq yetg taub Eeid.
7.20: Zxg cvj yemj faauj zi'g Bovb nivq zyepg Mmd Dx'g.
7.24: uam yemj Jyenq luvb Diaq yetg pc'q Mmd zyepg Nxi.
7.7: ninb Zauj ninb Eei aub Jweiq txnb Bwavd pia'g Ravq mivb pyauj Dutq Byuvb swib imj yemj.
7.19: uam pwavq Jyenq faauj Tauj yemj Revg luvb Diaq Lav Jiaj Eei Bovb nivq.
7.17: Byuvb swib imj yemj Jyenq Dau faauj feij zyepg Nxi. uam pwavq Jyenq faauj, Ravq zyrug yem Daub peib Byrub Jyenq faauj.
7.11: no-yaa pwavq lua'g pc'q Havj uaq Havj, Eeig Laaj zyepg Zyetq uaq Nxi, Daub Diaq Eei uamb zivq Beuj Zwrtq, luvb Eei kcvb yetg zuvq Gxi,
7.5: no-yaa zyrug ei Jyenq zyruq Paaiq Eei waag zruj zyavj Revg.
7.9: yetg txij yetg txij Eei, maaib taub kruq maaib taub Eeid, taaib Zauj no-yaa pia'g Ravq ei Tinb huvb Paaiq Eei waag.
7.16: taaib pia'g Ravq Eei Euvb Euvg scvb Kuq, maaib taub kruq maaib taub Eeid, ziuj Tinb huvb Paaiq no-yaa Eei waag. zyruq kanb zyrug kwrn Jyenq Ravq Eei kcvb.
7.4: yem naaiq mivb siag Nxi Navq, yia xij pun luvb twib Byuvg feij zyepg Nxi feij zyepg mwrnd. yia yaag xij zx'q yia zeij taaib yem Daub peib maaib mcvg Eei Euvb Euvg ka'naaiq myetg Revg.”
7.10: Jiaj liud siag Nxi, Byuvb swib imj yemj luvb Diaq a'q.
7.22: ta'faanb yem Daub peib maaib mcvg, haib Tauq Qiaj Eei ka'naaiq taig Revg mig a'q.
7.12: twib tomb Byuvg Fiag feij zyepg Nxi feij zyepg mwrnd.
7.15: yetg zuvq maaib mcvg Eei ka'naaiq, yetg Euvg maaib yetg Euvg Eei txij, taaib Zauj no-yaa pia'g Ravq.
7.13: tovb uaq Nxi, no-yaa Zauj ninb Eei pua taub txn, sem, haam Zauj yaa-fetq Zauj no-yaa Eei auq Zauj ninb Eei pua taub Bwavd pia'g Ravq.
7.1: zyruq kxvq Buaj no-yaa, “meib Zauj meib Eei yetg pyauq Mwavq txig xij zu'g pia'g Ravq a'q. yem naaiq Jaaj luvb Diaq yia pwatg Kuvj meib kanb Navq zruj tu'q hxpg yia Eei Hruq.

17.18: ninb Buaj Tinb huvb, “o Toq meib Zeij fu'q pun i-saa-maa-en.”
17.8: tovb meib ib zang yem Jyenq penj kanb fivj myenb naaiq nxm teib puv, se Kaa-naa-an Eei yetg zuvq teib puv, yia xij Jiu pun meib, pun meib Zauj meib Eei zeib fun yetg liud tu'q Ripg. yia yaag xij zruj ninb Bua Eei Tinb huvb.”
17.3: apg-laam zyrug Pua'q Fiag Dau. Tinb huvb kxvq Buaj ninb,
17.21: mq paag yia lyepg Eei vcvg waag, yia xij Zauj i-sakg lyepg, tovb saa-laa Tauj ta'Eeig Havj naaiq nxm zyavb hog xij yuvd uaq taub.”
17.14: haiq taub mJavg txn maiq Jiaj kaatq Eei leid zyrug yem ninb Eei myenb Bu'Dovj zu'g Pai kwavg, laaij ninb maiq ei yia Eei vcvg waag.”
17.23: tovb uaq Nxi apg-laa-ham ei Jyenq Tinb huvb Eei waag zruj. ninb Tevj ninb Eei txn, i-saa-maa-en, Zauj yem ninb Eei pyauq zov taub taub mJavg txn, maiq kunq yem ninb Eei pyauq Zwrtq seij fai lovg Eaanb Tevj kanb fivj maaid Eei, yetg zuvq mJavg txn Jiaj kaatq Eei leid Revg a'q.
17.6: yia xij pun meib Eei zeib fun Yaavj Zamq taaib, zuvq penj ziaj fivj myenb, yaag maaib Zamb taub huvb yem meib Zwrtq taaib.
17.2: yia xij Zauj meib lyepg vcvg waag yaag xij pun meib Eei zeib fun Yaavj Jyenq faauj Zamq.”
17.20: mq paag yia haid meib Tevj i-saa-maa-en Toq, yia zyrug Zeij fu'q pun ninb yaag pun ninb maaib zeib fun Yaavj taaib Zamq. ninb xij zruj zyepg Eeig taub pyeiq zeiq Eei tia. yia yaag xij pun ninb Eei zeib fun penj yetg kua'q Lo Eei.
17.24: Jiaj kaatq Eei leid uaq zang apg-laa-ham tu'q Juaq zyepg Juaq Havj.
17.7: yia Zauj meib cvj Zauj meib txig Jiaj txig Eei zeib fun lyepg Jiad vcvg waag, penj yetg liud Eei vcvg waag. se yia lcvd zruj meib Eei Tinb huvb yaag zruj meib Eei hod txig zeib fun Eei Tinb huvb.
17.19: Tinb huvb tau, “maiq zeid. se meib Eei auq, saa-laa kanb, xij yuvd taub txn pun meib. meib xij zu'g Tevj ninb Zwrtq Buaj heug i-sakg. yia xij Zauj ninb lyepg vcvg waag, se Zauj ninb Eei hod txig zeib fun lyepg yetg liud Eei vcvg waag.
17.17: apg-laa-ham Pua'q Fiag Dau Jyetq Jyenq yem Hruq Namq, “tu'q yetg pc'q Havj Eei mJavg txn Zxg haib maaib fu'Jweiq fai ni? saa-laa tu'q Juaq zyepg Havj ninb Zxg haib maaib kub vwaad Eei?”
17.27: ninb Eei pyauq zov yetg zuvq mJavg txn, se yem ninb Eei pyauq Zwrtq seij fai lovg Eaanb Tevj kanb fivj maaid taaib Eei myenb, Zauj apg-laa-ham Bua yetg Fiag Jiaj kaatq Eei leid.
17.11: meib xij zu'g Jiaj kaatq Eei leid weig zruj yia Zauj meib lyepg vcvg waag Eei Javb hog.
17.5: yavb naaiq Jiaj meib Eei Buaj maiq heug apg-laam a'q. meib Eei Buaj xij zu'g heug apg-laa-ham, weig zu'g yia pun meib zruj Zamb fivj myenb Eei ovb Taaib vc'q.
17.9: Tinb huvb kxvq Buaj apg-laa-ham, “meib kanb cvj Zauj meib Eei hod txig zeib fun xij zu'g txig Jiaj txig ei Jyenq yia Eei vcvg waag.
17.16: yia xij Zeij fu'q pun ninb, zuvq xij pun ninb yuvd taub txn pun meib. yia xij Zeij fu'q ninb, pun ninb zruj Zamb fivj myenb Eei mkuj Taaij vc'q. yaag xij maaib Zamb fivj myenb Eei huvb yem ninb Zwrtq.”
17.4: “naaiq se yia Zauj meib lyepg Eei vcvg waag. meib zyrug zruj Zamb fivj myenb Eei ovb Taaib vc'q.
17.10: naaiq se yia Zauj meib cvj Zauj meib Eei hod txig zeib fun lyepg Eei vcvg waag, tovb meib Bua xij zu'g ei Jyenq Eei vcvg waag. yem meib Bua ka'Euad Eei taub taub mJavg txn xij zu'g Jiaj kaatq Eei leid.
17.22: Tinb huvb Zauj apg-laa-ham kxvq liud naaiq teij waag, Tinb huvb zyrug leib Gxi ninb mig a'q.
17.12: meib txig Jiaj txig Eei mJavg txn, ta'faanb kub vwaab txn Zwrtq seij taaib tu'q Yetg Nxi uaq Nxi xij zu'g Jiaj kaatq Eei leid. lyemb yem meib Eei pyauq zov Zwrtq seij Eei Zauj lovg Eaanb Tevj kanb fivj maaid taaib Eei myenb, se maiq zeid meib Bua kanb Eei Zyen zeib fun, xij zu'g Jiaj kaatq Eei leid.
17.15: Tinb huvb cvj kxvq Buaj apg-laa-ham, “meib Eei auq, saa-laai, yem naaiq mivb maiq heug saa-laai a'q. xij zu'g heug saa-laa.
17.13: maiq kunq yem meib Eei pyauq zov Zwrtq seij fai lovg meib Eei Eaanb maaid taaib, taub taub zuvq xij zu'g Jiaj kaatq Eei leid. Navq naaiq se yem meib Bua Eei sin zruj Javb hog pun Ziv yia Zauj meib Bua lyepg Jiad yetg liud Eei vcvg waag.
17.1: apg-laam Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q Juaq zyepg Juaq Havj uaq zang, zyruq hing Zwrtq taaib Buaj ninb, “yia se nrnb Jiaj Eei Tinb huvb. meib xij zu'g mwavj yia Eei waag, zanb zang zruj hxpg, maiq lamb Gemb txvj.
17.26: tovb uaq Nxi apg-laa-ham Zauj ninb Eei txn, i-saa-maa-en, Jiaj kaatq Eei leid.
17.25: ninb Eei txn, i-saa-maa-en, tu'q zyepg faam Havj.

49.18: “ zyruq aag, yia zuaq Jyenq meib Fruj yia.
49.8: “yu-Daa aag, meib Eei muab txig xij Zev meib. meib lovg meib Eei puad nanq Jyenq meib Eei winb wavq Eei Jaav. meib Eei muab txig xij kweig Fiag Dau paaij meib.
49.33: yaa-Kopq Paaiq waag Buaj liud ninb Eei txn Bua, ninb pweij Fiag Zruj  zyrug tavj Qiaj, kwei seij mig a'q.
49.3: “lu-Ben aag, meib zruj yia Eei txnb Lo. meib se yia Eei Qa'q. yia penj tomb myenb tu'q taaib Eei taaub taub txn. meib zruj tomb kxj, yetg pua'q txn meib kaub maaib mevb Jiaj, meib yaag kaub henq.
49.32: uaq Rov Dau Zauj Bcvb Kwrtq Tevj hitq-Tai myenb maaid taaib.”
49.21: “napq-Taa-li penj taub Faib Eeid puvj uaq lomg, ninb Fiag tu'q txn Rweig Eei.
49.14: “itg-saaj-Kaa Navq lxb nx henq, Baapq Fiag ninb Eei pa'ki yuvb laanb  Bu'Dovj.
49.23: pwrnq Jwavb zinj Eei myenb taaib Zauj ninb Bx'q Jaaj zruj to'g, pwrnq ninb, zruj hxig ninb.
49.6: ninb Bua taaq za'eij, yia maiq Zauj ninb Bua Zaavb laavb. ninb Bua kapq zunq Eei zyavb hog, yia maiq Zauj ninb Bua zruj txig, weig zu'g ninb Bua Qiaj Jiad taij myenb. ninb Bua sweib eij Va'q vovb kruq Eei tomb lwavg Jaan tavj.
49.2: “yaa-Kopq Eei txn aag, meib Bua taaib zunq mwavj. taaib mwavj meib Eei tia, i-saa-laa-en, kxvq.
49.20: “aa-se Eei teib puv puvb zua'g, ka'naaib zwavj lovj, haib zruj tu'q Pwij huvb tiaj Eang.
49.24: mq paag ninb zaavq tivg ninb Eei Jwavb zinj. ninb Eei puad yaag maaib Qa'q henq weig yaa-Kopq Eei nrnb Jiaj Eei Tinb huvb, weig kruj pa'ki yuvb Eei myenb, se i-saa-laa-en Eei la'pyeiq.
49.28: naaiq se i-saa-laa-en Eei zyepg Eeig fivj. yaag ziuj ninb Bua Eei tia pwav Eei waag Pwij tu'q ninb Bua taub taub.
49.7: laaij ninb Bua Qiaj Jiad, Zyruq, ninb Bua zu'g hruq. laaij Qiaj pe'q, Hruq to'g, ninb Bua zu'g zyruj. yia xij pun ninb Bua Raanj mivb kxmj i-saa-laa-en teib puv, yaag xij pun ninb Bua zxpg Jyenq i-saa-laa-en myenb yem.
49.29: yaa-Kopq Paaiq waag pun ninb Eei txn Bua, “yia aaq lamb kwei seij a'q.  xij zu'g txb yia mivb Zauj yia Eei ovb Taaij Bua zavj Jyenq hitq-Tai myenb, e-fo-lon, Eei Dau,
49.19: “kaatg xij zu'g kwanb Janb za'g Zaavq, mq paag ninb taauj sin zung Jyenq nitq Jyenq zaub Go mivb.
49.17: Daan xij penj tiub naav yem uaq Jauq, penj tiub naavb to'g yem uaq Jaub Len, Ex'q maad Eei zauj, hxig keb maad Eei myenb ta'Ryaauj faan, Dxtq ka'Diaq Dau mivb.
49.31: apg-laa-ham Zauj ninb Eei auq, saa-laa, zavj uaq.  i-sakg Zauj ninb Eei auq, le-Be-Kaa, yaag zavj uaq.  yia yaag zavj le-aa yem uaq nxm txvj.
49.30: makq-pe-laa, Eei Bcvb Kwrtq. naaiq teij Dau yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv, mam-le Eei tov puv mcvj. se apg-laa-ham Tevj uaq taub hitq-Tai myenb, e-fo-lon, maaid uaq Rov Dau Zauj uaq nxm Bcvb Kwrtq zruj zrub kemb.
49.27: “Ben-yaa-min Navq taub Yiab Juq Zei xq, luvb Dxm Eang ninb vaatg taaib Eei xq, luvb Mwavj pun Gxi ninb Zaavq taaib Eei ka'naaiq.”
49.11: ninb Eei lxb kruq ninb Dob Jyenq a'vung Mei, lxb txn Dob Jyenq kaub lovj Jiaj Eei a'vung Mei Gwaab. ninb xij lovg a'vung tiuq Roj ninb Eei lwib hruj, lovg a'vung uam si'q Eei Navq Ryaamq nx, Roj ninb Eei lwib Daauq.
49.5: “si-me-on Zauj le-wi zruj i muad. ninb Bua Eei Ru'g Daauq se zruj to'g Eei ua'g king.
49.9: yu-Daa aag, meib se Navq taub syenb txn nx.  yia Eei txn aag, meib Zwrtq mivb vaatg xq cvj Rwrnj meib Eei txvj. meib Baapq Fiag cvj pweij Fiag Navq syenb kruq. Navq syenb Eeid nx, haiq taub haib kaamq hc'q ninb Eia?
49.16: “Daan xij pcvb fim Eei syemq ninb Eei pc'g fivj. ninb Eei fivj se yetg fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb.
49.4: meib peiq Navq uamb seij nx, zyrug maiq tu'q zruj Lo, weig zu'g meib pweij meib Eei tia Eei aub txn, pun tia Eei Zruj maaib wij.
49.10: yu-Daa xij yetg liud nanq Jyenq huvb tiaj Eei pyaaq. ninb kunq myenb Eei pyaab Byaag zuvq maiq leib ninb Eei i Jia'q zauj Bu'Dovj, zuaq Tauj uaq tiub pyaab Byaag Eei zyruq  taaib Tauj. maang fivj myenb yaag mwavj ninb Eei waag.
49.22: “yo-sepq se zyavb pyruq Zamq Eei Dyavb Gwaab, se yem uamb zivq Len zyavb pyruq kitq Eei Gwaab. ninb Eei Gwaab yaag yxmg Zwrtq ka'Eiag zi'g laatg.
49.12: weig hopq a'vung tiuq, ninb Eei mziv si'q, weig ninb hopq vovb Exj, ninb Eei Eaab yaag pc'g.
49.15: ninb pwatg ninb hitq Eei txvj lovj, uaq nxm teib puv Kub yem, ninb zyrug Eiaj Jyenq ka'naaiq Jutg Jutq Eei mivb, lcvd zruj nrub pun myenb aapq zruj kov Kruq.
49.13: “sej-Bu-lun tu'q yem uaq Kxib Len, penj nxm Ravb prug pun Ravq tivb. ninb Eei kapg Jaaij mivb taauj Jyenq sai-Dxn zivb.
49.1: yaa-Kopq heug ninb Eei txn Bua taaib Rxib. ninb kxvq, “meib Bua taaib kapq zunq yia naaiq. yia xij kxvq Ga'haaq hivq meib Bua xij pwavb Eei sig.
49.26: meib Eei tia pun meib tu'q Eei fu'q se kaub Lo Jiaj yetg liud yem Eei Bov tu'q taaib Eei fu'q. se kaub Lo Jiaj yia Eei ovb Taaij pun taaib Eei fu'q.  Toq naaiq teij fu'q yem yo-sepq Eei mGxvq, yaag yem zinb Daavg leib ninb Eei muab txig uaq taub Eei pyxvb.
49.25: weig meib Eei tia Eei Tinb huvb, tovb Tevj meib uaq taub, yaag weig nrnb Jiaj Eei Tinb huvb Zeij fu'q pun meib. ninb pun kub vwaaig Eei fu'q, ka'Diaq Dau Eei fu'q, Zauj maaib scvb Kuq Zauj tu'q fu'Jweiq Eei fu'q.

11.18: pe-lekq tu'q faab zyepg Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug le-u.
11.8: zyruq zyrug pun ninb Bua Raanj Revg pwavq luvb Diaq. ninb Bua zyrug kwavg, maiq Zeij uaq nxm zivb a'q.
11.3: laanb kxvq Buaj laanb, “taaib maa'b! Bua nanq niab zun puaq vcvg taaib.” ninb Bua lovg niab zun tiq la'pyeiq. Daub Diaq Erub haig Eei zuv ninb Bua lovg tiq pa'naib nia.
11.32: Te-laa zyavb tu'q Eig pc'q levb pyaa Havj zyrug yem haa-laan zivb kwei seij mig a'q.
11.21: tu'q liud sej-lukq, ninb zyavb tu'q Eig pc'q levb siag Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
11.14: Qe-laa tu'q faab zyepg Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug e-Be.
11.23: tu'q liud naa-ho, ninb zyavb tu'q Eig pc'q Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
11.6: zyruq kxvq, “mavg kaaj! naaiq teij myenb se Du'g fivj myenb yaag kxvq Du'g Euvg waag Navq. Ko'q ho'g Jiad kxn zruj, ninb Bua haib zruj tu'q Dovg naaiq, ninb Bua Jiad Hruq zruj haiq Euvg ninb Bua zyrug haib zruj tu'q Zwrtq Eei.
11.2: ninb Bua swiq Jyenq mivb tov puv mcvj, Tauj si-naa teib puv, maaib Daub pcvb Eei txvj, zyrug tivb Fiag yem uaq a'q.
11.20: le-u tu'q faab zyepg Eeig Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug sej-lukq.
11.24: naa-ho tu'q Eig zyepg Juaq Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug Te-laa.
11.28: haa-laan kwei seij Daavg ninb Eei tia, Te-laa. haa-laan mtaaib yem ninb Zwrtq seij Eei teib puv kwei seij, se Ken-Dia myenb Eei u-aa zivb.
11.7: taaib maa'b! Bua Fiag mivb zruj lung ninb Bua Eei waag weig pun laanb maiq mevb pc'g laanb.”
11.29: apg-laam Zauj naa-ho i taub txv Jaa. apg-laam Eei auq heug saa-laai. naa-ho Eei auq heug min-Kaa, se haa-laan Eei sia'q. haa-laan zruj min-Kaa Zauj itg-Kaa Eei tia.
11.19: tu'q liud le-u, ninb zyavb tu'q Eig pc'q levb Duab Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
11.17: tu'q liud pe-lekq, ninb zyavb tu'q feij pc'q faab zyepg Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
11.31: Te-laa txb ninb Eei txn, apg-laam, Zauj ninb Eei fun, haa-laan Eei txn, lotq, Zauj ninb Eei Bwavd, apg-laam Eei auq, saa-laai, Zwrtq Ken-Dia teib puv Eei u-aa zivb xij mivb Kaa-naa-an teib puv. mq paag ninb Bua mivb Tauj haa-laan zivb zyrug tivb Fiag yem uaq a'q.
11.30: saa-laai maiq haib maaib scvb yuvd. ninb maiq maaib fu'Jweiq.
11.27: yem naaiq mivb kxvq Te-laa Eei zeib fun. Te-laa zruj apg-laam, naa-ho Zauj haa-laan Eei tia. haa-laan zruj lotq Eei tia.
11.11: tu'q liud aan-faa-satq, ninb zyavb Jyenq Mmd pc'q Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
11.5: zyruq zyrug Fiag taaib mavg paamb myenb Zeij Eei zivb Zauj fanb Taapq.
11.9: weig naaiq, uaq nxm zivb maaib Buaj heug Baa-Ben, weig zu'g yem uaq zyruq pun myenb Eei waag lung Revg. yem uaq zyruq yaag pun zwavj myenb Raanj mivb yem pwavq luvb Diaq.
11.16: e-Be tu'q faab zyepg feij Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug pe-lekq.
11.4: ninb Bua cvj kxvq, “taaib maa'b! Bua Zeij nxm zivb yaag Zeij nxm fanb Taapq Lav Tauj kub vwaaig luvb, pun Bua maaib mevb taub yaag maiq zu'g pun Raanj pwavq luvb Diaq.”
11.10: yem naaiq mivb kxvq sem Eei zeib fun. Byuvb swib imj yemj liud luvb Diaq, Ga'haaq i Havj, sem tu'q yetg pc'q Havj uaq Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug aan-faa-satq.
11.22: sej-lukq tu'q faab zyepg Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug naa-ho.
11.12: aan-faa-satq tu'q faab zyepg Mmd Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug Qe-laa.
11.15: tu'q liud e-Be, Qe-laa zyavb tu'q feij pc'q levb pua Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
11.13: tu'q liud Qe-laa, aan-faa-satq zyavb Jyenq feij pc'q levb pua Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
11.1: zinb Daavg luvb Diaq myenb yetg zuvq kxvq Du'g Euvg waag Navq. waab eij fib Navq Revg.
11.26: Te-laa tu'q Zyetq zyepg Havj, ninb tu'q pua taub txn, Buaj heug apg-laam, naa-ho Zauj haa-laan.
11.25: tu'q liud Te-laa, ninb zyavb tu'q yetg pc'q zyepg Juaq Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.

33.18: yaa-Kopq yem patg-Daan-aa-lam mivb Tauj Kaa-naa-an teib puv, se-Kem zivb mig a'q. lovj Eei, maiq maaib haiq Euvg. ninb Zxv Jyenq Dopg liub yem uaq zivb ka'Len.
33.3: yaa-Kopq kanb mivb Daavg Pua'q Fiag Tauj Dau siag Rung Zivj Tauj fatq teij ninb Eei kxj uaq.
33.8: e-saau naaig kaaj, “yia pwavb uaq teij scvb Kuq kwanb maaib haiq Euvg eij leid?” yaa-Kopq tau, “oq, naaiq se weig xij pun kxj Gxi fim Gxi eij Namq yia.”
33.19: Zxv Dopg liub Eei Dau ninb lovg yetg pc'q Kwaaiq Eaanb Tevj haa-mo Eei txn Bua, se-Kem Eei tia, maaid taaib.
33.9: mq paag e-saau tau, “yrud aag, yia mq paag maaib kauj lovg Eei. meib Eei, lyrub meib kanb lovg a'q.”
33.7: Jiaj taaib le-aa Zauj ninb Eei fu'Jweiq yaag taaib kweig Fiag paaij. yo-sepq Zauj laa-sen Ga'haaq Tauj yaag fib Navq Eei kweig Fiag paaij.
33.5: e-saau Zau Myen pwatg uaq teij msia'q txn Zauj fu'Jweiq, ninb naaig kaaj, “kan meib taaib naaiq teij myenb se haiq taub?” yaa-Kopq tau, “naaiq teij fu'Jweiq se Tinb huvb Kxb lyenb yia, Zeij pun yia, meib Eei pru.”
33.16: uaq Nxi e-saau zyrug Rwrnj sej-i teig mig a'q.
33.20: yem uaq nxm txvj ninb Zeij nxm ziab txvb cvj Zwrtq Buaj heug en-e-lo-he-i-saa-laa-en.
33.17: mq paag yaa-Kopq mivb sukg-Kotq komq pyauq, zruj scvb Kuq liub. uaq nxm txvj zyrug Zwrtq Buaj heug sukg-Kotq.
33.14: meib kunq mivb Daavg a'q. yia Ga'haaq manb mang mivb. sij kxvq fu'Jweiq Zauj scvb Kuq mivb tu'q nx, yia mq paag kaanq Jyenq mivb Tauj yia cvj pwavb meib, yia Eei zyruq, yem sej-i teig.”
33.4: mq paag e-saau Tiuj mivb zipq, Qam Jyenq zom. i muad zuvq Eyemq.
33.2: ninb pun ninb Eei i taub nrub peid Zauj ninb Bua Eei fu'Jweiq mivb Daavg. Jiaj taaib maaib le-aa Zauj ninb Eei fu'Jweiq. laa-sen Zauj yo-sepq Ga'haaq laai Jiaj.
33.6: uaq teij i taub nrub peid Zauj ninb Bua Eei fu'Jweiq zyrug taaib kweig Fiag paaij.
33.13: yaa-Kopq tau, “yia Eei zyruq yaag hiuq Eei, fu'Jweiq mwrng haig. yia yaag xij zu'g Namq Tauj pa'ki yuvb Zauj yuvb Zauj vovb txb Jyenq txn Eei. sij kxvq hxvb Jyenq mivb pe'q nx, yetg Nxi Navq scvb Kuq zuvq taig Revg a'q.
