33.12: e-saau kxvq, “Bua lomb Rxib mivb a'q. yia mivb Daavg txb meib.”
33.15: e-saau kxvq, “uaq Euvg, yia pun i ziaj taub yia kanb Eei myenb Zauj meib yem naaiq.” yaa-Kopq tau, “maiq zu'g Navq naaig lx'g. ta'faanb tu'q yia Eei zyruq Gxi eij Navq tu'q a'q.”
33.11: Toq kxj zipq yia txb taaib Eei zivb Eeig. Tinb huvb Kxb lyenb yia, pun yia maaib kauj lovg.” yaa-Kopq kxvq kau, e-saau lcvd lovg mig a'q.
33.1: yaa-Kopq mivb kau, pwatg e-saau Zauj ninb Eei feij pc'q taub myenb taaib. ninb zyrug pun Gxi ninb Eei fu'Jweiq pun le-aa, laa-sen Zauj i taub nrub peid, yetg taub txb teij mivb.
33.10: yaa-Kopq kxvq, “Toq maiq tuvq Navq naaiq nx kxvq og. sij kxvq meib Gxi eij yia nx, Toq lovg yia Eei zivb Eeig. ib zang yia pwatg meib Eei Myen se Navq pwatg Tinb huvb Eei Myen nx, weig zu'g meib maaib Hruq zipq yia lovj haig.

16.3: apg-laam Eei auq, saa-laai, zyrug zx'q ninb Eei nrub peid uaq taub i-yipq myenb, haa-kaa, pun ninb Eei Goj lovg zruj auq. (uaq zang apg-laam yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv tu'q zyepg Havj.)
16.8: zyrug naaig ninb, “saa-laai Eei nrub peid, haa-kaa aa'b! meib yem haaij taaib? xij mivb haaij?” haa-kaa tau, “yia pyauj yia Eei zyruq, saa-laai a'q.”
16.9: zyruq Eei finb myenb cvj kxvq, “meib xij zu'g Rwrnj meib Eei zyruq uaq yaag Bua'g ninb kunq.”
16.7: zyruq Eei finb myenb pwavb haa-kaa yem teib puvb Waav mivb su-waa zivb uaq tiub Jauq Eei uamb zivq Len,
16.5: saa-laai kxvq Buaj apg-laam, “se laaij meib yia Zivj zu'g haa-kaa mavg yia maiq Jiad. yia zx'q yia Eei nrub peid pun meib Qam Jyenq. ib zang ninb hiuq tu'q ninb maaib Jyenq sin ninb zyrug mavg Piaj yia. Toq zyruq syemq mavg kaaj, yia zruj tu'q hxpg fai meib zruj tu'q hxpg.”
16.16: haa-kaa yuvd i-saa-maa-en pun apg-laam uaq zang apg-laam Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q petq zyepg lua'g Havj.
16.14: Navq naaiq nx yem Kaa-Detg Zauj Be-letq Bu'Dovj uaq nxm uamb Kwrtq, myenb Zwrtq Buaj heug Be-e-laa-hai-lxi.
16.4: apg-laam Zauj haa-kaa pweij, haa-kaa zyrug maaib Jyenq sin a'q. haa-kaa hiuq tu'q kanb maaib Jyenq sin, ninb zyrug mavg maiq faauj mweig ninb Eei zyruq, saa-laai.
16.2: saa-laai zyrug kxvq Buaj apg-laam, “zyruq pun yia maiq haib tu'q fu'Jweiq. meib pia'g mivb Zauj yia Eei nrub peid pweij maa'b! Riaj yia haib laaij ninb tu'q fu'Jweiq mq pei.” apg-laam mwavj saa-laai Eei waag.
16.6: apg-laam tau, “ninb mtaaib zruj meib Eei nrub peid, yem meib Eei puab Diaq. meib xij Navq haiq nx zruj pun ninb, sweib meib zruj a'q maa'b!” saa-laai zruj to'g haa-kaa, haa-kaa zyrug pyauj mig a'q.
16.13: haa-kaa zyrug Zwrtq Buaj pun zyruq, tovb Zauj ninb kxvq waag uaq taub. ninb kxvq, “meib se mavg tu'q pwatg yia uaq taub Tinb huvb.” cvj kxvq, “yia yem naaiq pwatg liud mavg tu'q pwatg yia uaq taub mq paag Zxg maaib mcvg zyavb Eei?”
16.12: meib Eei txn xij Navq taub Yiab lxb nx. ninb Eei puad xij Bx'q zwavj myenb, zwavj myenb yaag xij Bx'q ninb. Zauj ninb Eei yetg zuvq muab txig yaag maiq haib hxpg.”
16.15: Ga'haaq haa-kaa yuvd tu'q taub txn pun apg-laam. apg-laam zyrug Tevj ninb Eei txn Zwrtq Buaj heug i-saa-maa-en.
16.11: zyruq Eei finb myenb cvj kxvq Buaj haa-kaa, “meib ib zang maaib Jyenq sin, xij yuvd tu'q taub txn. meib xij zu'g Tevj ninb Zwrtq Buaj heug i-saa-maa-en, weig zu'g zyruq haid liud meib Eei Kruq naang a'q.
16.1: apg-laam Eei auq, saa-laai, maiq haib yuvd fu'Jweiq pun apg-laam. saa-laai maaib taub nrub peid, Buaj heug haa-kaa, se i-yipq myenb.
16.10: zyruq Eei finb myenb cvj kxvq Buaj ninb, “yia xij pun meib Eei zeib fun Yaavj taaib zuvq saauq maiq hivb.”

40.18: yo-sepq kxvq, “meib Eei Beij Eei eij leid se Navq naaiq. uaq teij pua nxm Jei peiq pua Nxi.
40.8: ninb Bua tau, “a'Mwavj yia Bua i taub zuvq Beij Beij. yem naaiq yaag maiq maaib haiq taub haib Tevj yia Bua Pxq Beij.” yo-sepq tau, “Kuvj Tinb huvb Navq haib Pxq Beij maiq zeid? meib Bua kxvq meib Bua Eei Beij pun yia mwavj maa'b!”
40.3: zyrug zx'q ninb Bua wrnj Jyenq kruj huvb ting uaq taub tomb pcvb pyeiq Eei pyauq Eei lob, tovb yo-sepq zu'g wrnj uaq nxm lob.
40.21: prub a'vung tiuq uaq taub cvj tu'q zruj kov Navq lod uaq nx, zyrug zx'q tiub zaanq prub mivb pun huvb tiaj.
40.14: meib tu'q lovj Eei zyavb hog Toq Javj teij yia, zruj lovj pun yia. kxvq teij yia Eei Jauq pun faa-lo huvb mwavj, Fruj yia Zwrtq naaiq nxm lob.
40.23: mq paag prub a'vung tiuq uaq taub Jyen la'Ku'q yo-sepq mig a'q. maiq Javj zu'g ninb a'q.
40.6: ta'Eeig Dxm yo-sepq pia'g mivb mavg, pwatg ninb Bua i taub zuvq Raub Raub uaq.
40.2: huvb tiaj Qiaj Jiad haig naaiq teij i taub Jyen,
40.20: cvj Jiaj pua Nxi Tauj faa-lo huvb Eei sib Eyetg Nxi, ninb zyrug Beng Eang hopq zruj Jxm Zivq ninb Eei yetg zuvq zruj Jyen Eei myenb taaib. ninb yaag puvj prub a'vung tiuq Zauj zruj Fuaq uaq teij i taub tomb Jyen Zwrtq taaib yem zwavj Jyen Eei Ra'Myen.
40.7: ninb naaig kaaj faa-lo Eei tomb Jyen, tovb Zauj ninb zu'g wrnj Jyenq ninb Eei zyruq Eei pyauq Eei lob uaq teij i taub, “meib Bua ib Nxi zruj haiq Euvg? pwatg Raub Raub uaq!”
40.19: cvj pua Nxi faa-lo huvb xij pun myenb Va'q Dutq meib Eei mGxvq cvj zx'q meib Eei sei Diuj Jyenq Dyavj. nx'g yaag xij taaib Eang meib Eei xq.”
40.17: kub vwaaig uaq nxm Jei maaib Euvb Euvg zi'q taaib Eei Fuaq pun faa-lo huvb Eang. mq paag nx'g taaib Eang uaq teij Fuaq.”
40.11: uaq zang faa-lo huvb Eei zaanq yem yia Eei puad. yia zyrug kc'q uaq teij a'vung pyruq nanq pyrub uam tapq Jyenq zaanq prub pun faa-lo.”
40.5: maaib mwrnd nx, prub tiuq Zauj zruj Fuaq uaq teij i taub tomb Jyen yem uaq lob Beij Beij. yetg taub Beij pwatg yetg Euvg. yetg taub Eei Beij yaag maaib yetg Euvg eij leid.
40.9: prub a'vung tiuq uaq taub tomb Jyen zyrug kxvq ninb Eei Beij pun yo-sepq mwavj. ninb kxvq, “yia pwatg tiub a'vung Mei yem yia Eei Ra'Myen.
40.16: zruj Fuaq Eei tomb Jyen pwatg yo-sepq Pxq Beij Eei eij leid lovj, ninb zyrug kxvq Buaj yo-sepq, “yia yaag Beij nxm Beij. yia pwatg yia kanb Eei mGxvq Dovj Jyenq pua nxm Jei, tapq Jyenq Fuaq Eei.
40.4: kruj huvb ting uaq taub tomb pcvb pyeiq Paaiq yo-sepq kruj ninb Bua. ninb Bua i taub yaag zu'g wrnj Jyenq lob laub Eei.
40.10: uaq tiub Mei yaag maaib pua Zaaj Gwaab. yetq Zwrtq Zunj taaib yaag Gxi pyavb, pyrub Jxib yaag zua'g.
40.22: mq paag zruj Fuaq uaq taub c'q, faa-lo huvb heug zx'q taaib Diuj Jyenq uaq Dyavj taij kwavg mig a'q. naaiq teij sig za'kevb txij Revg yo-sepq Pxq Eei Beij.
40.12: yo-sepq kxvq, “meib Eei Beij Eei eij leid se Navq naaiq. uaq teij pua Gwaaq Gwaab peiq pua Nxi.
40.15: yia yem hipq-lu myenb Eei teib puv zu'g txb Tauj naaiq taaib. yem naaiq i-yipq teib puv yia yaag maiq txvg haiq Euvg zig tu'q pun yia zu'g wrnj Jyenq naaiq lob Mwavj.”
40.13: cvj pua Nxi faa-lo huvb xij puvj meib Zwrtq, xij kwavg meib Eei zwid, yaag pun meib tu'q zruj kov Navq lod uaq nx. meib cvj tu'q prub a'vung tiuq pun faa-lo huvb Navq zinb Daavg meib zruj uaq nx.
40.1: Jiaj liud yetg Zaamj, Tevj i-yipq teib puv Eei faa-lo huvb prub a'vung tiuq uaq taub tomb Jyen Zauj zruj Fuaq pun faa-lo huvb Eang uaq taub tomb Jyen txvg huvb tiaj.

37.18: ninb Eei kxj Bua pwatg yo-sepq Zxg yem ko Eei. taaib maiq kcvb Tauj, ninb Bua zyrug lomb Rxib Zaavb laavb taaq za'eij taij.
37.8: ninb Eei kxj Bua naaig kaaj ninb, “meib kevb xij zruj yia Bua Eei huvb? xij kunq yia Bua?” laaij yo-sepq Beij Eei Beij Zauj ninb kxvq Eei waag, ninb Eei kxj Bua kaub fatq Rxv ninb a'q.
37.33: yaa-Kopq zia'q tu'q Eei. ninb kxvq, “naaiq za'kevb! yia Eei txn Eei lwi. za'kevb! ka'naaiq vaatg, ka'naaiq petq mig a'q lx'g.”
37.3: i-saa-laa-en Namq yo-sepq kaub Zamq Jiaj ninb Eei yetg zuvq txn, weig zu'g ninb koj a'q, Zivj tu'q yo-sepq taaib. ninb lunb teij lwib Daauq, lwib mweid yaag Daauq, pun yo-sepq.
37.32: cvj txb Rwrnj pun ninb Eei tia mavg. ninb Bua kxvq, “yia Bua lxd pwatg naaiq teij lwi. tia mavg kaaj, meib Eei txn Eei lwi saa'b?”
37.21: lu-Ben haid ninb yrud Bua Navq naaiq nx kxvq, ninb xij lxd Jauq Fruj yo-sepq Zwrtq ninb Bua Eei puab Diaq. ninb zyrug kxvq, “Bua maiq tuvq taij ninb.”

37.34: yaa-Kopq Raub haig, petq ninb kanb Eei lwi cvj zx'q la'maab Diab Zru sai Jyenq Jaaiq. ninb Raub haig, Eyemq ninb Eei txn ziaj laaig laub.

4.18: e-nokq tu'q taub txn heug i-laatq. i-laatq zruj me-huj-yaa-en Eei tia. me-huj-yaa-en zruj me-Tu-saa-en Eei tia. me-Tu-saa-en zruj laa-mekq Eei tia.

4.2: Ga'haaq ninb cvj yuvd Kaa-in Eei yrud, aa-Bcn. aa-Bcn Lo taaib ninb yuvd pa'ki yuvb. Kaa-in c'q, zruj lyavb Deig.

46.17: aa-se Eei txn se im-naa, itg-waa, itg-wi Zauj Be-li-yaa. naaiq teij txn Eei muag heug se-laa-aa. Be-li-yaa Eei txn se he-Be Zauj man-Ki-en.
46.31: yo-sepq kxvq Buaj ninb Eei muab txig Zauj ninb Eei tia Bua yetg zuvq Mwavq txig, “yia xij Buaj faa-lo huvb, ‘yia Eei muab txig Zauj yia Eei tia Bua Mwavq txig yetg zuvq yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv ib zang taaib Tauj yia naaiq taaib a'q.
46.30: i-saa-laa-en kxvq Buaj yo-sepq, “ib zang yia tu'q pwatg liud meib, hiuq tu'q meib Zxg zyavb Jyenq Eei, yia taig yaag Hruq Gaai a'q.”
46.27: cvj maaib yo-sepq yem i-yipq teib puv tu'q uaq teij i taub txn. yaa-Kopq pia'g i-yipq teib puv uaq zang, ninb Eei txnb Jweiq funb fa'q yetg zuvq maaib Zyetq zyepg taub.
46.11: le-wi Eei txn se ke-son, Ko-haatq Zauj me-laa-li.
46.5: yaa-Kopq yem Be-e-Qe-Baa teig Zwrtq Jauq. ninb Eei txn Bua pun ninb Bua Eei tia Zauj ninb Bua Eei fu'Jweib faij Zauj ninb Bua yetg zuvq Eei auq faauj faa-lo huvb pun taaib zipq yaa-Kopq Bua uaq teij vovb Zia mivb.
46.9: lu-Ben Eei txn se haa-nokq, pan-lu, hetq-lon, Zauj Kaan-mi.
46.16: kaatg Eei txn se si-fi-yon, hakq-ki, su-ni, etg-Bon, e-le-i, aa-lo-Di Zauj aa-le-li.
46.4: yia Zauj meib mivb i-yipq teib puv, Dovg haaij zuvq xij txb meib Rwrnj taaib. meib kwei seij Eei zyavb hog, yo-sepq kanb xij Tevj meib Eei mziv Fipq.
46.10: si-me-on Eei txn se ye-mu-en, yaa-min, o-haatg, yaa-Kin, soj-haaj Zauj saa-un. saa-un zruj Kaa-naa-an sia'q Eei txn.
46.22: naaiq teij se laa-sen yuvd pun yaa-Kopq Eei txnb Jweiq funb fa'q. yetg zuvq maaib zyepg feij taub.
46.12: yu-Daa Eei txn se e-aa, o-nan, Qe-laa, pe-letq Zauj ze-laa. (mq paag e-aa Zauj o-nan yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv uaq zang kwei seij mig a'q.) pe-letq Eei txn se hetq-lon Zauj haa-mun.
46.15: naaiq teij se le-aa yem patg-Daan-aa-lam yuvd pun yaa-Kopq Eei txnb Jweiq funb fa'q. cvj maaib taub sia'q, Buaj heug Di-naa. le-aa Eei pwrng txnb Jweiq funb fa'q yetg zuvq maaib faab zyepg faam taub.
46.13: itg-saaj-Kaa Eei txn se To-laa, pu-waa, i-opg Zauj sim-lon.
46.1: i-saa-laa-en txb Jyenq ninb maaib Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq Zwrtq Jauq mivb Tauj Be-e-Qe-Baa teig yem uaq ziag ninb Eei tia, i-sakg, Eei Tinb huvb.
46.26: kan yaa-Kopq mivb i-yipq teib puv uaq zang, ninb kanb Eei txnb Jweiq funb fa'q maaib lua'g zyepg lua'g taub, Zib Zwrtq ninb Eei Bwavd.
46.25: naaiq teij se laa-Baan pun ninb Eei sia'q, laa-sen, uaq taub nrub peid, Bin-haa, yuvd pun yaa-Kopq Eei txnb Jweiq funb fa'q. yetg zuvq maaib siag taub.

13.18: apg-laam zyrug swiq ninb Eei Dopg liub mivb Zxv Jyenq yem he-Bo-lon hxvg nitq mam-le Eei tomb Ba'ov zwei Dyavb lomg. yem uaq ninb cvj Zeij nxm ziab txvb zavg zyruq.
13.3: ninb yem ne-kepg, yetg Kav swiq Jiaj yetg Kav, mivb Tauj Betg-en zivb, cvj Rwrnj Tauj Betg-en Zauj ai zivb Bu'Dovj,
13.8: apg-laam zyrug kxvq Buaj lotq, “Bua maiq tuvq ta'hauq. Bua Eei kruj scvb Kuq pru yaag maiq tuvq ta'hauq weig zu'g Bua se Zyen Eei.
13.9: Dau yetg zuvq yem meib uaq Daavg mcvj. Bua xij zu'g pun Gxi txig yem. sij kxvq meib mivb zaaij puv, yia zyrug mivb Byaaug puv. sij kxvq meib mivb Byaaug puv, yia zyrug mivb zaaij puv.”
13.7: apg-laam Eei kruj scvb Kuq pru Zauj lotq Eei kruj scvb Kuq pru zyrug ta'hauq a'q. (uaq zang Kaa-naa-an myenb Zauj pe-litq-si myenb Zxg yem Jyenq uaq nxm teib puv.)
13.5: lotq kan Jyenq apg-laam mivb. ninb yaag maaib pa'ki yuvb maaib yuvb kwanb, maaib vovb kwanb, maaib ninb kanb Eei Mwavq txig Zauj pru.
13.16: yia xij pun meib Eei zeib fun Yaavj taaib Navq niab Buv nx Zamq. haiq taub haib saauq tu'q Revg niab Buv Zivj taaib haib saauq tu'q Revg meib Eei zeib fun.
13.17: meib mivb a'q. mivb yrub zweib Daauq zweib Javq mavg kxmj Revg naaiq nxm teib puv weig zu'g yia xij Jiu pun meib.”
13.14: lotq Zauj apg-laam pun Gxi txig liud, zyruq Buaj apg-laam, “Zau Myen mavg kaaj tov naamb fai pa'q, ta'faanb meib yem naaiq mavg pwatg Eei txvj.
13.4: tovb zinb Daavg Zxv Dopg liub yaag Zeij Jiad ziab txvb uaq nxm txvj. apg-laam cvj yem uaq kxvq Zwrtq zyruq Eei Buaj zavg zyruq.
13.2: apg-laam putq zxib haig, maaib scvb Kuq, maaib Jyem, maaib Eaanb Zamq haig.
13.6: yem uaq nxm txvj Eei Dau maiq Javq, maiq kauj ninb Bua i taub yem. i taub zuvq maaib scvb Kuq Zamq haig. Jwavg Jyenq yem maiq Fiag.
13.13: soj-Dom myenb waaig haig, paamd zwid txvg zyruq Zamq.
13.12: apg-laam Zxg yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv. lotq c'q, yem Jx-Dcn hxvg Eei Daub pcvb Eei zivb yaag Zxv ninb Eei Dopg liub nitq soj-Dom.
13.15: yia pun Revg meib Zauj meib Eei zeib fun yetg liud yem.
13.11: lotq zyrug kinq Jx-Dcn hxvg Eei Daub pcvb yetg zuvq penj ninb Eei pwrng, zyrug Zwrtq Jauq yavb tov puv mivb. ninb Bua i pc'g fun zyrug pun Gxi txig mig a'q.
13.1: apg-laam txb Jyenq ninb Eei auq Zauj ninb maaib Eei Euvb Euvg ka'naaiq Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv mivb Tauj ne-kepg. lotq yaag Zauj Jyenq ninb mivb.
13.10: lotq Zau Myen samj mavg, pwatg Jx-Dcn hxvg Eei Daub pcvb, Zwrtq soj-aa zivb uaq puv, maaib uamb swiq lovj Navq zyruq Eei Wivj yaag Navq i-yipq teib puv nx. (uaq zang zyruq maiq kcvb myetg soj-Dom Zauj ko-mo-laa zivb.)

26.18: ninb cvj wetq Rung tovb yem ninb Eei tia, apg-laa-ham, Eei seij zeiq wetq taaib Eei uamb Kwrtq, weig zu'g apg-laa-ham kwei seij liud, Ga'haaq fi-li-saa-tia myenb tinb Dipg Revg mig a'q. i-sakg yaag Zwrtq uaq teij uamb Kwrtq Eei Buaj ziuj zinb Daavg ninb Eei tia Zwrtq Eei Buaj.
26.8: i-sakg yem uaq laub a'q. maaib Nxi nx, aa-Bi-me-lekq huvb yem huvb ting mavg Zwrtq fov mwrnb, pwatg i-sakg Zauj le-Be-Kaa Qam Jyenq Jaaj.
26.33: i-sakg zyrug Zwrtq uaq nxm uamb Kwrtq Eei Buaj heug Qi-Baa. weig naaiq, uaq nxm txvj Eei zivb Eei Buaj heug Be-e-Qe-Baa Tauj ib Jaaj Nxi.
26.3: xij zu'g yem naaiq nxm teib puv, yia zyrug Zauj meib yem yaag Zeij fu'q pun meib, weig zu'g yia xij zx'q naaiq teij yetg zuvq teib puv pun meib Zauj meib Eei zeib fun yetg liud yem. yia xij ei Jyenq yia Zauj meib Eei tia, apg-laa-ham, hruq Jiaj vcvg waag zruj zyavj.
26.32: tovb uaq Nxi i-sakg Eei pru taaib kxvq Tauj ninb Bua wetq uamb Kwrtq Eei Jauq. ninb Bua kxvq, “yia Bua wetq Tauj uam mig a'q.”
26.21: i-sakg Eei pru cvj wetq tu'q nxm uamb Kwrtq. myenb cvj taaib Rcv. i-sakg zyrug Zwrtq Buaj heug sitg-naa.
26.35: weig naaiq teij i taub msia'q txn, i-sakg Zauj le-Be-Kaa zu'g Raub Zamq.
26.14: ninb maaib vovb, maaib pa'ki yuvb, maaib yuvb Zamq. pru yaag maaib Zamq. fi-li-saa-tia myenb zyrug mweig Jia'q haig.
26.23: i-sakg cvj swiq mivb yem Be-e-Qe-Baa zivb.
26.6: i-sakg zyrug yem Jyenq ke-laa-aa zivb.
26.34: e-saau tu'q feij zyepg Havj uaq zang ninb txv Jaa. ninb lovg hitq-Tai myenb, Be-e-li, Eei sia'q, yu-Ditg. cvj lovg hitq-Tai myenb, e-lon, Eei sia'q, Baa-sej-matq.
26.2: zyruq hing Zwrtq kxvq Buaj i-sakg, “maiq tuvq mivb yem i-yipq teib puv. xij zu'g yem tovb yia xij Buaj meib yem Eei teib puv.
26.20: ke-laa-aa zivb Eei yuvd scvb Kuq Eei pru taaib Zauj i-sakg Eei yuvd scvb Kuq Eei pru Rcv. ninb Bua kxvq, “naaiq nxm uamb Kwrtq se yia Bua Eei.” i-sakg zyrug Zwrtq uaq nxm uamb Kwrtq Eei Buaj heug e-sekg, weig zu'g ninb Bua taaib Zauj ninb Rcv.
26.24: uaq mwrnd zyruq hing Zwrtq Buaj ninb, “yia se meib Eei tia, apg-laa-ham, Eei Tinb huvb. maiq tuvq kamb Riaj og. yia Zauj meib yem yaag weig yia Eei pru, apg-laa-ham, xij Zeij fu'q pun meib yaag pun meib Eei zeib fun Yaavj Jyenq faauj.”
26.28: ninb Bua tau, “yia Bua pwatg tu'q mevb Eei, zyruq Zauj meib yem. yia Bua taaib Toq Zauj meib lomb Rxib lcvd waag, pun meib Zauj yia Bua lyepg Jiad vcvg waag.
26.7: uaq nxm txvj Eei myenb naaig Tauj ninb Eei auq. i-sakg kxvq le-Be-Kaa zruj ninb Eei muag, kamb Riaj maiq kxvq le-Be-Kaa zruj ninb Eei auq. ninb yem Hruq Namq, “Riaj yem naaiq Eei myenb haib laaij le-Be-Kaa taij yia mq pei, weig zu'g le-Be-Kaa zyavb tu'q Rweig haig.”
26.29: Toq lcvd meib maiq zruj haiq Euvg hxig yia Bua, Navq zinb Daavg yia Bua maiq zruj haiq Euvg hxig meib nx. yia Bua Kuvj zruj lovj pun meib Navq. meib yaag tu'q pcvb xn Eei Zwrtq teib puv. ib zang meib se zyruq Zeij fu'q Eei myenb.”
26.19: i-sakg Eei pru cvj wetq nxm uamb Kwrtq yem uaq hxvd. wetq Zwrtq zivq uam taaib a'q.
26.17: i-sakg zyrug swiq mivb Zxv Dopg liub yem ke-laa-aa hxvd.
26.31: ta'Eeig Dxm ninb Bua Jiad sin Ryruq Eei, laanb Zauj laanb lyepg Jiad vcvg waag. lyepg liud, i-sakg fuvj ninb Bua Zwrtq Jauq, pcvb xn Eei leib Gxi txig.
26.30: i-sakg weig ninb Bua Beng tonj Naavj lovj Eei. ninb Bua zyrug yem uaq Eang, yem uaq hopq.
26.27: Tauj uaq i-sakg zyrug naaig kaaj, “zinb Daavg meib Bua Rxv yia, zung yia Zwrtq meib Bua Eei teib puv. ib zang meib Bua cvj taaib lxd yia zruj haiq Euvg?”
26.11: aa-Bi-me-lekq zyrug hatg ninb Eei pc'g fivj, “haiq taub zruj haiq Euvg pun naaiq taub myenb fai ninb Eei auq, uaq taub xij zu'g taij taig.”
26.5: weig zu'g apg-laa-ham mwavj yia Eei waag yaag ei Jyenq yia Paaiq Eei Jauq, Zauj yia Eei leib latg, yia Eei livg Zauj leid.”
26.9: aa-Bi-me-lekq heug i-sakg taaib zyrug kxvq, “ninb za'kevb meib Eei auq nyaa. meib weig haiq tiug kxvq ninb zruj meib Eei muag?” i-sakg tau, “weig zu'g yia Raub heij laaij ninb myenb xij taij yia mq pei.”
26.16: aa-Bi-me-lekq kxvq Buaj i-sakg, “meib xij zu'g swiq Gxi yia Bua a'q, weig zu'g meib ib zang kaub henq yia Bua.”
26.4: yia xij pun meib Eei zeib fun Yaavj taaib Dovg kub vwaaig luvb Eei Leij Zamq, yaag zx'q naaiq teij yetg zuvq teib puv pun ninb Bua. luvb Diaq maang kua'q myenb yaag xij weig meib Eei zeib fun tu'q fu'q,
26.10: aa-Bi-me-lekq kxvq, “meib fuvg Navq naaiq nx zruj pun yia Bua? sij kxvq maaib taub yia Eei pc'g fivj Zauj meib Eei auq pweij nx, se meib kanb txb zwid taaib hxig yia Bua.”
26.22: i-sakg zyrug leib Gxi uaq nxm txvj cvj kanb wetq nxm uamb Kwrtq. naaiq Rung maiq maaib haiq taub Rcv a'q. ninb zyrug Zwrtq uaq nxm uamb Kwrtq Eei Buaj heug le-hoj-Botg. ninb kxvq, “ib zang zyruq pun Bua maaib txvj yem. Bua yem naaiq nxm teib puv haib Jaa tu'q lovj Jyenq mivb a'q.”
26.12: i-sakg yem uaq nxm teib puv zwavj ka'naaiq. uaq Havj ninb zwavj yetg kruq syru tu'q yetg pc'q kruq weig zu'g zyruq Zeij fu'q pun ninb.
26.15: ninb Bua zyrug wetq nia tinb Dipg tovb zinb Daavg yem i-sakg Eei tia, apg-laa-ham, Eei seij zeiq uaq zang ninb Eei pru wetq taaib Eei uamb Kwrtq.
26.13: ninb kunq zruj kunq penj Jyenq faauj Tauj za'kevb zruj tomb putg zxib myenb.
26.1: yem apg-laa-ham Eei seij zeiq, naaiq nxm teib puv pwavb zu'g yetg Rung tomb Waav tomb vxg. Tauj i-sakg Eei seij zeiq cvj pwavb Rung. i-sakg zyrug mivb Tauj ke-laa-aa zivb, fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei huvb, aa-Bi-me-lekq uaq.
26.26: aa-Bi-me-lekq huvb Zauj Tevj ninb Zaavb laavb Eei myenb, aa-hutg-satq, cvj Zauj ninb Eei tomb pcvb pyeiq, fi-Ko, yem ke-laa-aa zivb mivb lxd i-sakg.
26.25: i-sakg zyrug yem uaq Zeij nxm ziab txvb yaag kxvq Zwrtq zyruq Eei Buaj taaib zavg. ninb yaag Zxv Dopg liub yem uaq nxm txvj. ninb Eei pru cvj wetq nxm uamb Kwrtq.

44.18: yu-Daa cvj mivb fatq teij txij yo-sepq kxvq, “yia Eei zyruq aag, yia Toq Zauj meib kxvq Jruj waag. meib maiq tuvq kcvb Qiaj Jiad yia, meib Eei pru, maiq kunq meib Dovg faa-lo huvb Lo.
44.8: mavg kaaj, maaid taaub Rung Byaub Eei Eaanb yem yia Bua Eei Bua'g yia Bua zuvq yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv txb taaib Twij Rwrnj pun meib. yia Bua fuvg haib nimg yem meib Eei zyruq Eei pyauq Eei Jyem Eaanb?
44.33: “Navq naaig, yia Toq pun yia, meib Eei pru, yem naaiq zruj meib Eei nrub tiq naaiq taub txn. Toq pun ninb kan Jyenq ninb Eei kxj Bua Rwrnj a'q og.
44.3: ta'Eeig Dxm Ryruq Eei, luvb Byrub Byrud Fav, tomb pru zyrug fuvj ninb Bua Zauj ninb Bua Eei lxb Zwrtq Jauq Rwrnj.
44.32: yia kanb lovg yia Eei mcvg zruj Daamb taaub Buaj yia Eei tia, ‘yia maiq txb naaiq taub yrud Rwrnj pun tia nx, yia lcvd yem tia Eei Ra'Myen yetg seij Daamb txv.’
44.21: “meib heug yia Bua, meib Eei pru, txb ninb taaib naaiq pun meib mavg.
44.14: yu-Daa Zauj ninb Eei muab txig Rwrnj Tauj yo-sepq Eei pyauq uaq zang, yo-sepq Zxg yem pyauq Eei. ninb Bua yem ninb Eei Ra'Myen Baapq Fiag Dau.
44.23: mq paag meib Buaj yia Bua, meib Eei pru, ‘yia Bua maiq txb naaiq taub yrub laai Zauj Jyenq taaib nx, yia Bua maiq tu'q cvj pwatg meib Eei Myen.’
44.6: uaq taub pru zung zaaig, ninb zyrug ei yo-sepq Eei waag kxvq.
44.34: sij kxvq naaiq taub txn maiq Zauj yia Rwrnj, yia Navq haiq nx haib Rwrnj yia Eei tia uaq. yia maiq xij pwatg yia Eei tia zu'g ze'g naang hxig ninb.”
44.2: zx'q yia Eei zaanq, tovb Eaanb zaanq uaq nxm, Zauj maaid Byaub Eei Eaanb tapq Jyenq yrub laai uaq taub Eei Bua'g Rwib.” pru zyrug ei Jyenq yo-sepq Eei waag zruj.
44.20: yia Bua tau, ‘tia maaib Eei mq paag koj haig a'q. yrud yaag maaib Eei. tia zuvq koj haig Zivj tu'q naaiq taub txnb laai. naaiq taub txn Eei kxj taig mig a'q. ninb Bua i muad Jwavg maa mq paag ib zang Kuvj maaib ninb kanb Navq. ninb Eei tia yaag Namq haig ninb.’
44.24: yia Bua txb meib Eei waag Rwrnj mivb kxvq pun meib Eei pru, yia Bua Eei tia, mwavj.
44.28: maaib taub zuvq leib Gxi yia. yia Namq taaib ninb zu'g Yiab ka'naaiq petq ninb mig a'q. Tauj ib zang yia maiq tu'q pwatg uaq taub txn.
44.7: mq paag uaq teij muab txig kxvq, “tomb kxj aag, meib zruj haiq Euvg Navq naaiq nx kxvq? yia Bua zuvq maiq Namq Tauj Navq naaiq nx zruj.
44.29: sij kxvq meib Bua txb naaiq taub mivb, ninb yaag pwavb zu'g sig nx, meib Bua zyrug pun yia, ovb mGxvb pc'g, Raub Tauj pia'g yemb ken.’+”
44.19: zyruq naaig yia Bua, meib Eei pru, ‘meib Bua Zxg maaib tia, maaib yrud Eei fai?’
44.17: yo-sepq kxvq, “maiq zeid Navq naaig lx'g. Kuvj zaanq yem Bua'g uaq taub xij zu'g zruj yia Eei nrub Navq. zevg uaq teij kunq pcvb xn Eei Rwrnj meib Bua Eei tia uaq a'q.”
44.31: yia Eei tia pwatg yia Eei yrud maiq Zauj yia Rwrnj nx, ninb zyrug taig a'q, weig zu'g naaiq taub txn zruj yia Eei tia Eei Ba'Riub kxn. Navq naaiq yia Eei tia, meib Eei pru, ovb mGxvb pc'g, Raub Tauj taig.
44.30: yu-Daa cvj kxvq, “sij kxvq yia Rwrnj meib Eei pru, yia Eei tia, uaq, yaag maiq maaib naaiq taub txn Zauj yia Rwrnj,
44.27: “meib Eei pru, yia Bua Eei tia, Buaj yia Bua, ‘meib Bua hiuq tu'q yia Eei auq, laa-sen, yuvd tu'q i taub txn pun yia Navq.
44.11: taub taub zyrug syepg syepq Eei prub Bua'g Fiag ton Jyenq uaq Dau Kxi.
44.5: meib Bua weig haiq tiug nimg yia Eei zyruq Eei Eaanb zaanq mivb? naaiq nxm zaanq ninb lovg hopq yaag lovg naaig zinb hod Eei Jauq. meib Bua za'kevb zruj txvg Do haig a'q.’+”
44.9: sij kxvq meib pwatg uaq nxm zaanq yem haiq taub, pun uaq taub zu'g taig a'q. zevg uaq teij lcvd zruj meib Eei nrub.”
44.16: yu-Daa kxvq, “yia Bua Navq haiq nx haib tau zyruq? Navq haiq nx haib kxvq? yia Bua Navq haiq nx haib Jaiq sin? Tinb huvb wetq Zwrtq Revg yia Bua zruj txvg Eei sig. ib zang maiq zeid Kuvj zaanq yem Bua'g uaq taub penj meib Eei nrub Navq. lyemb yia Bua yetg zuvq penj meib Eei nrub a'q.”
44.4: Zwrtq zi'g zivb mivb maiq kcvb navg ko, yo-sepq kxvq Buaj ninb Eei tomb pru, “kaanq mivb zung uaq teij myenb. zung zaaig, xij zu'g naaig kaaj ninb Bua, ‘yia Bua zruj lovj pun meib Bua. meib Bua weig haiq tiug zruj waaig pun yia Bua?
44.10: pru kxvq, “hxpg Eei. ei Jyenq meib Bua Eei waag zruj a'q. mq paag lxd pwatg yem haiq taub Eei Bua'g, uaq taub kanb xij zu'g zruj yia Eei nrub. zevg Fiag uaq teij maiq txvg haiq Euvg.”
44.22: yia Bua Buaj meib, yia Bua Eei zyruq, ‘uaq taub txn leib maiq tu'q ninb Eei tia. leib nx, ninb Eei tia haib taig Eei.’
44.12: pru zyrug sru a'q, yem tomb kxj Eei sru Jyenq mivb Tauj yrub laai Eei. Tauj Ben-yaa-min Eei Bua'g zyrug sru Zwrtq uaq nxm zaanq.
44.15: yo-sepq kxvq Buaj ninb Bua, “naaiq meib Bua zruj haiq Euvg lcb? meib Bua maiq hiuq tu'q yia naaiq Euvg myenb haib mavg tu'q Zwrtq zinb hod Eei sig, haib zx'q tu'q meib Bua fai?”
44.13: uaq teij muab txig Raub haig, petq ninb Bua Eei lwi, cvj prub Bua'g faauj pun lxb Tx Jyenq taauj Gaav Rwrnj uaq zivb a'q.
44.1: yo-sepq Paaiq kruj ninb Eei pyauq Eei tomb pru, “zx'q Byaub tapq naaiq teij myenb Eei Bua'g. tapq kauj ninb Bua txb. cvj zx'q kx'g myenb maaid Byaub Eei Eaanb tapq kx'g myenb Eei Bua'g Rwib.
44.26: yia Bua tau, ‘yia Bua maiq haib mivb. sij kxvq yia Bua Eei yrub laai Zauj Jyenq yia Bua mivb nx, yia Bua mivb Eei. weig zu'g yrub laai maiq Zauj yia Bua mivb nx, yia Bua maiq tu'q pwatg uaq laanb myenb Eei Myen.’
44.25: “yia Bua Eei tia Buaj yia Bua, ‘cvj mivb maaid teij Byaub maa'b!’

8.18: no-yaa Zauj ninb Eei aub Jweiq txnb Bwavd zyrug Zwrtq Revg taaib a'q.
8.8: no-yaa cvj puvj nxm nx'g Go Zwrtq mivb weig zu'g ninb xij hiuq tu'q Daub peib Eei uam haapq fai maiq kcvb haapq.
8.3: uam manb mang haapq Jyenq Fiag. Jiaj liud yetg pc'q Mmd zyepg Nxi uam Zxg haapq Jyenq Fiag.
8.21: zyruq haid naaiq teij Qiaj Daav, hxpg Hruq haig, zyrug yem Hruq Namq, “yia yetg liud maiq cvj weig myenb zruj waaig sig hruq Daub peib, weig zu'g myenb maanb yem faij Eei mtaaib Kuvj maaib Hruq zruj waaig sig Navq. yavb naaiq Jiaj, yia maiq Navq naaiq Rung myetg Euvb Euvg maaib mcvg Eei ka'naaiq.
8.14: Tauj Eeig Laaj Eig zyepg Zyetq uaq Nxi, Dau Gaai Revg mig a'q.
8.6: Jiaj liud feij zyepg Nxi, no-yaa Kxi Gxi tovb ninb zruj taaib yem Ravq Eei fov mwrnb
8.2: Daub Diaq Eei uamb zivq Eei Kwrtq yetg zuvq Dipg mig a'q. kub vwaaig luvb Eei kcvb yaag kwrn Revg. luvb yaag Lxvj mig a'q.
8.20: no-yaa Zeij nxm ziab txvb taaib weig zyruq. ninb cvj zx'q Euvb Euvg maiq maaib wij Eei scvb Kuq Zauj Euvb Euvg maiq maaib wij Eei nx'g, an ziab txvb penj puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq.
8.7: zyrug puvj nxm nx'g aa Zwrtq. nx'g aa Kuvj Daij mivb Daij taaib Tauj ka'Diaq Dau Eei uam haapq Gaai Revg.
8.19: yetg zuvq scvb Kuq Zauj Exv Dau Eei ka'naaiq Zauj nx'g, yetg zuvq yem Daub peib haib tovd Eei ka'naaiq, yetg Euvg yetg Euvg Eei, Zwrtq Ravq Revg.
8.17: Zauj meib yem naaiq teij Euvb Euvg maaib mcvg Eei ka'naaiq, nx'g, scvb Kuq Zauj Exv Dau Eei ka'naaiq xij zu'g txb Zwrtq taaib weig pun ninb Bua trug pwrnq Yaavj taaib pwavq luvb Diaq.”
8.11: luvb maanb Mwavj nx'g Go Rwrnj Tauj no-yaa uaq, Rwib pcvj Daam Jyenq yetg Kwaaiq ka'lanq nxmb mcv Eei, Eyemd Eei. no-yaa zyrug hiuq tu'q uam haapq Fiag mig a'q.
8.5: uam cvj haapq Jyenq Fiag Tauj zyepg Laaj scvb yetq uaq Nxi, Bovb nivq zyrug Zwrtq taaib.
8.9: mq paag uam Zxg yemj Jyenq luvb Diaq. nx'g Go lxd maiq tu'q txvj Ropg zyrug Rwrnj taaib Tauj Ravb Len. no-yaa cvj suv puad zipq pia'g Ravq.
8.16: “meib Zauj meib Eei aub Jweiq txnb Bwavd Zwrtq Ravq a'q.
8.4: Tauj Zyetq Laaj zyepg Zyetq uaq Nxi, Ravq zyrug tivb Jyenq aa-laa-latq keb Eei yetg nxm Bovb nivq.
8.10: ninb zuaq siag Nxi liud cvj puvj nx'g Go yem Ravq Zwrtq mivb.
8.22: “ta'faanb paamb ken Zxg yem Jyenq Eei zyavb hog, zwavj Eei Zunb Zyru Zauj syru Eei Zunb Zyru, Jwavq Eei zyavb hog Zauj yua'q Eei zyavb hog, tovb ken Zauj Zunb ken, luvb Nxi zang Zauj luvb mwrnd zang, yetg liud maiq haib Revg.”
8.12: ninb cvj zuaq siag Nxi liud zyrug puvj nx'g Go Zwrtq Rung. naaiq Rung nx'g Go maiq Rwrnj a'q.
8.13: no-yaa tu'q lua'g pc'q levb yetg Havj, zib Laaj scvb yetq uaq Nxi, Daub peib Eei uam Gaai mig a'q. no-yaa zyrug Zc'q Tov Ravb liub mavg pwatg Dau Gaai teij a'q.
8.1: Tinb huvb zuvq maiq la'Ku'q no-yaa yaag Zauj ninb yem Ravq uaq teij yetg zuvq scvb Kuq Yiab zxib. Tinb huvb pun Ryaauj pwrng Daub peib, uam zyrug haapq Jyenq Fiag.

9.18: yem Ravq Zwrtq taaib maaib no-yaa Eei txn, Buaj heug sem, haam, Zauj yaa-fetq. (haam se tovb Kaa-naa-an Eei tia.)
9.8: Tinb huvb kxvq Buaj no-yaa Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua,
9.3: yetg zuvq maaib mcvg haib tovd Eei ka'naaiq penj meib Bua Eei Eang hopq. ib zang yia zx'q Euvb Euvg Jiu pun meib Bua Navq zinb Daavg yia zx'q laib mcv laib miaq Jiu pun meib Bua uaq nx.
9.21: maaib Rung ninb hopq Wivj Eei a'vung tiuq Gwin mivb, lcvb kcvq Eei pweij Jyenq Dopg liub ka'Euad.
9.14: yia haiq zang pun Bwrnj om Jyenq Daub peib kub vwaaig yaag maaib Juv hing uaq Bwrnj,
9.23: sem Zauj yaa-fetq zyrug zx'q teij lwi Kwavj Jyenq ninb Bua Eei Ba'taub, Lwrtq Jyenq pia'g mivb, puvj lwi Fiag homg Jyenq ninb Bua Eei tia Eei sin, yaag maiq Win mavg ninb Bua Eei tia lcvb kcvq Eei sin.
9.6: “haiq taub taij myenb, pun Ryaamq lyrug Zwrtq, uaq taub zuvq zu'g myenb taij, pun Ryaamq lyrug Zwrtq, weig zu'g Tinb huvb zeij myenb, se zeij taaib zwavq ninb kanb.
9.2: ta'faanb yem Daub peib Eei scvb Kuq Zauj yem Daamb luvb Eei nx'g, Exv Daub peib Eei ka'naaiq Zauj yem Kxiq Eei Byaud xij kamb Riaj meib Bua. yia zx'q ninb Bua Jiu pun meib Bua kunq.
9.20: no-yaa penj zruj Deig Eei taaub taub myenb yaag zruj Wivj zwavj a'vung pyruq.
9.24: Ga'haaq no-yaa Rav taaib, hiuq tu'q ninb Eei txnb faij Navq haiq nx zruj pun ninb.
9.28: Byuvb swib imj yemj liud luvb Diaq, no-yaa Zxg zyavb tu'q faamb pc'q Mmd zyepg Havj.
9.7: meib Bua yaag xij zu'g maaib fu'Jweiq Zamq, Yaavj taaib maaib fun maaib fa'q Zamq Jyenq faauj pwavq luvb Diaq.”
9.29: ninb Eei Havb Jeiq zyavb tu'q Juaq pc'q Mmd zyepg Havj zyrug kwei seij mig a'q.
9.19: naaiq se no-yaa Eei pua taub txn. tovb naaiq teij txn pun Fiag Eei zeib fun Raanj mivb yem pwavq luvb Diaq.
9.17: Tinb huvb kxvq Buaj no-yaa, “naaiq se yia Zauj luvb Diaq yetg zuvq maaib mcvg Eei ka'naaiq lyepg vcvg waag Eei Javb hog.”
9.27: Toq Tinb huvb pun yaa-fetq Yaavj Jiad taaib, pun ninb tu'q yem sem Eei Dopg liub, yaag pun Kaa-naa-an zruj yaa-fetq Eei nrub kauq.”
9.11: yia xij Zauj meib Bua lyepg vcvg waag, yavb naaiq Jiaj yia yetg liud maiq lovg Byuvb swib imj yemj, myetg myenb maanb yetg zuvq maaib mcvg Eei ka'naaiq. yetg liud yaag maiq lovg Byuvb swib imj yemj waaig Daub peib.”
9.5: haiq taub hxig meib Bua Eei mcvg, yia zyrug pun uaq taub zu'g hxig mcvg taig. haiq taub scvb Kuq hxig meib Bua Eei mcvg, yia zyrug pun ninb zu'g hxig mcvg taig. haiq taub myenb hxig myenb Eei mcvg, yia pun uaq taub zu'g hxig mcvg taig.
9.9: “ib zang yia kanb Zauj meib Bua yaag Zauj meib Bua Eei zeib fun lyepg Jiad vcvg waag,
9.16: Juv hing yem uaq Bwrnj Zwrtq taaib, yia mavg pwatg zyrug Javj zu'g Tinb huvb Zauj luvb Diaq Euvb Euvg maaib mcvg Eei ka'naaiq yetg liud lyepg Jiad Eei vcvg waag.”
9.4: “mq paag maiq tuvq Eang maaib Ryaamq yem Jyenq Eei xq weig zu'g mcvg yem Ryaamq.
9.10: cvj Zauj meib yem yetg zuvq maaib mcvg Eei ka'naaiq, se nx'g Zauj yetg zuvq scvb Kuq Yiab zxib, ta'faanb yem Ravq Zwrtq taaib yem paamb ken maaib mcvg Eei ka'naaiq, lyepg Jiad vcvg waag.
9.22: haam, tovb Kaa-naa-an Eei tia uaq taub, pwatg ninb Eei tia lcvb kcvq Eei yem, ninb zyrug Zwrtq ka'Eiag Buaj ninb Eei i taub kxj.
9.12: Tinb huvb kxvq, “mavg maa'b! naaiq nxm Javb hog se yia Zauj meib Bua, yaag Zauj meib Bua yem naaiq Euvb Euvg maaib mcvg Eei ka'naaiq, lyepg Eei vcvg waag. se txig Jiaj txig yetg liud yem Eei vcvg waag.
9.15: yia zyrug Javj zu'g yia Zauj meib Bua Zauj Euvb Euvg maaib mcvg Eei ka'naaiq lyepg Eei vcvg waag. Byuvb swib imj yetg liud maiq cvj yemj, myetg yetg zuvq maaib mcvg Eei ka'naaiq a'q.
9.13: yia pun tiub Juv hing uaq Bwrnj. naaiq se yia Zauj paamb ken lyepg vcvg waag Eei Javb hog.
9.1: Tinb huvb pwav waag no-yaa Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua. ninb kxvq, “meib Bua xij zu'g maaib txnb Jweiq funb fa'q Yaavj taaib pwavq luvb Diaq.
9.26: ninb yaag kxvq, “xij zu'g Zev zyruq, sem Eei Tinb huvb. Toq pun Kaa-naa-an zruj sem Eei nrub kauq.
9.25: ninb zyrug kxvq, “Kaa-naa-an zu'g hruq a'q! ninb xij zu'g Tevj ninb Eei i taub kxj zruj kaub aiq Jiaj Eei nrub kauq.”

32.18: xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx tau. ‘tovb meib Eei pru, yaa-Kopq, Eei. ninb fuvj naaiq teij scvb Kuq taaib zruj zivb Eeig pun ninb Eei zyruq, e-saau. yaa-Kopq kanb yaag kan Jyenq Ga'haaq taaib.’+”
32.8: ninb yem Hruq Namq, “sij kxvq e-saau taaib zruj waaig taaub kwanb, ta'Eeig kwanb Zxg haib pyauj tu'q Dutq.”
32.3: yaa-Kopq Paaiq teij trug fyenj myenb mivb Daavg Tauj sej-i teig, e-Dom teib puv, lxd ninb Eei kxj, e-saau.
32.32: laaij yaa-Kopq zu'g uaq taub myenb mua'q ninb Eei Zamb zwib Buvq Pyatq mivb, yem naaig taaib Tauj ib zang, i-saa-laa-en myenb maiq Eang Zamb zwib Buvq Eei Jaan.
32.21: yaa-Kopq fuvj zivb Eeig mivb Daavg. ninb kanb c'q, cvj pweij mwrnd uaq Dopg liub Zyavq.
32.14: ninb zx'q Zwrtq Eig pc'q taub yuvb Eeid, Eig zyepg taub yuvb kruq, Zauj Eig pc'q taub pa'ki yuvb Eeid, Eig zyepg taub pa'ki yuvb kruq,
32.23: ninb cvj fuvj ninb Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq Jiaj Revg.
32.6: trug fyenj myenb Rwrnj Tauj yaa-Kopq uaq kxvq, “yia Bua Tauj meib Eei kxj e-saau uaq mig a'q. ib zang ninb taaib pwavb meib, cvj maaib feij pc'q taub myenb Zauj Jyenq ninb taaib.”
32.2: yaa-Kopq pwatg finb myenb ninb kxvq, “naaiq se Tinb huvb Eei pcv.” ninb zyrug Zwrtq uaq nxm txvj Eei Buaj heug maa-haa-naa-im.
32.20: meib Bua xij zu'g kxvq, ‘meib Eei pru, yaa-Kopq, kan Jyenq yia Bua Ga'haaq taaib.’+” weig zu'g yaa-Kopq yem Hruq Namq, “yia fuvj zivb Eeig mivb Daavg nund Jyenq ninb Eei Hruq. yia tu'q pwatg ninb Eei Myen Riaj ninb Zauj yia zruj hxpg mq pei.”
32.24: Kuvj zevg ninb kanb yem uaq Navq. cvj maaib taub myenb taaib Zauj ninb pxvd Jaaj Tauj luvb aaq lamb Fav.
32.28: uaq taub myenb kxvq, “yem naaiq mivb meib Eei Buaj maiq heug yaa-Kopq a'q. meib Eei Buaj heug i-saa-laa-en, weig zu'g meib Zauj Tinb huvb pxvd Jaaj yaag pxvd tu'q hivb. Zauj myenb pxvd Jaaj yaag pxvd tu'q hivb.”
32.7: yaa-Kopq kamb Riaj haig yaag Raub haig a'q, zyrug zx'q kan ninb taaib Eei myenb Zauj vovb kwanb, pa'ki yuvb kwanb, yuvb kwanb, Zauj lxb Txb pun Gxi zruj i kwanb.
32.29: yaa-Kopq kxvq, “Toq Buaj yia, meib Eei Buaj heug haiq Euvg?” mq paag ninb tau, “meib weig haiq tiug naaig yia Eei Buaj?” ninb zyrug yem uaq pwav waag yaa-Kopq.
32.19: yaa-Kopq Faauj zyavj ta'Eeig Zauj ta'faam cvj Zauj taub taub hxvb scvb Kuq Eei myenb, “pwavb e-saau Eei zyavb hog xij zu'g tovb Jruj waag kxvq.
32.17: yaa-Kopq yaag kxvq Buaj mivb Daavg uaq taub, “pwavb zu'g yia Eei kxj, e-saau, uaq zang, ninb naaig kaaj meib, ‘meib Eei zyruq tovb haiq taub?’ Zauj ‘meib mivb haaij? mivb Daavg naaiq teij scvb Kuq se haiq taub Eei?’
32.31: yaa-Kopq Jiaj pe-ni-en uaq zang, Ba'Nxi Zwrtq taaib a'q. ninb zyrug la'Baib la'Bai Eei mivb a'q, laaij ninb Eei Zamb zwib Buvq Pyatq mivb.
32.30: yaa-Kopq kxvq, “yia Myen txij Myen pwatg liud Tinb huvb, yia Zxg maaib mcvg zyavb Eei.” ninb zyrug Zwrtq uaq nxm txvj Eei Buaj heug pe-ni-en.
32.27: uaq taub myenb naaig kaaj, “meib Eei Buaj heug haiq Euvg?” ninb tau, “yia heug yaa-Kopq.”
32.11: Toq meib Fruj yia pyauj Dutq yia Eei kxj, e-saau, Eei puab Diaq weig zu'g yia kamb Riaj ninb xij taaib taij Revg yia Bua, lyemb msia'q txn Zauj fu'Jweiq taij Revg.
32.5: yia maaib vovb, lxb, pa'ki yuvb Zauj yuvb, maaib nrub kauq nrub peid. yia Paaiq myenb mivb Buaj meib, yia Eei zyruq, Toq meib Gxi fim Gxi eij pun yia.’+”
32.9: yaa-Kopq tauj kauj kxvq, “yia Eei ov, apg-laa-ham, Eei Tinb huvb Zauj yia Eei tia, i-sakg, Eei Tinb huvb aag. o zyruq, meib Buaj yia Rwrnj yia kanb Eei pwrnb teib puv, yia Eei Zyenb Ze'q muab txig Eei txvj. meib yaag xij pun yia tu'q lovj.
32.16: ninb pun Gxi yetg Euvg zruj yetg kwanb, yetg kwanb pun yetg taub pru kruj. ninb cvj Buaj pru, “meib xij zu'g hxvb scvb Kuq mivb Daavg yia. yetg kwanb Zauj yetg kwanb xij zu'g leib saa teij.”
32.4: ninb yaag Faauj zyavj waag ninb Bua. ninb kxvq, “meib Bua xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx Buaj yia Eei zyruq, e-saau, og. Buaj ninb, ‘meib Eei pru, yaa-Kopq, kxvq, yia mivb Zauj laa-Baan yem Tauj ib zang.
32.10: yia maiq Pwij meib Dovg naaiq Kxb lyenb, zyepg zua'q Eei zruj pun yia, meib Eei pru. Jiaj Jx-Dcn Daaib uaq zang yia Kuvj maaib Du'g tiub pyaab Byaag Navq. ib zang yia cvj Rwrnj maaib naaiq teij i kwanb myenb Zauj scvb Kuq.
32.22: uaq mwrnd yaa-Kopq Jiad sin txb ninb Eei i taub auq, i taub nrub peid, Zauj ninb Eei zyepg yetq taub fu'Jweiq, yavb yapq-Bxkg Daaib Eei Jaub prug Jiaj uaq vaang zi'g yapq-Bxkg Daaib.
32.12: zyruq kxvq Jiaj, ‘yia xij pun meib tu'q lovj yaag pun meib Eei zeib fun Dovg Kxib Len Eei saab zyru Zamq, zuvq saauq maiq zyend.’+”
32.15: Zauj faab zyepg taub lxb Txb txb Jyenq txn Eei, Zauj feij zyepg taub vovb Eeid, zyepg taub vovb kruq, Zauj Eig zyepg taub lxb Eeid, zyepg taub lxb kruq.
32.13: uaq mwrnd yaa-Kopq hitq uaq nxm txvj. ninb kinq Zwrtq teij ninb maaib Eei ka'naaiq zruj zivb Eeig pun ninb Eei kxj, e-saau.
32.1: yaa-Kopq kan Jyenq Jauq mivb uaq zang, maaib teij Tinb huvb Eei finb myenb taaib pwavb ninb.
32.26: uaq taub myenb kxvq, “puvj yia maa'b! luvb Fav a'q nyaa.” yaa-Kopq tau, “meib maiq pwav waag yia nx, yia maiq puvj meib.”
32.25: uaq taub myenb haid ninb pxvd maiq hivb yaa-Kopq, ninb zyrug mua'q yaa-Kopq Eei Zamb zwib Buvq Pyatq mivb.

21.18: Jiad sin mivb Lxpq ninb taaib nanq Jyenq puad, weig zu'g yia xij pun ninb penj yetg kua'q Lo Eei.”
21.8: uaq taub txn Lo teij a'q. Tauj kwavg Exj Eei Nxi apg-laa-ham Beng Eang Beng hopq Lo Eei hrug ninb Eei txn kwavg Exj.
21.33: apg-laa-ham yem uaq Be-e-Qe-Baa zwavj zuvb linb lyrud Dyavj, cvj yem uaq kxvq Zwrtq zyruq Eei Buaj zavg zyruq, tovb yetg liud yem Eei Tinb huvb.
21.3: saa-laa yuvd pun ninb uaq taub txn, apg-laa-ham Zwrtq Buaj heug i-sakg.
21.32: yem Be-e-Qe-Baa lyepg liud vcvg waag, aa-Bi-me-lekq Zauj ninb Eei tomb pcvb pyeiq, fi-Ko, Rwrnj fi-li-saa-tia teib puv.
21.21: ninb yem paa-laan teib puvb Waav. ninb Eei maa mivb kxvq taub i-yipq sia'q pun ninb lovg zruj auq.
21.14: ta'Eeig Dxm Ryruq Eei, apg-laa-ham Jiad sin taaib, zx'q teij Fuaq Zauj yetg Dopg Bua'g uam pun haa-kaa pwij Jyenq zyrug pun ninb txb Jyenq uaq taub txn Zwrtq pyauq mivb mig a'q. haa-kaa zyrug leib uaq nxm txvj mivb Tauj Be-e-Qe-Baa teib puvb Waav Jiaj naaiq Jiaj uaq Eei.
21.23: meib xij zu'g yem naaiq zyavq Jyenq Tinb huvb lcvd meib maiq zruj haiq Euvg txvg yia fai yia Eei txnb Jweiq funb fa'q. yia Navq haiq nx zruj lovj pun meib, meib yaag xij zu'g Navq uaq nx zruj lovj pun yia Zauj meib ib zang yem Jyenq naaiq Eei teib puv.”
21.6: saa-laa kxvq, “Tinb huvb pun yia Kub Jyetq. haiq taub haid yaag xij Kub Jyetq.”
21.34: apg-laa-ham Zxg yem uaq fi-li-saa-tia teib puv laub Eei.
21.2: apg-laa-ham Havb Jeiq koj uaq zang, saa-laa maaib kub vwaad, yuvd tu'q taub txn pun apg-laa-ham txij Revg Tinb huvb lcvd Eei zyavb hog.
21.20: Tinb huvb Zauj uaq taub txn yem. ninb Lo taaib yem teib puvb Waav cvj penj taub pwrnq xq henq Eei myenb.
21.24: apg-laa-ham kxvq, “yia zyavq Jyenq Tinb huvb lcvd a'q.”
21.28: apg-laa-ham yem ninb Eei pa'ki yuvb kwanb kinq Zwrtq siag taub pa'ki yuvb zeig txn pun Gxi txvj yem.
21.7: ninb cvj kxvq, “haiq taub kaamq kxvq Buaj apg-laa-ham, saa-laa haib maaib kub vwaad hopq Exj? apg-laa-ham koj haig a'q, mq paag yia yuvd tu'q taub txn pun ninb mig a'q.”

21.19: kxvq liud, Tinb huvb pun haa-kaa pwatg nxm uamb Kwrtq. haa-kaa zyrug mivb zaavb uam pwavq Dopg Bua'g pun ninb Eei txn hopq.
21.17: Tinb huvb haid naaiq taub txn Eyemq. Tinb huvb Eei finb myenb yem kub vwaaig luvb heug, “haa-kaa aag, meib weig haiq tiug Dovg naaig Raub? maiq tuvq kamb Riaj og. naaiq taub txn pweij Jyenq uaq Dau Eyemq, Tinb huvb haid mig a'q.

6.18: mq paag yia xij Zauj meib lcvd Jiad vcvg waag. meib xij zu'g txb meib Eei aub Jweiq txnb Bwavd Zauj meib pia'g Ravq.

6.2: maaib teij tob myenb txn pwatg paamb myenb Eei sia'q Rweig. ninb Bua yaag kinq teij lovg zruj auq.

15.20: hitq-Tai myenb, pe-litq-si myenb, le-faa-im myenb,
15.17: Ba'Nxi mwrtq, luvb Mwavj Revg mig a'q. maaib nxm trub lrub Zwrtq trub syruj Zauj kwaaj trub paaq Zwrtq taaib kan Jyenq uaq teij i puv xq Bu'Dovj Jiaj.

20.16: ninb cvj kxvq Buaj saa-laa, “yia zx'q siag Jxib Eaanb taaib pun meib Eei kxj zruj Raauj Myen Eaanb, pun Zauj meib yem Eei myenb hiuq tu'q meib za'kevb maiq txvg. haiq taub zyrug hiuq tu'q meib maiq zruj txvg haiq Euvg.”

20.15: aa-Bi-me-lekq Buaj apg-laa-ham, “mavg kaaj! yia Eei teib puv yem meib Eei Ra'Myen. meib xij yem haaij, kunq yem a'q.”
20.11: apg-laa-ham tau, “yia laaig yem naaiq maiq maaib haiq taub kamb Riaj Tinb huvb. Riaj ninb Bua xij taij yia weig tu'q yia Eei auq.
20.1: apg-laa-ham yem mam-le Eei tomb Ba'ov zwei Dyavb lomg swiq mivb Tauj ne-kepg, Kaa-Detg zivb Zauj su-waa teig Bu'Dovj, yem trug ke-laa-aa muvq.
20.10: aa-Bi-me-lekq cvj naaig apg-laa-ham, “meib weig haiq tiug Navq naaiq nx zruj?”

5.18: yaa-letq tu'q yetg pc'q lua'g zyepg Eeig Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug e-nokq.
5.8: setg Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q Juaq pc'q zyepg Eeig Havj, ninb zyrug kwei seij mig a'q.
5.3: aa-Dam tu'q yetg pc'q faab zyepg Havj, ninb cvj tu'q taub txn taaib zwavq ninb, yaag Tevj Zwrtq Buaj heug setg.
5.32: no-yaa zyavb tu'q Mmd pc'q Havj Zivj tu'q pua taub txn, Buaj heug sem, haam Zauj yaa-fetq.
5.21: e-nokq tu'q lua'g zyepg Mmd Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug me-Tu-sej-laa.
5.14: Ke-nan Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q Juaq pc'q levb zyepg Havj zyrug kwei seij mig a'q.
5.23: e-nokq Eei syrug Ewrnb zyavb tu'q faamb pc'q lua'g zyepg Mmd Havj.
5.6: setg tu'q yetg pc'q levb pyaa Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug e-notq.
5.2: ninb zeij penj mJavg msia'q yaag Zeij fu'q pun ninb Bua, cvj Tevj Zwrtq Buaj heug “paamb myenb.”
5.20: yaa-letq Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q Juaq pc'q lua'g zyepg Eeig Havj zyrug kwei seij mig a'q.
5.24: e-nokq zanb zang Zauj Tinb huvb Jiu Tov, Tinb huvb txb ninb mivb mig a'q. zyav naaig maiq pwatg mig a'q.
5.28: laa-mekq tu'q yetg pc'q petq zyepg Eeig Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn taaib,
5.7: yem tu'q liud e-notq, ninb zyavb tu'q petq pc'q levb siag Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
5.29: Tevj ninb Zwrtq Buaj heug no-yaa. ninb kxvq, “weig zu'g zyruq hruq Dau, yia Bua xij zu'g lovg puad zruj kov Kruq. naaiq taub txn haib Tevj yia Bua Eei kovb pru hev teij.”
5.19: yem tu'q liud e-nokq, ninb cvj zyavb tu'q petq pc'q Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
5.17: maa-haa-laa-len Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q petq pc'q Juaq zyepg Mmd Havj zyrug kwei seij mig a'q.
5.31: laa-mekq Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q Zyetq pc'q Zyetq zyepg Zyetq Havj zyrug kwei seij mig a'q.
5.30: laa-mekq tu'q liud no-yaa, ninb cvj zyavb tu'q Mmd pc'q Juaq zyepg Mmd Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
5.27: me-Tu-sej-laa Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q Juaq pc'q lua'g zyepg Juaq Havj zyrug kwei seij mig a'q.
5.11: e-notq Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q Juaq pc'q levb pyaa Havj, ninb zyrug kwei seij mig a'q.
5.5: aa-Dam Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q Juaq pc'q faab zyepg Havj zyrug kwei seij mig a'q.
5.9: e-notq tu'q Juaq zyepg Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug Ke-nan.
5.16: tu'q liud yaa-letq, ninb cvj zyavb tu'q petq pc'q faab zyepg Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
5.4: yem tu'q liud setg, aa-Dam cvj zyavb tu'q petq pc'q Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
5.10: yem tu'q liud Ke-nan, ninb zyavb tu'q petq pc'q zyepg Mmd Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
5.22: tu'q liud naaiq taub txn, e-nokq Zauj Tinb huvb hxpg Hruq Jiu Tov faamb pc'q Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
5.12: Ke-nan tu'q Zyetq zyepg Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug maa-haa-laa-len.
5.15: maa-haa-laa-len tu'q lua'g zyepg Mmd Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug yaa-letq.
5.13: tu'q liud maa-haa-laa-len, ninb cvj zyavb tu'q petq pc'q feij zyepg Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
5.1: naaiq se aa-Dam Eei zeib fun Eei trub zov taan. Tinb huvb zeij myenb taaib uaq zang, ninb zeij taaib zwavq ninb kanb.
5.26: yem tu'q liud laa-mekq, ninb cvj zyavb tu'q Zyetq pc'q petq zyepg Eeig Havj, Zxg maaib txn maaib sia'q Eei.
5.25: me-Tu-sej-laa tu'q yetg pc'q petq zyepg Zyetq Havj, ninb tu'q taub txn, Buaj heug laa-mekq.

19.18: mq paag lotq tau, “tomb kxj aa'b! Toq maiq tuvq Navq naaig.
19.8: mavg kaaj! yia maaib i taub sia'q maiq kcvb pweij Jiaj txn. yia txb ninb Bua Zwrtq taaib pun meib Bua sweib eij zruj. mq paag maiq tuvq zruj haiq Euvg pun naaiq teij mJavg txn. ninb Bua taaib yem yia Eei pyauq, yia xij zu'g kruj lovj peu Jyenq ninb Bua.”
19.33: uaq mwrnd ninb Bua i muab sia'q pun ninb Bua Eei tia hopq a'vung tiuq, sia'g Lo zyrug pia'g mivb Zauj ninb Eei tia pweij. tia zuvq maiq hiuq tu'q ninb Eei sia'q zyavb haaij pweij, zyavb haaij Jiad sin mivb.
19.3: mq paag lotq Qa'q! Toq, ninb Bua zyrug Zauj Jyenq lotq Rwrnj, pia'g ninb Eei pyauq. lotq liug leid Eang hopq, zi'q maiq an pivq Eei Fuaq, ninb Bua zyrug Eang a'q.
19.32: Bua xij zu'g pun aa tia hopq tiuq Gwin mivb, Bua zyrug haib Zauj ninb pweij, weig pavg Bua Eei tia maaib hod paan.”
19.21: finb myenb kxvq Buaj lotq, “meib Toq Eei yia Gxi Rwib. yia zyrug maiq myetg meib kxvq uaq nxm muvq.
19.35: uaq mwrnd ninb Bua zyrug pun ninb Bua Eei tia cvj hopq a'vung tiuq. sia'g faij zyrug pia'g mivb Zauj ninb Eei tia pweij. ninb Eei tia fib Navq Eei maiq hiuq tu'q ninb Eei sia'q zyavb haaij pweij zyavb haaij Jiad sin.
19.14: lotq zyrug Zwrtq mivb Buaj kxvq zyavb ninb Eei sia'q uaq teij sia'g laavb, “kaanq syepq teij pyauj. zyruq xij myetg naaiq nxm zivb haig a'q.” mq paag ninb Eei laavb Bua laaig ninb kxvq Jyetq a'Ryaaug Navq.
19.23: lotq mivb Tauj soj-aa zivb uaq zang, Ba'Nxi Zwrtq taaib a'q.
19.6: lotq Zwrtq kcvb Ka'Dau, zx'q kcvb kwrn Jyenq,
19.34: ta'Eeig Nxi sia'g Lo kxvq Buaj sia'g faij, “a'Mwavj yia Zauj aa tia pweij liud a'q. ib mwrnd Bua xij zu'g cvj pun ninb hopq a'vung tiuq, meib yaag mivb Zauj ninb pweij weig pavg Bua Eei tia maaib hod paan.”
19.2: kxvq, “tomb kxj aag, Toq meib Bua taaib hitq yia, meib Eei pru, Eei pyauq. haib Raauj zauj, pweij mwrnd, Fav Dxm Jiad sin Ryruq Eei mtaaib mivb.” ninb Bua tau, “maiq zu'g a'q. yia Bua pweij naaiq zivb Eei tomb zwavj zaamg yaag tu'q Eei.”
19.36: Navq naaiq nx lotq Eei i taub sia'q maaib Jyenq ninb Bua kanb Eei tia Eei kub vwaad.
19.20: mavg maa'b! uaq Dau maaib nxm muvq faij Eei, fatq Eei, haib Tiuj tu'q Tauj Eei. Toq pun yia pyauj mivb uaq. penj yetg nxm fiub muvq Navq maiq zeid? Navq naaig zyrug tu'q yia Eei mcvg Zwrtq.”
19.24: zyruq lyemb zeib pun zia'g Jyenq trud Eei huvb yem kub vwaaig luvb Fiag soj-Dom Zauj ko-mo-laa zivb,
19.28: mavg Fiag. ninb pwatg soj-Dom Zauj ko-mo-laa Zauj uaq nxm hxvg Zwrtq trub syrub ton Zutg Zutq Eei faauj Navq puaq tomb trub Raug nx.
19.7: Buaj uaq teij myenb, “kxb yrud aa'b! Toq meib Bua maiq tuvq Navq naaiq nx zruj. maiq tuvq zruj naaiq Euvg waaig haig Eei sig.
19.29: Navq naaig, Tinb huvb myetg uaq nxm hxvg zavg Eei zivb, lyemb lotq yem Eei zivb, uaq zang, ninb Javj zu'g apg-laa-ham Zivj taaib txb lotq pyauj Zwrtq, maiq zu'g taig.
19.19: ziuj meib pwatg yia, meib Eei pru, zruj tu'q hxpg meib Eei Hruq, meib yaag zruj lovj pun yia, Fruj Zwrtq yia Eei mcvg. yia maiq haib pyauj maiq Tauj Bov. Riaj yia pyauj maiq Dutq naaiq teij tomb ze'g naang, yia zyrug taig a'q.
19.17: pyauj Zwrtq zi'g zivb mivb, maaib taub uaq teij finb myenb kxvq, “kaanq pyauj maa'b! maiq tuvq Win mavg Ga'haaq, lyemb maiq tuvq tivb naaiq Daub pcvb Eei haiq nxm txvj. Govb pyauj mivb uaq Jiaj Bov. maiq zei c'q, xij zu'g taig a'q.”
19.38: sia'g faij yaag yuvd tu'q taub txn, Tevj Zwrtq Buaj heug Ben-am-mi. Ben-am-mi se zruj ib Jaaj Nxi am-mon myenb Eei ovb Taaib vc'q.
19.31: sia'g Lo Buaj sia'g faij, “Bua Eei tia koj a'q. yem naaiq pua'q Dau maiq maaib myenb taaib lovg Bua Navq luvb Diaq myenb lovg nx.
19.30: weig zu'g lotq kamb Riaj, maiq kaamq yem soj-aa zivb, ninb Zauj ninb Eei i taub sia'q pyauj faauj Bov, yem nxm Bcvb Kwrtq ka'Euad.
19.27: ta'Eeig Dxm Ryruq Eei, apg-laa-ham mivb Tauj, tovb ninb sruq Jyenq yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen uaq nxm txvj,
19.11: ninb Bua cvj zruj pun yem ka'Eiag zi'g kcvb Eei yetg zuvq myenb kob koj lunb lunj Eei mziv Buaq Revg zyrug Waaj naaiq Waaj uaq yaag lxd maiq pwatg kcvb.
19.5: ninb Bua heug lotq, “ib mwrnd taaib meib naaiq uaq teij i taub myenb yem haaij? txb Zwrtq taaib pun yia Bua Zaa maa'b!”
19.9: zwavj myenb kxvq, “simq Gxi maa'b!” cvj kxvq, “naaiq taub loq yem kanb nxm txvj taaib zyrug yia Bua yem. ib zang zuvq xij Tevj yia Bua zruj syemq zwid Jyen. yia Bua xij zruj pun meib kaub Kruq zruj pun uaq teij i taub.” ninb Bua Fiag Qa'q fovq lotq laatg Raatg mivb Tauj kcvb Daavg xij Bx'q kcvb Tov.
19.16: lotq Zxg samb samb so'g so'q Eei. uaq teij i taub myenb zyrug zx'q lotq Bua i Mwavq Zauj ninb Bua Eei i taub sia'q Eei puad Ken Jyenq Zwrtq ka'Eiag zi'g zivb mivb, weig zu'g zyruq Kxb lyenb ninb.
19.37: sia'g Lo yuvd tu'q taub txn, Tevj Zwrtq Buaj heug mo-apg. mo-apg zruj ib Jaaj Nxi mo-apg myenb Eei ovb Taaib vc'q.
19.4: naaiq teij i taub myenb maiq kcvb pweij, soj-Dom zivb Eei mJavg txn kob koj lunb lunj taaib Rxib, maiq zevg yetg taub, weib Jyenq lotq Eei pyauq.
19.10: mq paag uaq teij i taub Kc'q myenb Haa puad Zwrtq taaib zx'q lotq Tx pia'g pyauq mivb, zx'q kcvb kwrn Jyenq.
19.22: kaanq Tiuj Jyenq mivb uaq a'q. meib mivb maiq kcvb Tauj uaq nxm txvj, yia maiq haib Fiag puad zruj haiq Euvg.” weig naaiq myenb zyrug Zwrtq naaiq nxm zivb Eei Buaj heug “soj-aa.”
19.12: uaq teij i taub myenb Buaj lotq, “yem naaiq Zxg maaib haiq taub meib Eei myenb fai? maiq kunq txn fai sia'q, sia'g laavb fai yem naaiq zivb meib Eei haiq taub myenb, meib xij zu'g txb ninb Bua pyauj Zwrtq.
19.15: ta'Eeig Dxm luvb Fav, finb myenb pe'q lotq. ninb Bua kxvq, “kaanq syepq teij maa'b! txb Jyenq meib Eei auq cvj Zauj meib yem naaiq Eei i taub sia'q pyauj Gxi. maiq zei c'q, naaiq nxm zivb zu'g tivg zwid zu'g myetg, meib Bua yaag Zauj Jyenq zu'g taig a'q.”
19.13: yia Bua xij myetg soj-Dom zivb weig zu'g zyruq haid koj naaiq nxm zivb Eei waag Zamq haig a'q. ninb zyrug Paaiq yia Bua taaib myetg.”
19.1: uaq teij i taub finb myenb mivb Tauj soj-Dom zivb uaq zang, luvb maanb Mwavj a'q. lotq zweid Jyenq uaq zivb kcvb Daavg. yetq pwatg ninb Bua i taub ninb Jiad sin mivb zipq, zyrug Pua'q Fiag Dau
19.26: mq paag lotq Eei auq yem Ga'haaq Win Rwrnj mavg zyrug penj nxm Raub tovg mig a'q.
19.25: puaq myetg Revg uaq nxm hxvg zavg Eei zivb, lyemb myenb, lyemb Dau Zwrtq Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq.

38.18: yu-Daa naaig kaaj, “meib xij yia tivg haiq Euvg Daavg kaub lovj?” Taa-maa kxvq, “xij zu'g pun meib Eei yenj Zauj Diuj yenj Eei Laav cvj Zauj meib ib zang nanq Jyenq naaiq tiub pyaab Byaag.” yu-Daa zyrug zx'q taaib pun ninb mig a'q. pun Jyenq zyrug Zauj ninb pweij. Ga'haaq Taa-maa maaib Jyenq yu-Daa Eei kub vwaad a'q.
38.8: yu-Daa cvj kxvq Buaj o-nan, “meib xij zu'g mivb Zauj meib Eei Eaam pweij weig zruj yrud Eei leib Eeig, tu'q fu'Jweiq Tevj meib Eei kxj maaib hod txig zeib fun.”
38.3: ninb Eei auq zyrug maaib Jyenq sin a'q, yuvd tu'q taub txn, Zwrtq Buaj heug e-aa.
38.21: ninb zyrug naaig kaaj uaq nxm txvj Eei myenb, “yem e-naa-im muvq Eei Jaub Len uaq taub maaig pwrnb sin Eei msia'q txn Jiaj haaij mig a'q.” ninb Bua tau, “yem naaiq maiq maaib maaig pwrnb sin Eei msia'q txn.”
38.14: Taa-maa zyrug yeng Gxi ninb Eei aub kwaaq lwib hruj, zx'q Kwaaiq Dia pwij Jyenq, Byxvd Jyenq Myen. zxv zyavj, ninb zweid Jyenq mivb Tim-naa-haa Eei Jaub Len, pia'g e-naa-im muvq Eei zivb kcvb Daavg. ninb hiuq tu'q yu-Daa Eei txnb laai, Qe-laa, Lo a'q, mq paag yu-Daa maiq pun ninb lovg.
38.23: yu-Daa kxvq, “uaq teij ka'naaiq Zinb ninb lovg a'q. Riaj myenb xij Jyetq Bua mq pei. txb yuvb txn mivb xij pun yaag lxd maiq pwatg ninb pun.”
38.6: yu-Daa Tevj ninb Eei txnb Lo, e-aa, lxd tu'q taub auq, Buaj heug Taa-maa.
38.2: yem uaq yu-Daa pwavb taub Kaa-naa-an myenb, Qu-aa, Eei sia'q, zyrug lovg zruj auq. lovg Jyenq,
38.20: yu-Daa Buaj ninb Eei lob kcv txig, uaq taub aa-Dun-lam myenb, hi-laa, txb yuvb txn mivb zua'g ninb tivg uaq teij ka'naaiq Rwrnj. hi-laa mivb kau, lxd maiq pwatg uaq taub msia'q txn.
38.24: Ga'haaq aaq lamb teij pua Laaj Eia'g Eei txvj, maaib myenb Buaj yu-Daa, “meib Eei Bwavd, Taa-maa, Yenj Goj. ib zang Txi kub vwaad a'q.” yu-Daa kxvq, “txb ninb Zwrtq taaib puaq kwavg maa'b!”
38.28: mun Jyenq uaq zang, maaib taub Eei puad Zwrtq Daavg. kruj Taa-maa uaq taub msia'q txn zx'q tiub feib si'q Dob Jyenq kub vwaad Eei puab seib Jaav cvj kxvq, “naaiq taub Zwrtq seij Daavg.”
38.7: mq paag ziuj zyruq mavg, e-aa waaig haig. zyruq zyrug pun ninb taig mig a'q.
38.29: mq paag kub vwaad cvj Lwrtq ninb Eei puad pia'g, ta'Eeig taub zyrug yuvd Zwrtq Daavg. kruj Taa-maa uaq taub msia'q txn kxvq, “zruj haiq Euvg meib Bevj Zwrtq Daavg lcb?” uaq taub txn ninb Bua zyrug Zwrtq Buaj heug pe-letq.
38.19: Taa-maa Rwrnj mivb zx'q Gxi Byxvd Myen Eei Dia cvj zu'q Jyenq ninb Eei aub kwaaq Eei lwib hruj Navq lod uaq nx.
38.17: yu-Daa tau, “yia xij zx'q taub yia Eei yuvb kwanb Eei yuvb txn pun meib.” Taa-maa tau, “meib xij lovg haiq Euvg tivg Jyenq Daavg Tauj meib fuvj yuvb txn taaib?”
38.30: Dob Jyenq feib si'q uaq taub txn Ga'haaq yuvd yaag Zwrtq Buaj heug ze-laa.
38.27: Tauj yuvd Eei zyavb hog pwatg Taa-maa maaib suvb kub vwaad.
38.11: yu-Daa kxvq Buaj ninb Eei Bwavd, Taa-maa, “Rwrnj mivb Zauj meib Eei tia yem a'q. meib xij zu'g zruj aub kwaaq zuaq yia Eei txn, Qe-laa, Lo taaib.” yu-Daa Navq naaiq nx kxvq weig zu'g ninb yem Hruq Namq Raub heij Qe-laa taig Navq ninb Eei kxj Bua nx. Taa-maa zyrug Rwrnj ninb Eei tia Eei pyauq mig a'q.
38.5: Ga'haaq cvj yuvd taub txn, Zwrtq Buaj heug Qe-laa. Qe-laa Zwrtq seij uaq zang yu-Daa yem Ke-sipq.
38.9: o-nan hiuq tu'q yuvd tu'q fu'Jweiq mq paag maiq funj ninb Eei pwrng. Navq naaig, haiq zang Zauj ninb Eei Eaam pweij, ninb tu'g eij puvj ninb Eei Eim Dxtq ka'Diaq Dau weig maiq pun kxj maaib hod txig zeib fun.
38.16: yu-Daa mivb uaq Jaub Len Zauj ninb kxvq waag. ninb kxvq, “taaib maa'b! pun yia Zauj meib pweij og.” yu-Daa maiq hiuq tu'q se ninb Eei Bwavd. Taa-maa naaig, “yia Zauj meib pweij, meib pun haiq Euvg yia?”
38.4: ninb Eei auq cvj maaib ta'Eeig Rung sin, yuvd tu'q taub txn, Zwrtq Buaj heug o-nan.
38.10: ziuj zyruq mavg, o-nan zruj Eei sig se waaig haig. zyruq yaag pun ninb taig mig a'q.
38.22: hi-laa zyrug Rwrnj mivb Buaj yu-Daa, “yia lxd maiq pwatg uaq taub msia'q txn. yem uaq Eei myenb yaag kxvq yem naaig maiq maaib Jiaj maaig pwrnb sin Eei msia'q txn.”
38.12: Jiaj taaib, yu-Daa Eei auq, Qu-aa Eei sia'q, kwei seij mig a'q. zuaq Raub Eei zyavb hog Jiaj liud, yu-Daa Zauj ninb Eei lob kcv txig, aa-Dun-lam myenb, hi-laa, mivb Tim-naa-haa, maaib myenb Tevj Japq ninb Eei pa'ki yuvb pyei uaq nxm txvj.
38.15: yu-Daa pwatg Taa-maa, laaig ninb zruj maaig pwrnb sin Eei msia'q txn, weig zu'g ninb maaib Dia Byxvd Jyenq Myen.
38.13: maaib myenb Buaj Taa-maa, “meib Eei ovb puag xij mivb Tim-naa-haa Japq pa'ki yuvb pyei.”
38.1: tovb uaq zang, yu-Daa leib Gxi ninb Eei muab txig, pyauj mivb kan taub aa-Dun-lam myenb, Buaj heug hi-laa.
38.26: yu-Daa zia'q tu'q naaiq teij ka'naaiq se ninb Eei. ninb kxvq, “naaiq taub msia'q txn zruj Eei se kaub hxpg yia zruj Eei, weig zu'g yia maiq pun ninb lovg yia Eei txn, Qe-laa.” Ga'haaq yu-Daa yetg liud maiq Zauj ninb pweij.
38.25: txb Taa-maa Zwrtq taaib uaq zang, Taa-maa Jwij waag mivb Buaj ninb Eei ovb puag, “Yenj yia Txi kub vwaad se tovb naaiq teij ka'naaiq Eei zyruq. lovb lovj Eei mavg kaaj. naaiq nxm yenj, Laav Zauj pyaab Byaag se haiq taub Eei?”

31.18: yaag zung Jyenq scvb Kuq mivb Daavg. cvj txb Jyenq ninb yem patg-Daan-aa-lam zxng tu'q taaib Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq Zwrtq Jauq Rwrnj Kaa-naa-an teib puv, ninb Eei tia, i-sakg, uaq.
31.45: yaa-Kopq zyrug zx'q nxm la'pyeiq lyepg Jiad taaib ton Jyenq zruj Javb hog,
31.3: zyruq kxvq Buaj yaa-Kopq, “Rwrnj meib Eei Zyenb Ze'q Eei teib puv uaq og. yia xij Zauj meib yem.”
31.43: laa-Baan tau yaa-Kopq, “naaiq teij sia'q se yia Eei sia'q. naaiq teij fu'Jweiq yaag yia Eei. naaiq teij yuvb kwanb Zauj pa'ki yuvb kwanb yaag yia Eei. meib pwatg Jyenq Eei yetg zuvq se yia Eei. ib Nxi yia haib zruj haiq Euvg Tevj yia Eei sia'q Zauj ninb Bua Eei fu'Jweiq?
31.50: sij kxvq meib zruj to'g yia Eei sia'q, fai Zwrtq liud yia Eei sia'q meib cvj kanb lovg taub auq, maiq kunq yia maiq hiuq, Javj Jyenq og, maaib Tinb huvb Tevj meib Zauj yia zruj zxvb zevj.”
31.14: laa-sen Zauj le-aa tau yaa-Kopq, “yia Bua Eei tia Eei Jaab tivb ib zang zuvq maiq maaib yia Bua Ripg Eei pwrng.
31.48: laa-Baan kxvq, “ib Nxi naaiq Dwi la'pyeiq zruj Bua i taub Eei zxvb zevj.” weig naaiq uaq nxm txvj heug kaa-le-etg.
31.34: laa-sen zx'q uaq teij yem pyauq zavg Eei miub favj tapq Jyenq lxb Txb Eei txj. ninb kanb c'q, zweid Jyenq kub vwaaig. laa-Baan sru Revg laa-sen Eei Dopg liub mq paag lxd maiq pwatg.
31.2: yaa-Kopq yaag zia'q tu'q laa-Baan Eei eij leid maiq Navq zinb Daavg uaq nx, Pyruj Zamq haig a'q.
31.36: yaa-Kopq Qiaj Jiad haig zyrug kxvq laa-Baan, “yia zruj haiq Euvg txvg meib, zi'g zwid meib, meib Zivj Qa'q zung Jyenq yia taaib?
31.35: laa-sen kxvq Buaj ninb Eei tia, “aa tia aag, meib maiq tuvq nrud yia og. yia hxpg zu'g Jiad sin zipq tia, mq paag yia Eei sinb yeng Tauj, yia Jiad maiq tu'q sin.” laa-Baan sru Revg ka'naaiq yaag lxd maiq pwatg ninb yem pyauq zavg Eei miub favj.
31.24: uaq mwrnd laa-Baan Beij pwatg Tinb huvb taaib kxvq Buaj ninb, “faij fim og. maiq kunq lovj fai Zyruq, maiq tuvq kxvq haiq Euvg pun yaa-Kopq.”
31.7: mq paag meib Bua Eei tia Zxg Pyenj yia. ninb Tiuq yia Eei kovb zinb tu'q zyepg Rung a'q. mq paag Tinb huvb maiq pun ninb zruj haiq Euvg hxig yia.
31.17: yaa-Kopq zyrug Beng zyavj ka'naaiq. ninb pun ninb Eei aub Jweiq keb Jyenq lxb Txb,
31.49: cvj tu'q Buaj heug mitq-paa, weig zu'g laa-Baan kxvq, “Bua leib Gxi txig mq paag Toq zyruq yem meib Zauj yia Bua Bu'Dovj zuaq Jyenq.
31.11: Beij pwatg Jyenq Eei zyavb hog, Tinb huvb Eei finb myenb heug yia, ‘yaa-Kopq aag.’ yia tau, ‘oij! yia yem naaiq og.’
31.33: laa-Baan zyrug pia'g yaa-Kopq Eei Dopg liub Zauj le-aa Eei Dopg liub Zauj uaq teij i taub nrub peid Eei Dopg liub sru mq paag sru maiq Zwrtq ninb Eei miub favj. ninb yem le-aa Eei Dopg liub Zwrtq taaib cvj pia'g laa-sen Eei Dopg liub.
31.16: Tinb huvb pun meib tu'q yia Bua Eei tia Eei ka'naaiq se penj yia Bua Eei yaag penj yia Bua Eei fu'Jweiq Eei. ib zang Tinb huvb Navq haiq nx Buaj meib, kunq Navq uaq nx zruj.”
31.40: luvb Nxi zang yia tiaq Eutg Pwi, tiaq yua'q. luvb mwrnd zang yaag tiaq Jwavq, kwavg mFxmb Jaaj.
31.37: meib sru Revg yia Eei ka'naaiq meib pwatg haiq Euvg zeid meib Eei ka'naaiq? zx'q Zwrtq taaib an Jyenq naaiq maa'b! pun meib Eei myenb Zauj yia Eei myenb lomb Rxib mavg. ninb Bua zyrug hiuq tu'q yia Zauj meib, haiq taub zruj hxpg.
31.4: yaa-Kopq zyrug pun waag mivb Buaj laa-sen Zauj le-aa taaib ninb Eei pa'ki yuvb yem Eei Zyavq.
31.51: laa-Baan cvj kxvq Buaj yaa-Kopq, “mavg kaaj, naaiq se yia Dwi Eei la'pyeiq Zauj ton Jyenq Eei la'pyeib tovg yem meib Zauj yia Bu'Dovj.
31.12: ninb kxvq, ‘mavg kaaj maa'b! Tiuj yuvb Eeid Eei yetg zuvq yuvb kruq maaib teij pen Eei, maaib teij tyemq mwrng Eei, maaib teij tyemq Zru Eei, weig zu'g laa-Baan zruj pun meib Eei yetg zuvq yia pwatg Revg.
31.46: cvj Buaj ninb Eei myenb, “Raud la'pyeiq taaib maa'b!” ninb Bua zyrug Raud la'pyeiq taaib Dwi Jyenq a'q. Dwi liud, ninb Bua zyrug lomb Rxib yem uaq la'pyeib Dwi Eei ka'Len Eang Naavj.
31.13: yia se Tinb huvb, tovb yem Betg-en hing Zwrtq pun meib pwatg uaq taub. yem Betg-en meib lyepg nxm la'pyeiq ton Jyenq toj yrub fuvj pun yia, yaag yem uaq lcvd Jiad vcvg waag. mivb a'q. ib zang Zwrtq naaiq nxm teib puv Rwrnj meib Zwrtq seij Eei teib puv.’+”
31.26: laa-Baan kxvq Buaj yaa-Kopq, “meib fuvg Navq naaiq zruj? meib Duaq yia cvj kwaaiq Jyenq yia Eei sia'q pyauj Navq Bx'q Jaaj Zaavq tu'q taaib Eei msia'q txn nx.
31.28: meib lyemb maiq pun yia tu'q zom yia Eei fun Zauj yia Eei sia'q. naaiq meib zruj Eei Jauq za'kevb Vovj haig.
31.54: ninb yaag yem uaq nxm Bovb aiq lovg scvb Kuq ziag pun Tinb huvb yaag heug ninb Eei kxb yrud taaib lomb Rxib Eang Naavj. Eang liud, ninb Bua zyavb mwrnd yem uaq nxm Bov.
31.8: sij kxvq ninb kxvq, ‘yuvb maaib tyemq Eei xij zu'g funj meib Eei kovb zinb,’ yetg zuvq yuvb Fiag txn maaib tyemq Eei Navq. sij kxvq ninb kxvq, ‘yuvb pen xij zu'g funj meib Eei kovb zinb,’ zyavb kwanb yuvb zyrug Kuvj Fiag txn pen Eei Navq.
31.9: Navq naaig, Tinb huvb zx'q meib Eei tia Eei pwrng scvb Kuq pun yia Revg mig a'q.
31.32: mq paag meib Eei miub favj c'q, sij kxvq lxd pwatg yem haiq taub, maiq tuvq lyrub ninb Eei mcvg a'q. txv Jyenq yia Bua Eei zwavj kxb yrud sru Zwrtq meib Eei haiq Euvg ka'naaiq, kunq zx'q Rwrnj a'q.” yaa-Kopq maiq hiuq tu'q laa-sen nimg ninb Eei tia Eei miub favj.
31.21: ninb txb Jyenq ninb maaib Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq pyauj Jiaj zi'g yu-fe-titg Daaib, huvj Jyenq ki-le-aatg Eei Bovb aiq txvj mivb.
31.23: ninb zyrug txb Jyenq ninb Eei kxb yrud mivb zung. zung siag Nxi zyrug zung zaaig yem ki-le-aatg Eei Bovb aiq txvj.
31.6: meib Bua yaag hiuq tu'q yia lovg Revg Qa'q Tevj meib Bua Eei tia zruj kov.
31.55: ta'Eeig Dxm Ryruq Eei, laa-Baan zom ninb Eei sia'q Zauj ninb Eei fun yaag pwav waag ninb Bua, zyrug Zwrtq Jauq Rwrnj pyauq a'q.
31.44: taaib maa'b! meib Zauj yia xij zu'g lyepg Jiad vcvg waag weig Tevj Bua i taub zruj zxvb zevj.”
31.20: yaa-Kopq yaag Duaq ninb Eei ovb taa, aa-lam myenb, laa-Baan, weig zu'g ninb pivj Jyenq pyauj, maiq Buaj.
31.5: yaa-Kopq kxvq Buaj ninb Eei auq Bua, “yia pwatg meib Eei tia Eei eij leid Zauj yia maiq Navq zinb Daavg. mq paag yia Eei tia Eei Tinb huvb Zauj yia yem.
31.53: Toq apg-laa-ham Eei Tinb huvb Zauj naa-ho Eei Tinb huvb, tovb ninb Bua Eei tia Eei Tinb huvb, Tevj Bua tunj sig.” yaa-Kopq zyrug zyavq Jyenq tovb ninb Eei tia, i-sakg, zavg Eei Tinb huvb Eei Buaj lcvd Jiad vcvg waag.
31.19: uaq zang laa-Baan Zwrtq mivb Japq ninb Eei pa'ki yuvb pyei. laa-sen pavg uaq nxm zyavb hog nimg ninb Eei tia yem pyauq zavg Eei miub favj.
31.38: “yia Zauj meib yem tu'q Eig zyepg Havj a'q. meib Eei pa'ki yuvb Zauj yuvb maiq Baav Jiaj txn. yetg taub meib Eei pa'ki yuvb kruq fai yuvb kruq yia maiq Eang Jiaj.
31.31: yaa-Kopq tau laa-Baan, “yia kamb Riaj meib xij zx'q meib Eei sia'q Rwrnj.
31.52: naaiq Dwi la'pyeiq Zauj naaiq nxm la'pyeib tovg zruj zxvb zevj Tevj Bua Javj zu'g, yia maiq Jiaj meib uaq puv zruj haiq Euvg hxig meib. meib yaag maiq Jiaj naaiq puv zruj haiq Euvg hxig yia.
31.27: meib fuvg Navq naaiq nx Duaq yia, pivj Jyenq pyauj yaag maiq Buaj yetg Jruj yia? sij kxvq yia hiuq nx, yia zruj naug Eitg pun myenb paauj Ruv, Bx'q lxb Bx'q Rod, Patq taanb paab, fuvj meib Bua Fyenb yrub Eei Zwrtq Jauq.
31.41: yia Navq naaiq nx Zauj meib yem pwavq Eig zyepg Havj. yia zruj kov zyepg feij Havj pyetq meib Eei i taub sia'q lovg. cvj zruj Ju'q Havj pyetq meib Eei scvb Kuq. meib Zxg Tiuq yia Eei kovb zinb tu'q zyepg Rung mig a'q.
31.1: yaa-Kopq haid kxvq laa-Baan Eei txn vopq. ninb Bua kxvq, “yaa-Kopq Rcv Revg aa tia Eei Jaab tivb ka'naaiq. ninb putq zxib taaib maaib Eei Euvb Euvg se yem Bua Eei tia taaib.”
31.39: sij kxvq Yiab ka'naaiq vaatg, yia maiq txb mivb pun meib mavg. yia kanb lcvd Dxtq Navq. Janb za'g nimg haiq Euvg, maiq kunq luvb Nxi zang fai luvb mwrnd zang, meib zuvq heug yia kanb Tipq.
31.47: laa-Baan Zwrtq uaq nxm txvj Eei Buaj heug ye-kaa-saaj-haaj-Du-Taa, mq paag yaa-Kopq Zwrtq Buaj heug kaa-le-etg.
31.10: “yuvb scv Eei zyavb hog, yia Beij pwatg Tiuj yuvb Eeid Eei yuvb kruq, maaib teij pen Eei, maaib teij maaib tyemq Zru Eei, maaib teij maaib tyemq mwrng Eei.
31.25: laa-Baan zung zaaig yaa-Kopq uaq zang, yaa-Kopq Zxv Jyenq Dopg liub yem ki-le-aatg Eei Bovb aiq txvj. laa-Baan Zauj kan ninb mivb Eei kxb yrud yaag Zxv Jyenq ninb Bua Eei Dopg liub uaq.
31.22: yaa-Kopq pyauj mivb tu'q pua Nxi, laa-Baan Zivj hiuq tu'q.
31.42: sij kxvq maiq zeid yia Eei tia Eei Tinb huvb, apg-laa-ham Eei Tinb huvb, tovb i-sakg zavg Eei Tinb huvb, Zauj yia yem nx, meib zuvq pun yia Kuvb puad pc'g zauj Eei Zwrtq Navq. mq paag Tinb huvb pwatg yia Eei Krub zivb Zauj yia Eei puad zruj Eei kov. a'Mwavj ninb zyrug paaq Jyenq meib.”
31.15: ninb zruj pun yia Bua Navq penj kanb fivj myenb nx. ninb yaag maaig yia Bua Eei mGxvq taaib yaag na'q Revg mig a'q.
31.29: ib zang meib yem yia Eei puab Diaq. yia xij zruj haiq Euvg hxig meib se zruj tu'q Eei. mq paag a'Mwavj meib Eei tia Eei Tinb huvb poj Beij Buaj yia, ‘maiq kunq lovj fai Zyruq, maiq tuvq kxvq haiq Euvg pun yaa-Kopq.’
31.30: yia hiuq tu'q meib Eei Hruq xij Rwrnj meib Eei tia Eei pyauq Zivj taaib pyauj. mq paag meib weig haiq tiug nimg yia yem pyauq zavg Eei miub favj?”

27.18: yaa-Kopq mivb Tauj ninb Eei tia uaq kxvq, “aa tia aag.” ninb Eei tia tau, “txn aag, meib tovb haiq taub txn?”
27.45: la'Ku'q meib zruj pun ninb Eei sig, yia mtaaib pun myenb mivb txb meib Rwrnj. maa fuvg haib pun tu'q yetg Nxi taig i taub txn?”
27.3: txn aag, zx'q meib Eei Jwavb zinj Zauj fxv mivb kemb pwrnq taub xq taaib pun yia Eang.
27.43: txn aa'b! mwavj maa Eei waag og. meib xij zu'g pyauj mivb haa-laan zivb, maa Eei kxj, laa-Baan uaq.
27.14: yaa-Kopq zyrug mivb zx'q taaib pun ninb Eei maa. ninb Eei maa ei Jyenq yaa-Kopq Eei tia yetg kau xij Eang Eei Beng zyavj.
27.34: e-saau haid ninb Eei tia Eei waag ninb Hruq mun haig, puvb siv puvb Qiaj Eei Eyemq Jyenq kxvq, “aa tia aa'b! Toq pwav waag yia. Toq tia yaag pwav waag pun yia maa'b!”
27.2: i-sakg kxvq, “tia koj haig a'q. maiq hiuq tu'q haiq Nxi taig.
27.36: e-saau kxvq, “ninb Eei Buaj heug yaa-Kopq kevb! Pwij haig a'q, weig zu'g ninb Duaq yia i Rung mig a'q. yia zruj txnb Lo tu'q suvb kruq Eei leid ninb Duaq tu'q mig a'q. ib zang tovb tia xij pwav pun yia Eei waag ninb yaag Duaq tia pwav pun ninb Revg mig a'q. aa tia aa'b! meib maiq lyrub yetg teij pwav pun yia a'q?”
27.35: i-sakg tau, “tovb yia xij pwav meib Eei waag meib Eei yrud taaib Duaq yia pwav pun ninb Revg mig a'q.”
27.24: mq paag ninb cvj naaig Rung, “meib za'kevb yia Eei txn, e-saau, fai?” yaa-Kopq tau, “zeid Eei.”
27.7: ‘pwrnq taub xq Beng taaib Kuq Eei pun yia Eang weig yem yia maiq kcvb taig tu'q yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen pwav waag pun meib.’
27.17: le-Be-Kaa zx'q ninb liug leid zyavj Eei xq Zauj Fuaq pun yaa-Kopq prub mivb.
27.11: yaa-Kopq kxvq Buaj ninb Eei maa, “maa kanb hiuq tu'q Eei, e-saau Zwrtq pyei su'g su'q uaq. yia maiq maaib pyei, Lyruq Fav Eei.
27.33: i-sakg lyemb zeib sin zinj Fwrnb Fwrnq Eei. ninb kxvq, “uaq Euvg, haiq taub pwrnq xq txb taaib pun yia? yia Ko'q ho'g Eang liud, meib zyrug Tauj. tia zuvq pwav waag pun ninb mig a'q. ziuj tia pwav Eei waag ninb yaag za'kevb tu'q.”
27.16: ninb cvj zx'q yuvb txn Eei Dopq nctq Jyenq yaa-Kopq Eei puad Zauj Jaav, tovb maiq maaib pyei Eei txvj. zxv zyavj,
27.40: meib xij zu'g Kauj Ru'g Daauq yuvd mcvg, yaag xij zu'g fub suj meib Eei yrud. mq paag meib haiq zang haib simq tu'q Dutq ninb, meib zyrug maiq zu'g ninb kunq.”
27.37: i-sakg tau, “tia pun ninb zruj meib Eei zyruq yaag pun yetg zuvq muab txig Zyenb Ze'q zruj ninb Eei pru. lyemb Byaub Meiq Zauj syavb a'vung tiuq yia pun weig yuvd ninb Eei mcvg. txn aa'b! yia maaib haiq Euvg haib Tevj meib?”
27.4: zruj Kuq Eei Navq yetg kau yia xij Eang uaq nx, Beng taaib pun yia, weig yem yia maiq kcvb taig yia tu'q pwav Ga'haaq laai uaq Rung waag pun meib.”
27.12: pwavb zu'g tia Lua yia, ninb zyrug hiuq tu'q yia Duaq ninb. ninb maiq zeid pwav waag pun yia, zuvq zyruj yia mq pei!”
27.46: le-Be-Kaa kxvq Buaj i-sakg, “laaij e-saau Eei i taub hitq-Tai myenb auq, yia maiq nxig faanb zyavb a'q. sij kxvq yaa-Kopq cvj lovg taub naaiq nxm teib puv Eei hitq-Tai myenb Eei sia'q zruj auq nx, yia taig kaub lovj.”
27.13: ninb Eei maa kxvq, “yia Eei txn aag, sij kxvq zu'g hruq nx, se Dxtq zu'g maa kanb. Kuvj xij zu'g mwavj maa Eei waag Navq. mivb zx'q yuvb taaib pun maa og.”
27.26: Eang liud, hopq liud i-sakg kxvq, “txn aag, taaib fatq teij zom tavb tia Eei Myen.”
27.28: Toq Tinb huvb pun Byuvb swiq yem uaq luvb Fiag, yaag pun meib Eei Dau lovj. Toq ninb yaag pun meib tu'q Byaub Meiq Zauj syavb a'vung tiuq Zamq.
27.8: txn aag, Navq naaig, meib mwavj yia, ei Jyenq yia Eei waag zruj.
27.9: meib mivb yuvb kwanb uaq kinq i taub yuvb txn Rweig Eei Jung Eei txb taaib pun maa. maa zyrug ei Jyenq yetg kau meib Eei tia xij Eang Kuq Eei Beng taaib pun ninb Eang.
27.32: ninb Eei tia, i-sakg, naaig kaaj, “meib haiq taub?” e-saau tau, “yia meib Eei txnb Lo, e-saau.”
27.21: i-sakg cvj kxvq Buaj yaa-Kopq, “txn aag, taaib fatq teij pun yia Lua kaaj, meib za'kevb yia Eei txn, e-saau, zeid fai maiq zeid.”
27.23: ninb zia'q maiq tu'q naaiq se yaa-Kopq weig zu'g puad maaib pyei su'g su'q Navq ninb Eei kxj, e-saau, Eei puad nx. i-sakg zyrug pwav waag pun ninb.
27.6: le-Be-Kaa Buaj ninb Eei txn, yaa-Kopq, “a'Jav yia haid meib Eei tia kxvq Buaj e-saau,
27.44: xij zu'g Zauj ninb Bua yem trug zuaq meib Eei kxj Eei ka'Qiaj fiu mivb,
27.20: i-sakg naaig ninb Eei txn, “txn aa'b! meib fuvg pwrnq tu'q xq Dovg naaig syepq?” yaa-Kopq tau, “zyruq, meib Eei Tinb huvb, pun yia haib pwavb xq syepq Eei.”
27.5: i-sakg Zauj ninb Eei txn, e-saau, i txnb tiaj kxvq waag uaq zang, le-Be-Kaa mwavj Jyenq Eei. e-saau mivb kemb pwrnq xq uaq zang,
27.19: yaa-Kopq tau, “yia meib Eei txnb Lo, e-saau. yia ei tia Eei waag Beng zyavj. tia Jiad sin zweid Jyenq Eang yia pwrnq taaib Eei xq a'q. Eang liud, tia tu'q pwav waag pun yia.”
27.38: e-saau Qa'q Toq ninb Eei tia, “aa tia aa'b! meib Kuvj maaib Du'g Euvg pwav Eei waag Navq? Toq meib yaag pwav teij pun yia maa'b!” ninb cvj Eyemq Rung a'q.
27.31: e-saau zyrug zruj teij xq Kuq Eei txb mivb pun ninb Eei tia Eang. ninb kxvq, “aa tia aa'b! Jiad sin zweid Jyenq Eang yia pwrnq taaib Eei xq a'q. Eang liud, aa tia tu'q pwav waag pun yia.”
27.27: yaa-Kopq mivb zom ninb Eei tia uaq zang, ninb Eei tia Nomq zu'g yaa-Kopq Eei lwi Eei Ryaau zyrug pwav waag ninb Eei txn a'q. ninb kxvq, “yia Eei txn Daav Eei, Navq zyruq Zeij fu'q Eei lyavb Deig Daav nx.
27.41: e-saau Rxv haig yaa-Kopq laaij ninb Eei tia pwav waag pun yaa-Kopq. ninb yem Hruq Namq, “Namq taaib maiq laub yia Eei tia kwei seij. zuaq yia Bua Raub Eyemq Eei zyavb hog Jiaj liud, yia xij taij yaa-Kopq kwavg a'q.”
27.1: i-sakg koj haig a'q. mziv yaag Buaq, mavg maiq pwatg. ninb heug ninb Eei txnb Lo, e-saau, taaib kxvq Buaj ninb, “txn aag.” e-saau tau, “aa tia aag, yia yem naaiq og.”
27.39: i-sakg zyrug kxvq Buaj ninb, “meib zu'g yem leib Daub Truq lovj Eei txvj ko. luvb Eei Byuvb swiq meib yaag maiq tu'q.
27.10: Beng zyavj meib txb mivb pun meib Eei tia Eang weig yem ninb maiq kcvb taig haib pwav Ga'haaq laai uaq Rung waag pun meib.”
27.25: i-sakg kxvq, “txn aag, txb meib pwrnq taaib Eei xq pun tia Eang. Eang liud zyrug pwav waag pun meib.” yaa-Kopq zyrug txb xq taaib pun ninb Eang, cvj txb a'vung tiuq taaib pun ninb hopq.
27.22: yaa-Kopq mivb fatq Eei. ninb Eei tia, i-sakg, zyrug Lua ninb. i-sakg kxvq, “meib Eei Qiaj se Navq yaa-Kopq Eei Qiaj, mq paag meib Eei puad haid Navq e-saau Eei puad nx.”
27.42: le-Be-Kaa haid kxvq ninb Eei txnb Lo, e-saau, taaq za'eij taij txnb faij, yaa-Kopq, ninb zyrug heug yaa-Kopq taaib kxvq Buaj ninb, “mwavj kaaj, meib Eei kxj, e-saau, taaq za'eij xij Jaauq win taij meib.
27.15: le-Be-Kaa cvj mivb zx'q ninb Eei txnb Lo, e-saau, Eei lwib hruj, tovb syru Jyenq uaq pyauq kaub lovj Jiaj uaq yemg, pun ninb Eei txnb faij, yaa-Kopq, zu'q Jyenq.
27.29: Toq pun Zamb fivj myenb fub suj meib, yaag pun Zamb nxm kua'q Eei myenb kweig Fiag paaij meib. Toq pun meib haib zruj meib Eei muab txig Eei zyruq, yaag pun meib Eei maa Eei zeib fun kweig Fiag paaij meib. haiq taub zyruj meib, Toq pun uaq taub zu'g zyruj. haiq taub pwav waag meib, Toq pun uaq taub tu'q zyruq Zeij fu'q.”
27.30: i-sakg pwav liud waag, yaa-Kopq Javb Jav Zwrtq mivb Navq, ninb Eei kxj, e-saau, pwrnq tu'q xq Rwrnj taaib.

41.18: maaib siag taub yavb vovb Eeid Rweig Eei, Jung Eei, yem uaq Daaib Zwrtq taaib yem uaq Eang lua'g ti'g nxmb.
41.45: huvb tiaj Tevj yo-sepq Zwrtq nxm i-yipq teib puv Eei Buaj heug saaj-fe-naatq-paa-ne-aa yaag zx'q on zivb Eei sai myenb, po-Ti-fe-laa, Eei sia'q, aa-sej-natq, pun yo-sepq lovg zruj auq. yo-sepq zyrug Zwrtq mivb zaab kxmj i-yipq teib puv.
41.3: cvj maaib siag taub yavb vovb Eeid Kxv Jaig Eei, a'mavg Eei, yem nai-aa Daaib Zwrtq taaib sruq Jyenq Jung uaq teij vovb Eeid Eei ka'Len.
41.43: faa-lo yaag pun yo-sepq zweid ninb Eei ta'Eeig nxm maab Zia. cvj maaib myenb mivb Daavg heug Jyenq kxvq, “kweig Fiag oq!” faa-lo huvb Navq naaiq xn ninb kunq i-yipq teib puv.
41.50: tomb vxg Eei Havb zivb maiq kcvb Tauj, on zivb Eei sai myenb, po-Ti-fe-laa, Eei sia'q, aa-sej-natq, yuvd tu'q i taub txn pun yo-sepq.
41.14: faa-lo huvb zyrug Paaiq myenb mivb heug yo-sepq taaib. ninb Bua zyrug syepg syepq Eei mivb txb ninb Zwrtq. yo-sepq Teij syaam, Japq Ba'pyei, yeng Gxi lwib hruj, mivb Tauj faa-lo huvb Eei Ra'Myen.
41.48: yo-sepq zyrug syru naaiq teij siag Havj ka'Euad Eei laavb zi'g kapq zunq yem nxmb nxm zivb. yem haiq nxm zivb Eei hxvg zavg zwavj Eei laavb zi'g yaag syru taaib kapq zunq an Jyenq uaq nxm zivb.
41.34: cvj xn teij Jyen kunq kxmj teib puv. naaiq teij puvb zua'g lovj Eei siag Havj ka'Euad xij zu'g syru yetg zuvq kcvb zwavj pyaa kruq Eei yetg kruq.
41.2: maaib siag taub yavb vovb Eeid Rweig Eei, Jung Eei, yem Daaib Zwrtq taaib yem uaq Eang lua'g ti'g nxmb.
41.36: naaiq teij laavb zi'g lyrub Jyenq Buvb i-yipq teib puv vxg siag Havj Eei zyavb hog zyrug maaib Eang maaib hopq weig maiq pun teib puv laaij vxg Naavj zu'g myetg Revg.”
41.35: naaiq teij Havb zivb lovj Eei zyavb hog, naaiq teij Jyen xij zu'g zx'q laavb zi'g kapq Rxib kwei faa-lo huvb Eei puab Diaq syru Jyenq yem nxmb nxm zivb zruj Eang hopq.
41.24: uaq teij Byaub mauj na'q Revg uaq teij siag txq Byaub Jaub mig a'q. yia kxvq yia Eei Beij pun mavg sru Pxq Beij Eei finb scv mwavj yaag maiq maaib yetg taub haib Pxq tu'q Zwrtq.”
41.7: Byaub mauj na'q Revg uaq teij siag txq Jaub Eei, yavb Eei Byaub mig a'q. faa-lo huvb zyrug Eia taaib, hiuq tu'q ninb Beij pwatg.
41.17: faa-lo huvb zyrug kxvq Buaj yo-sepq, “yia Beij pwatg yia kanb sruq Jyenq nai-aa Daaib Len.
41.49: yo-sepq syru tu'q laavb zi'g Dovg Kxib Len Eei saab zyru Zamq. Zamq kau, Laau maiq hivb, saauq maiq hivb, zyav naaig maiq saauq a'q.
41.11: maaib mwrnd nx, yia Bua i taub zuvq Beij Beij. yetg taub Eei Beij maaib yetg Euvg eij leid.
41.33: “Navq naaiq, Toq huvb tiaj kinq taub kwai Eei, maaib Zovb mevb Eei myenb, xn ninb kunq i-yipq teib puv.
41.16: yo-sepq tau faa-lo huvb, “se maiq zeid yia haib Pxq Beij. Tinb huvb kanb xij Pxq tu'q hxpg Buaj faa-lo.”
41.40: yia xij pun meib kruj yia Eei ting. yia Eei zwavj pc'g fivj yaag xij zu'g Bua'g meib, mwavj meib Eei waag. Kuvj yia kanb maaib livg kaub Lo Jiaj meib Eei Navq.”
41.37: faa-lo huvb Zauj ninb Eei yetg zuvq Jyen haid yo-sepq Eei za'eij lovj Eei.
41.4: vovb Jaig zyrug Eang Revg uaq teij siag taub vovb Jung. Beij liud, huvb tiaj zyrug Eia taaib a'q.
41.51: yo-sepq zyrug Tevj ninb Eei txnb Lo Zwrtq Buaj heug maa-natq-sej. ninb kxvq, “Tinb huvb Tevj yia la'Ku'q yia Eei yetg zuvq Kruq naang Zauj yia Eei tia Eei pyauq zov Mwavq txig.”
41.12: maaib taub hipq-lu myenb lunj myenb yaag Zauj yia Bua zu'g wrnj Jyenq lob. ninb zruj kruj huvb ting Eei tomb pcvb pyeiq Eei nrub. yia Bua kxvq yia Bua Eei Beij pun ninb mwavj, ninb zyrug ziuj kx'g myenb Eei Beij Pxq Beij Eei eij leid.
41.46: yo-sepq Jiad kxn weig i-yipq teib puv Eei faa-lo huvb zruj kov uaq zang, ninb Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q faab zyepg Havj. ninb yem huvb ting Zwrtq mivb yrub kxmj i-yipq teib puv.
41.13: Ga'haaq za'kevb txib tiug Revg ninb Pxq Eei eij leid. yia tu'q zruj kov Navq zinb Daavg nx, mq paag zruj Fuaq uaq taub zu'g txb mivb Diuj Jyenq Dyavj taij kwavg.”
41.26: uaq teij siag taub yavb vovb Jung peiq siag Havj. uaq teij siag txq Byaub Jaub yaag peiq siag Havj. i nxm Beij Eei eij leid se fib Navq Eei.
41.28: “naaiq za'kevb Navq yia Buaj liud huvb tiaj uaq nx. Tinb huvb xij pun meib hiuq tu'q ninb xij Navq haiq nx zruj.
41.54: cvj pia'g siag Havj Eei tomb vxg txij Revg yo-sepq kxvq Eei waag. nxmb nxm kua'q vxg Revg a'q. mq paag i-yipq teib puv nxmb nxm txvj maaib Eang Eei.
41.8: ta'Eeig Dxm ninb haid Hruq maiq henb zyrug heug i-yipq teib puv Eei mavg sru Pxq Beij Eei finb scv Zauj kwaib kx'q finb scv yetg zuvq taaib. faa-lo zyrug kxvq ninb Eei Beij pun ninb Bua mwavj. mq paag maiq maaib haiq taub haib Pxq tu'q Beij Zwrtq.
41.9: uaq zang Tevj faa-lo huvb prub tiuq uaq taub tomb Jyen kxvq Buaj huvb tiaj, “ib Nxi yia Javj zu'g yia zruj txvg Eei sig a'q.
41.32: huvb tiaj Beij naaiq teij i nxm Beij piuj mevb Tinb huvb tivg zyavj Navq naaiq nx zruj yaag xij syepg syepq Eei zruj.
41.21: Eang liud mq paag maiq maaib haiq taub zia'q tu'q ninb Bua Eang uaq teij vovb Jung. ninb Bua Zxg Navq zinb Daavg nx, a'mavg. yia zyrug Eia taaib a'q.
41.57: cvj maaib luvb Diaq myenb yetg zuvq mivb i-yipq teib puv Tevj yo-sepq maaid Byaub, weig zu'g luvb Diaq zu'g tomb Waav tomb vxg Kruq haig.
41.23: Ga'haaq cvj Zwrtq siag txq Byaub mauj, Eauj Revg, Jia'q Revg, laaij zu'g tov puv Eei Ryaauj pwrng.
41.6: Ga'haaq cvj Zwrtq siag txq Byaub mauj, Jia'q Eei, laaij zu'g tov puv mcvj Eei Ryaauj pwrng.
41.55: Tauj i-yipq myenb vxg taaib, zwavj pc'g fivj mivb Tevj faa-lo huvb Toq Eang. huvb tiaj kxvq Buaj ninb Bua, “meib Bua xij zu'g mivb lxd yo-sepq Navq. ninb Navq haiq nx kxvq, meib Bua xij zu'g ei Jyenq ninb Eei waag zruj.”
41.44: faa-lo cvj kxvq Buaj yo-sepq, “yia zruj faa-lo huvb tiaj. Zwrtq liud meib kanb Gxi Rwib, yem naaiq i-yipq teib puv maiq maaib haiq taub haib zruj haiq Euvg.”
41.20: uaq teij vovb Jaig Eang Revg Zwrtq Daavg uaq teij siag taub vovb Jung.
41.5: huvb tiaj cvj mFxmb mivb, Beij ta'Eeig nxm Beij. Beij pwatg maaib zuvb Byaub Zwrtq siag txq, yetg zuvq Jaub Eei, yavb Eei.
41.56: tomb vxg kunq zruj kunq Kruq pwavq Revg i-yipq teib puv mig a'q. yo-sepq zyrug Kxi Gxi ninb Eei nxmb nxm txvj Eei tomb lamd maaig Byaub Zwrtq pun i-yipq myenb.
41.53: i-yipq teib puv puvb zua'g lovj Eei siag Havj Jiaj liud,
41.19: Ga'haaq cvj maaib siag taub yavb vovb Eeid Kxv Jaig Eei, a'mavg Eei, Zwrtq taaib. yem i-yipq teib puv yia maiq kcvb pwatg Jiaj yavb vovb Dovg naaig a'mavg.
41.38: huvb tiaj kxvq Buaj ninb Eei zwavj Jyen, “Bua haib lxd tu'q kanb taub Navq naaiq taub maaib Tinb huvb Eei sivj livb fai?”
41.31: Tauj vxg Eei zyavb hog pa'la'g vxg tu'q Kruq haig, myenb zyrug la'Ku'q Revg puvb zua'g lovj Eei zyavb hog.
41.52: ta'Eeig taub txn ninb Zwrtq Buaj heug e-faa-im yaag kxvq, “weig zu'g yem naaiq teib puv yia syrug Kruq naang mq paag Tinb huvb pun yia tu'q fu'Jweiq.”
41.27: Ga'haaq Zwrtq uaq teij siag taub yavb vovb Jaig Eei, a'mavg Eei, Zauj uaq teij siag txq Byaub mauj zu'g tov puv mcvj Eei Ryaauj pwrng Jia'q mivb, se peiq siag Havj tomb Waav tomb vxg.
41.41: faa-lo huvb cvj kxvq Buaj yo-sepq, “yia ib zang xn meib kunq Revg i-yipq teib puv.”
41.1: Jiaj taaib pwavq i Havj, faa-lo huvb Beij nxm Beij, Beij pwatg ninb kanb sruq Jyenq nai-aa Daaib Len.
41.39: ninb kxvq Buaj yo-sepq, “weig zu'g Tinb huvb pun meib hiuq tu'q naaiq teij yetg zuvq sig, maiq maaib haiq taub Dovg meib kwai yaag maaib Zovb mevb.
41.47: yem uaq teij puvb zua'g lovj Eei siag Havj ka'Euad, teib puv Zwrtq kcvb zwavj ka'naaiq lovj haig.
41.10: maaib Rung huvb tiaj Qiaj Jiad ninb Eei pru, zyrug zx'q yia Zauj zruj Fuaq Eei tomb Jyen mivb wrnj Jyenq yem kruj huvb ting Eei tomb pcvb pyeiq Eei pyauq uaq nxm lob.
41.25: yo-sepq zyrug kxvq Buaj faa-lo huvb, “i nxm Beij Eei eij leid zuvq fib Navq Eei. Tinb huvb Jaab Daavg pun meib hiuq tu'q ninb xij Navq haiq nx zruj.
41.22: “yia cvj Beij pwatg maaib zuvb Byaub Zwrtq siag txq Jaub Eei, yavb Eei.
41.42: faa-lo huvb zyrug Lutq maaib yenj Eei puab Do'g Rcv Tevj yo-sepq tavb Jyenq. pun ninb zu'q Jyenq la'maab Diab mwrng Eei lwib Daauq, cvj zx'q tiub Jyemb limg Kwavj Jyenq ninb Eei Jaav.
41.15: huvb tiaj kxvq Buaj ninb, “yia Beij nxm Beij yaag maiq maaib haiq taub haib Pxq tu'q Zwrtq. yia haid myenb kxvq meib haid liud Beij zyrug haib Pxq Beij Eei.”
41.29: yem naaiq mivb siag Havj ka'Euad, kxmj i-yipq teib puv puvb zua'g lovj.
41.30: Ga'haaq cvj maaib siag Havj tomb Waav tomb vxg. laaij vxg Naavj, myenb zuvq xij la'Ku'q puvb zua'g lovj Eei Havj. teib puv yaag xij waaig Revg.

39.18: yia Qa'q heug, ninb zyrug kwavg ninb Eei lwi yem yia naaiq pyauj Zwrtq kcvb Ka'Dau mig a'q.”
39.8: mq paag yo-sepq maiq mwavj. ninb kxvq Buaj ninb Eei zyruq Eei auq, “yia Eei zyruq maiq zu'g Raub yem pyauq ka'Euad Eei haiq Euvg. yetg zuvq Jaab tivb ninb Jiu pun yia kruj.
39.3: uaq taub pyaub zyruq pwatg zyruq Zauj yo-sepq yem. zyruq yaag pun yo-sepq yem ninb zruj Eei Euvb Euvg tu'q lovj.
39.21: mq paag Tinb huvb Zauj ninb yem, yaag zruj lovj pun ninb, pun ninb zruj tu'q hxpg kruj lob uaq taub Jyen Eei Hruq.
39.14: ninb zyrug naub naug Eei heug yem ninb Eei pyauq uaq teij mJavg pru taaib. ninb kxvq, “mavg kaaj naaig! yia Eei Goj txb naaiq taub hipq-lu myenb taaib. ib zang ninb mavg Piaj yia Bua. ninb pia'g taaib xij yia Zauj ninb pweij, mq paag yia Qa'q naug.
39.23: yo-sepq kruj Jyenq Eei yetg zuvq sig, kruj lob Jyen maiq zu'g Raub weig zu'g zyruq Zauj yo-sepq yem. ninb zruj Eei Euvb Euvg zyruq Tevj ninb zruj tu'q lovj.
39.6: po-Ti-faa Eei yetg nxm Jaab tivb Euvb Euvg ka'naaiq ninb Jiu pun yo-sepq kruj Revg. Zwrtq liud ninb kanb Eei Eang hopq, ninb maiq zu'g Raub haiq Euvg. yo-sepq Eei sinb Pei zyavb tu'q lovj, Myenb mweig yaag Rweig.
39.2: ninb yem ninb Eei i-yipq myenb pyaub zyruq Eei pyauq. zyruq Zauj yo-sepq yem, pun ninb tu'q lovj.
39.20: zx'q yo-sepq wrnj Jyenq lob, tovb wrnj huvb tiaj Eei zwib myenb uaq nxm lob. yo-sepq zu'g wrnj Jyenq uaq
39.7: yem kau, ninb Eei zyruq Eei auq mavg yo-sepq haid hang haig, zyrug yua'g ninb kxvq, “meib taaib Zauj yia pweij og.”
39.19: yo-sepq Eei zyruq haid ninb Eei auq kxvq, “meib Eei nrub Navq naaiq nx zruj pun yia,” ninb zyrug Qiaj Jiad! haig,
39.17: ninb zyrug Navq naaiq nx kxvq, “tovb meib txb taaib Bua naaiq uaq taub hipq-lu nrub kauq pia'g taaib mavg yia maiq Jiad, xij Zauj yia.
