39.11: maaib Nxi nx, yo-sepq pia'g pyauq zruj ninb hxpg zu'g zruj Eei kov, yaag maiq maaib yetg taub pyauq Eei pru yem uaq.
39.5: yem po-Ti-faa Paaiq yo-sepq kruj Jyenq ninb Eei pyauq zov yetg zuvq Jaab tivb, zyruq weig yo-sepq Zeij fu'q pun uaq taub i-yipq myenb Eei Jaab tivb. ta'faanb yem pyauq yem Deig Eei yetg zuvq zyrug Zamq Jyenq faauj.
39.9: yem naaiq pyauq yia maaib hatg maad Dovg ninb Lo. yia Eei zyruq maiq Rcv haiq Euvg Zwrtq liud meib weig zu'g meib zruj ninb Eei auq. yia fuvg haib zruj waaig sig Dovg naaig Lo, paamd zwid txvg Tinb huvb?”
39.16: uaq taub auq zx'q yo-sepq Eei lwi an Jyenq ninb Eei ka'Len zuaq yo-sepq Eei zyruq Rwrnj taaib.
39.4: yo-sepq zruj tu'q hxpg po-Ti-faa Eei Hruq yaag tu'q zruj ninb Eei levg Jeiq pru. po-Ti-faa zyrug pun ninb kruj pyauq zov Zauj Jaab tivb yetg zuvq ka'naaiq.
39.10: maiq kunq uaq taub auq Nxib Nxi yua'g yo-sepq, yo-sepq maiq Kavq Zauj ninb pweij, lyemb maiq Zauj ninb yem yetg nxm txvj.
39.22: kruj lob Jyen zyrug pun yo-sepq kruj yetg zuvq yem lob Eei zwib myenb. ta'faanb yem lob ka'Euad Eei sig, yo-sepq kanb kunq Revg.
39.12: po-Ti-faa Eei auq Eau Jyenq yo-sepq Eei lwi kxvq, “taaib Zauj yia pweij maa'b!” mq paag yo-sepq kwavg Jyenq ninb Eei lwi yem uaq taub auq Eei puad, pyauj Zwrtq ka'Eiag zi'g pyauq mivb.
39.15: ninb haid yia heug, ninb zyrug kwavg Jyenq ninb Eei lwi yem yia naaiq cvj pyauj Zwrtq pyauq mig a'q.”
39.13: uaq taub auq pwatg yo-sepq kwavg Jyenq ninb Eei lwi pyauj Zwrtq ka'Eiag,
39.1: i-saa-maa-en myenb txb yo-sepq mivb i-yipq teib puv maaig pun taub i-yipq myenb, se faa-lo huvb Eei tomb Jyen, tovb kruj huvb ting Eei tomb pcvb pyeiq, po-Ti-faa.

47.18: uaq Havj Jiaj liud, Ga'haaq Havj ninb Bua cvj taaib Buaj yo-sepq, “yia Bua maiq pivj, kxvq za'g Buaj zyruq, yia Bua Eei Eaanb Revg. yia Bua Eei scvb Kuq yaag penj meib Eei Revg mig a'q. Zwrtq liud yia Bua Eei sin Zauj yia Bua Eei Dau maiq maaib haiq Euvg pun meib a'q.
47.8: huvb tiaj naaig yaa-Kopq, “meib Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q Bu'ziaj Havj a'q?”
47.3: faa-lo huvb naaig yo-sepq Eei kxj Bua, “meib Bua zruj haiq Euvg kov Eang Eei myenb?”
47.21: yo-sepq yaag pun zwavj pc'g fivj yem naaiq puv i-yipq mivb Tauj uaq puv i-yipq penj Revg faa-lo huvb Eei nrub.
47.14: yo-sepq syru Revg i-yipq myenb Zauj Kaa-naa-an myenb maaid Byaub Eei yetg zuvq Eaanb cvj txb mivb faa-lo Eei huvb ting.
47.23: yo-sepq kxvq Buaj zwavj pc'g fivj, “ib Nxi yia maaid meib Bua Zauj meib Bua Eei Dau pun faa-lo huvb mig a'q. naaiq yia cvj pun Jyenq ka'naaib Eim pun meib Bua zwavj uaq Deig.
47.6: i-yipq teib puv se yem meib Eei Ra'Myen. pun ninb Bua yem teib puv kaub lovj Jiaj Eei txvj lyepg vwaab kxn, se pun ninb Bua yem ko-sen teig. sij kxvq ninb Bua haiq taub maaib panb zeig, xij zu'g xn zruj pyeiq zeiq kruj yia Eei scvb Kuq.”
47.2: yo-sepq kinq pyaa taub ninb Eei kxj Zauj ninb mivb wig pwavb faa-lo huvb.
47.20: Navq naaig yo-sepq maaid Revg i-yipq teib puv Eei Dau pun faa-lo huvb. i-yipq myenb taub taub maaig Revg ninb Bua Eei Dau, laaij ninb Bua vxg tu'q pa'la'g Kruq Zuv mivb. Dau yetg zuvq zyrug penj Revg faa-lo Eei.
47.24: Tauj syru Eei zyavb hog, pyaa kruq zx'q Zwrtq yetg kruq pun faa-lo huvb. zevg uaq teij pyei kruq pun meib Bua zruj Eim zwavj yaag pun meib Bua kanb Zauj meib Bua Eei Mwavq txig Eang.”
47.28: yaa-Kopq yem i-yipq teib puv tu'q zyepg Zyetq Havj, ninb Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q yetg pc'q feij zyepg Zyetq Havj.
47.7: yo-sepq cvj txb ninb Eei tia, yaa-Kopq, mivb wig pwavb faa-lo huvb. yaa-Kopq yaag pwav waag faa-lo.
47.29: Tauj aaq lamb teij kwei seij Eei zyavb hog, ninb heug ninb Eei txn, yo-sepq, taaib, Buaj yo-sepq, “sij kxvq ziuj txn pwatg, yia zruj hxpg meib Eei Hruq nx, Toq txb meib Eei puad an Jyenq yia Eei Zamb zwib ka'Diaq mcvj lcvd vcvg waag. xij zu'g lcvd meib xij zyepg zua'q Eei zruj lovj pun yia, maiq zavj yia Eei sei yem naaiq i-yipq teib puv.
47.19: yia Bua weig haiq tiug xij zu'g yem meib Eei Ra'Myen vxg taig? lyemb yia Bua Zauj yia Bua Eei Dau xij zu'g myetg Revg. Toq meib lovg laavb zi'g yeng yia Bua Zauj yia Bua Eei Dau. yia Bua zyrug penj faa-lo huvb Eei nrub. yia Bua Eei Dau yaag penj ninb Eei mig a'q. Toq pun Byaub Eim yia Bua weig pun yia Bua haib tu'q mcvg zyavb, maiq taig. Deig yaag maiq zu'g kwavg Jyenq Waavb Waav uaq.”
47.17: pc'g fivj zyrug txb ninb Bua Eei scvb Kuq mivb yo-sepq uaq. yo-sepq lovg Byaub yeng ninb Bua Eei yuvb, pa'ki yuvb, vovb, lxb, maad. uaq Havj yo-sepq heug ninb Bua txb scvb Kuq taaib yeng laavb zi'g.
47.31: yaa-Kopq kxvq, “yia xij meib lcvd vcvg waag meib za'kevb zruj.” yo-sepq zyrug lcvd Jiad vcvg waag. lcvd liud, yaa-Kopq yem uaq Zrub taaub Do'q Fiag paaij Tinb huvb.
47.30: yia kwei seij, txn xij zu'g txb yia Eei sei Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv Rwrnj mivb Jwavg yia Eei ovb Taaij Eei zruq zavj.” yo-sepq tau, “yia zuvq xij ei Jyenq tia Eei waag zruj.”
47.27: i-saa-laa-en myenb yem i-yipq teib puv, ko-sen teig, tu'q ninb Bua kanb Eei Dau yaag Yaavj taaib maaib fu'Jweiq Zamq.
47.11: yo-sepq txb ninb Eei tia Zauj ninb Eei muab txig mivb lyepg vwaab kxn yem i-yipq teib puv kaub lovj Jiaj Eei txvj, laa-maa-setg zivb ka'Len, ziuj faa-lo huvb Buaj Eei waag.
47.5: faa-lo kxvq Buaj yo-sepq, “ib zang meib Eei tia, meib Eei muab txig taaib Tauj meib naaiq a'q.
47.9: yaa-Kopq tau faa-lo, “yia Eei seij zeiq yrub Jiaj naaiq yrub Jiaj uaq yem tu'q yetg pc'q faab zyepg Havj a'q. naaiq teij Nxib Eia'g yrug navq yrug Kruq. maiq Dovg yia Eei ovb Taaij Bua yrub Jiaj naaiq yem yrub Jiaj uaq yem Eei Eutg zeiq Daauq.”
47.16: yo-sepq kxvq, “sij kxvq meib Bua Eei Eaanb Revg mig a'q nx, txb meib Bua Eei scvb Kuq taaib yeng Byaub.”
47.4: ninb Bua tau, “yia Bua, meib Eei pru, se yuvd yuvb, yuvd pa'ki yuvb Eei myenb Navq yia Bua Eei ovb Taaij nx. yia Bua taaib yem trug naaiq nxm teib puv weig zu'g Kaa-naa-an teib puv vxg tu'q Kruq haig. lyemb maiq maaib miaq pun yuvb kwanb pa'ki yuvb kwanb Eang. Toq pun yia Bua yem uaq ko-sen.”
47.10: yaa-Kopq cvj pwav Rung waag faa-lo liud, zyrug Zwrtq mig a'q.
47.22: Kuvj zevg sai myenb Eei Dau yo-sepq maiq maaid Navq, weig zu'g sai myenb zanb zang tu'q faa-lo huvb Jwav Eei pwrng. ninb Bua tu'q kauj faa-lo huvb Eei pwrng yuvd mcvg zyrug maiq zu'g maaig kanb Eei Dau.
47.12: yo-sepq pun Eang hopq ninb Eei tia, ninb Eei muab txig, lyemb ninb Eei tia Eei yetg zuvq pyauq zov myenb, ziuj myenb laanb Jwav ninb Bua.
47.15: i-yipq myenb Zauj Kaa-naa-an myenb Eei Eaanb lovg Fav Revg mig a'q. i-yipq myenb zyrug mivb lxd yo-sepq kxvq, “Toq pun teij Naavj yia Bua Eang. yia Bua weig haiq tiug xij zu'g yem meib Eei Ra'Myen vxg taig? weig zu'g yia Bua Eei Eaanb Revg mig a'q.”
47.13: kxmj uaq nxm teib puv maiq maaib Eang hopq. myenb vxg tu'q Kruq! haig. i-yipq teib puv Zauj Kaa-naa-an teib puv Eei myenb vxg kau Naavj, Jaig Revg mig a'q.
47.1: yo-sepq zyrug Rwrnj mivb Buaj faa-lo huvb, “yia Eei tia Zauj yia Eei muab txig yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv pyenb Jyenq ninb Bua Eei yuvb, pa'ki yuvb, scvb Kuq, yetg zuvq ka'naaiq taaib Tauj a'q. ib zang ninb Bua yem uaq ko-sen.”
47.26: yo-sepq lyepg tiub leid taaib, Zxg lovg Jyenq Tauj ib Jaaj Nxi, se i-yipq teib puv Eei kcvb zwavj ka'naaiq pyaa kruq xij zu'g pun kruq huvb tiaj. Kuvj maaib sai myenb Eei Dau Navq maiq penj huvb tiaj Eei pwrng.
47.25: pc'g fivj kxvq, “meib Fruj Zwrtq yia Bua Eei mcvg. Toq pun yia Bua yem meib Eei Ra'Myen tu'q lovj, yia Bua zyrug lcvd zruj faa-lo huvb Eei nrub.”

10.18: aan-watq myenb, sej-me myenb Zauj haa-matq myenb. Ga'haaq Kaa-naa-an Eei Zamb fivj myenb Raanj mivb yem.
10.8: Kutq maaib taub txn, Buaj heug nim-lotq, se yem luvb Diaq penj taub taamq Lo, maaib panb zeig Eei myenb.
10.3: ko-me Eei txn se atg-Ke-natq, li-faatq, Zauj To-kaan-maa.
10.32: naaiq teij myenb yem no-yaa pun Fiag Eei zeib fun ziuj ninb Bua Eei trub zov, yem ninb Bua Eei kua'q. yem Byuvb swib imj yemj liud luvb Diaq, Ga'haaq naaiq teij myenb yetg zuvq Raanj mivb yem kxmj luvb Diaq.
10.21: sem se yaa-fetq Eei tomb kxj, yaag maaib txnb Jweiq Zamq Eei. ninb zruj e-Be Eei zeib fun Eei ovb Taaib vc'q.
10.14: patg-lu-simj, Katq-lu-him, (tovb zruj fi-li-saa-tia myenb Eei ovb Taaib vc'q uaq taub), Zauj Kapq-To-lim myenb.
10.23: aa-lam Eei txn se utg, hun, ke-Te Zauj matq.
10.6: haam Eei txn se Kutq, i-yipq, Putq Zauj Kaa-naa-an.
10.2: yaa-fetq Eei txn se ko-me, maa-kokg, maa-Dai, yaa-waan, Tu-Ban, me-sekq, Zauj Ti-laatq.
10.20: naaiq teij yetg zuvq se haam Eei zeib fun, ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng, ziuj ninb Bua Eei waag, ziuj ninb Bua Eei teig Zauj ninb Bua Eei kua'q.
10.24: aan-faa-satq zruj Qe-laa Eei tia. Qe-laa yaag zruj e-Be Eei tia.
10.7: Kutq Eei txn se sej-Baa, haa-wi-laa, sapg-Taa, laa-aa-maa Zauj sapg-Te-Kaa. laa-aa-maa Eei txn se Qe-Baa Zauj De-Daan.
10.29: o-fi, haa-wi-laa Zauj yo-Bapg. naaiq teij yetg zuvq zruj yokq-Taan Eei txn.
10.19: ninb Bua Eei kapg Jaaij yem sai-Dxn yavb naamb puv Tauj ke-laa-aa, nitq kaa-saa uaq. cvj mivb tov puv mcvj Tauj soj-Dom, ko-mo-laa, atg-maa Zauj sej-Bo-yim Tauj laa-saa uaq.
10.17: hi-wai myenb, aan-Kaa myenb, sij-ni myenb,
10.31: naaiq teij yetg zuvq se sem Eei zeib fun, ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng, ziuj ninb Bua Eei waag, ziuj ninb Bua Eei teig, Zauj ninb Bua Eei kua'q.
10.30: ninb Bua yem Eei teib puv se yem me-saa mivb sej-faa uaq puv, tov puv mcvj Bovb aiq txvj.
10.11: ninb yem naaiq Zwrtq mivb Tauj atg-si-lia teib puv Zeij Jiad ni-naa-we, le-hoj-Botg-i, Kaa-laa
10.5: (se naaiq teij myenb Eei hod txig Raanj mivb yem Kxib Len, kx'g myenb ziuj ninb Bua Eei kua'q, ziuj ninb Bua Eei fivj, ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng, ziuj ninb Bua Eei waag.)
10.9: ziuj zyruq mavg, nim-lotq zruj taub pwrnq xq henq haig Eei myenb. weig naaiq maaib waag kxvq, “Navq nim-lotq, ziuj zyruq mavg, ninb penj taub pwrnq xq henq haig Eei myenb.”
10.16: Kaa-naa-an yaag zruj Zamb fivj myenb Eei ovb Taaib vc'q. maaib ye-Butg myenb, aa-mo-lai myenb, ke-kaa-si myenb,
10.4: yaa-waan Eei txn se e-li-se-aa, Taan-sitq, Kitq-Tim Zauj lo-Daa-nim.
10.10: nim-lotq Eei kua'q taaub tavb maaib Baa-Ben, e-lekq Zauj akg-Katq. naaiq teij yetg zuvq yem si-naa teib puv.
10.22: sem Eei txn se e-laam, atg-su, aan-faa-satq, lu-De Zauj aa-lam.
10.12: Zauj le-senj uaq teij pyei nxm zivb. le-senj zivb yem ni-naa-we Zauj Kaa-laa zivb Bu'Dovj. Kaa-laa zruj tomb zivb.
10.15: Kaa-naa-an maaib i taub txn. txnb Lo heug sai-Dxn. txnb faij heug hetq.
10.13: i-yipq Eei txn se lu-Dim, aa-naa-mim, le-haa-Bim, napq-Tu-him,
10.1: yem naaiq mivb kxvq no-yaa Eei txn, sem, haam Zauj yaa-fetq Eei zeib fun. se Byuvb swib imj yemj liud luvb Diaq, Ga'haaq ninb Bua pua taub tu'q Eei txn.
10.26: yokq-Taan Eei txn se an-mo-Datg, Qe-lepq, haa-saan-maa-wetq, ye-laa,
10.25: e-Be maaib i taub txn. maaib taub, Buaj heug pe-lekq, weig zu'g yem ninb Eei seij zeiq myenb pun Gxi Daub peib yem. ninb Eei yrud heug yokq-Taan.

25.18: i-saa-maa-en Eei zeib fun Bua yem haa-wi-laa Zauj su-waa Bu'Dovj, yaag yem nitq i-yipq teib puv Eei kapg Jaaij, mivb atg-si-lia teib puv uaq tiub Jauq. ninb Bua Eei zeib fun maiq Zauj apg-laa-ham Eei kanb teij zeib fun yem.
25.8: ninb zyavb tu'q syrug Ewrnb Daauq, penj myenb koj myenb zyrug tavj Qiaj, kwei seij mig a'q.
25.33: yaa-Kopq kxvq, “mq paag meib xij zu'g hruq maaig pun yia Daavg.” e-saau hruq liud zyrug maaig ninb zruj txnb Lo tu'q suvb kruq Eei leid pun yaa-Kopq mig a'q.
25.3: yokq-saan Eei txn Eei Buaj heug Qe-Baa Zauj De-Daan. De-Daan Eei txn pun Fiag penj atg-su-lim, le-Tu-sim Zauj le-um-mim myenb.
25.32: e-saau tau, “mavg maa'b! yia xij taig haig a'q. zruj kxj tu'q suvb kruq Eei leid weig yia maaib haiq Euvg maaib lamb lovg?”
25.21: le-Be-Kaa maiq maaib fu'Jweiq, i-sakg zyrug weig ninb Eei auq tauj kauj Toq zyruq pun ninb Eei auq maaib fu'Jweiq. zyruq ei i-sakg Toq Eei waag zruj, le-Be-Kaa zyrug maaib kub vwaad a'q.
25.23: zyruq kxvq Buaj ninb, “maaib i fivj myenb yem meib Eei ka'sia ka'Euad. meib yuvd Zwrtq naaiq teij i fivj, yetg fivj Zauj yetg fivj xij pun Gxi. naaiq fivj xij kaub henq uaq fivj. kxj yaag xij zu'g fub suj yrud.”
25.6: mq paag apg-laa-ham maiq kcvb kwei seij uaq zang ninb pun zivb Eeig ninb Eei aub txn Eei txn Bua. Ga'haaq zyrug heug ninb Bua leib Gxi i-sakg mivb yem tov puv mcvj Eei teib puv,
25.34: yaa-Kopq zyrug zx'q teij Fuaq Zauj topg pun e-saau Eang. Eang liud hopq liud, e-saau zyrug Jiad sin mivb mig a'q. maiq Kxb fi'q ninb zruj txnb Lo tu'q suvb kruq Eei leid.
25.2: Ke-Tu-laa yuvd tu'q Zamb taub txn pun ninb. maaib simj-laan, yokq-saan, me-Daan, mi-Dyen, itg-Baakg Zauj Qu-waa.
25.20: i-sakg lovg le-Be-Kaa zruj auq uaq zang ninb tu'q feij zyepg Havj. le-Be-Kaa zruj Be-Tu-en Eei sia'q. Be-Tu-en se aa-lam myenb, yem patg-Daan-aa-lam. le-Be-Kaa yaag zruj aa-lam myenb, laa-Baan Eei muag.
25.24: Tauj yuvd Eei zyavb hog ninb zyrug yuvd tu'q suvb kub vwaab txn.
25.28: i-sakg kaub Namq e-saau, weig zu'g ninb tu'q Eang e-saau pwrnq taaib Eei xq. mq paag le-Be-Kaa kaub Namq yaa-Kopq.
25.7: apg-laa-ham Eei Havb Jeiq zyavb tu'q yetg pc'q Zyetq zyepg Mmd Havj.
25.29: maaib Nxi nx, yaa-Kopq wrnb Jyenq topg si'q, e-saau mivb kemb Rwrnj taaib, Hruq za'kevb! sia haig.
25.19: yem naaiq mivb kxvq apg-laa-ham Eei txn, i-sakg, Eei Jaub lrug. apg-laa-ham zruj i-sakg Eei tia.
25.17: i-saa-maa-en Eei Havb Jeiq zyavb tu'q yetg pc'q faab zyepg Zyetq Havj, ninb tavj Qiaj, kwei seij mig a'q.
25.31: yaa-Kopq kxvq, “maaig meib zruj txnb Lo tu'q suvb kruq Eei leid pun yia Daavg maa'b!”
25.30: ninb kxvq Buaj yaa-Kopq, “yia Hruq sia, xij taig haig a'q. pun teij uaq Euvg ka'naaib si'q yia na'q kaaj.” (weig naaiq myenb Zwrtq Buaj heug ninb zruj e-Dom.)
25.27: naaiq teij i taub txn Lo taaib. e-saau zruj taub pwrnq xq henq haig Eei myenb. haiq zang yaag xij mivb kemb pwrnq xq. yaa-Kopq c'q, waag zo'g, Hruq Do Eei myenb. ninb xij yem pyauq kaub Zamq.
25.11: apg-laa-ham kwei seij liud, Tinb huvb Zeij fu'q pun ninb Eei txn, i-sakg. i-sakg yem nitq Be-e-laa-hai-lxi.
25.5: apg-laa-ham Jiu ninb Eei Jaab tivb yetg zuvq ka'naaiq pun ninb Eei txn, i-sakg, Ripg Revg.
25.9: ninb Eei txn, i-sakg Zauj i-saa-maa-en, txb ninb mivb zavj nitq mam-le uaq nxm makq-pe-laa Bcvb Kwrtq. naaiq nxm Bcvb Kwrtq yem hitq-Tai myenb, soj-haaj Eei txn, e-fo-lon, Eei Deig.
25.16: naaiq se i-saa-maa-en Eei txn Eei Buaj. ninb pun Fiag zruj zyepg Eeig fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq. ninb Bua lyepg Eei laavd Zauj Zxv Dopg liub Eei txvj kan ninb Bua kanb Eei Buaj heug.
25.4: mi-Dyen Eei txn heug e-faa, e-fe, haa-nokq, aa-Bi-Daa Zauj en-Daa-aa. naaiq teij yetg zuvq zruj Ke-Tu-laa Eei zeib fun.
25.10: se apg-laa-ham Tevj hitq-Tai myenb maaid Eei Deig. apg-laa-ham Zauj ninb Eei auq, saa-laa, zyrug zavj Jyenq uaq a'q.
25.22: maaib suvb kub vwaad. kub vwaad yem maa Eei ka'sia pxvd Jaaj. le-Be-Kaa kxvq, “yia weig haiq tiug Dovg naaiq Kruq?” ninb zyrug mivb naaig zyruq.
25.12: ib zang kxvq apg-laa-ham Eei txn, i-saa-maa-en, Eei zeib fun, tovb saa-laa Eei nrub peid, i-yipq myenb, haa-kaa, yuvd pun apg-laa-ham uaq taub txn Eei zeib fun.
25.15: haa-Datg, Te-maa, ye-Tu, naa-fitq, Zauj Ke-De-maa.
25.13: yem naaiq mivb kxvq i-saa-maa-en Eei txn Eei Buaj zweib Lo Tauj faij. txnb Lo heug ne-Baa-yotq. cvj maaib Ke-Daa, atg-Be-en, mipq-samj,
25.1: apg-laa-ham cvj lovg taub auq, Buaj heug Ke-Tu-laa.
25.26: Ga'haaq yuvd uaq taub nanq Jyenq ninb Eei kxj, e-saau, Eei zaub Go Zwrtq. ninb Bua zyrug Zwrtq Buaj heug yaa-Kopq. le-Be-Kaa yuvd naaiq teij i taub txn uaq zang, i-sakg tu'q lua'g zyepg Havj.
25.25: yuvd Zwrtq Daavg uaq taub, sin si'q Eei, zyavb sin Zwrtq pyei su'g su'q uaq, Navq maaib pyei Eei Dopg lwi nx. ninb Bua zyrug Zwrtq Buaj heug e-saau.

22.18: luvb Diaq maang kua'q myenb weig meib Eei zeib fun xij tu'q fu'q, weig zu'g meib mwavj yia Eei waag.’+”
22.8: apg-laa-ham tau, “aa txn aag, Tinb huvb kanb xij liug leid zyavj puaq ziag Eei pa'ki yuvb txn.” i txnb tiaj cvj yavb Jyenq mivb.
22.3: ta'Eeig Dxm Ryruq Eei, apg-laa-ham Jiad sin taaib pwig Jyenq ninb Eei lxb, txb i taub ninb Eei pru Zauj ninb Eei txn, i-sakg, mivb. ninb kc'q zaavb kauj ninb xij puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq zyrug Zwrtq Jauq mivb Tinb huvb Buaj ninb mivb uaq nxm txvj.
22.21: txnb Lo heug utg. ninb Eei yrud heug Butg, Ke-mu-en (se aa-lam Eei tia),
22.14: uaq nxm txvj apg-laa-ham Tevj Zwrtq Buaj heug “zyruq kanb xij liug leid zyavj.” ib Jaaj Nxi myenb Zxg kxvq, “yem zyruq Eei Bov, zyruq kanb liug leid zyavj pun.”
22.23: Be-Tu-en zruj le-Be-Kaa Eei tia. min-Kaa yuvd tu'q naaiq teij Yetg taub txn pun apg-laa-ham Eei yrud, naa-ho.
22.6: apg-laa-ham zx'q lovg puaq ziag Eei zaavb pun ninb Eei txn, i-sakg, Eiaj Jyenq. ninb kanb txb trud Zauj Ru'g. ninb Bua i txnb tiaj mivb a'q.
22.2: Tinb huvb kxvq, “meib xij zu'g txb meib Eei txn, se meib Eei Do'g txn, i-sakg, tovb meib Namq uaq taub, mivb mo-li-yaa teig. Tauj uaq yia zyrug Buaj meib xij zu'g faauj haiq nxm Bov lovg meib Eei txn zruj puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq.”
22.20: naaiq teij sig Jiaj liud, Ga'haaq maaib myenb taaib Buaj apg-laa-ham, “min-Kaa yaag yuvd tu'q fu'Jweiq pun meib Eei yrud, naa-ho, mig a'q.
22.24: cvj maaib naa-ho Eei aub txn, le-u-maa, yuvd tu'q Te-Baa, kaa-ham, Taa-haatg Zauj maa-aa-Kaa.
22.7: i-sakg Zauj ninb Eei tia, apg-laa-ham, kxvq, “aa tia aa'b!” apg-laa-ham tau, “aa txn aag, zruj haiq Euvg?” i-sakg kxvq, “maaib trud, maaib zaavb Eei, mq paag lovg puaq ziag Eei pa'ki yuvb txn yem haaij?”
22.19: apg-laa-ham cvj taauj sin Rwrnj Tauj ninb Eei pru uaq. ninb Bua lomb Rxib Rwrnj Be-e-Qe-Baa. apg-laa-ham cvj yem uaq Be-e-Qe-Baa.
22.17: yia Dovg haaij zuvq xij Zeij fu'q pun meib. yia xij pun meib Eei zeib fun Yaavj Jyenq faauj Dovg luvb Eei Leij Zamq yaag Dovg Kxib Len Eei saab zyru Zamq. meib Eei zeib fun yaag xij tu'q ninb Bua Eei winb wavq Eei zivb zruj ninb Bua Ripg Eei pwrng.
22.11: mq paag zyruq Eei finb myenb yem kub vwaaig luvb Kaatq apg-laa-ham kxvq, “apg-laa-ham aa'b! apg-laa-ham!” apg-laa-ham tau, “oij! yia yem naaiq og.”
22.5: apg-laa-ham kxvq Buaj ninb Eei pru, “meib Bua Zauj lxb yem naaiq zuaq og. yia Bua i txnb tiaj xij mivb uaq zavg zyruq, Ga'haaq yia Bua cvj Rwrnj meib Bua naaiq.”
22.9: mivb Tauj Tinb huvb Buaj ninb uaq nxm txvj, apg-laa-ham Zeij nxm ziab txvb taaib, zx'q zaavb zweib yetq zweib Eeig Baib Jyenq ziab txvb kub vwaaig. ninb yaag zx'q ninb Eei txn, i-sakg, Dob Jyenq an Jyenq ziab txvb, zaavb Dwi kub vwaaig.
22.16: “zyruq kxvq, ‘yia zyavq Jyenq yia kanb lcvd waag weig zu'g meib Navq naaiq zruj. meib maiq Rcv meib Eei txn, se meib Eei Do'g txn.
22.4: Tauj ta'faam Nxi apg-laa-ham Zau Myen mavg pwatg uaq nxm txvj mq paag Zxg ko Eei.
22.10: ninb zyrug Haa puad zx'q Ru'g weig taij ninb Eei txn.
22.22: Ke-setg, haa-so, pin-Daatg, yitq-laapq, Zauj Be-Tu-en.”
22.12: finb myenb kxvq, “maiq tuvq hxig naaiq taub txn. maiq tuvq zruj haiq Euvg pun ninb. ib zang yia hiuq tu'q meib kamb Riaj yaag Taaib Tinb huvb weig zu'g meib maiq Rcv meib Eei txn, Eung zx'q meib Eei Do'g txn fuvj pun yia.”
22.15: zyruq Eei finb myenb yem kub vwaaig luvb cvj heug ta'Eeig Rung kxvq Buaj apg-laa-ham,
22.13: apg-laa-ham Zau Myen Win Rwrnj mavg Ga'haaq Gaav, pwatg maaib taub pa'ki yuvb kruq, Jxv Kwavj Jyenq lomb Byx'g. ninb zyrug mivb zx'q taaib zruj puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq tiq ninb Eei txn.
22.1: naaiq teij sig Jiaj liud, Ga'haaq Tinb huvb seij apg-laa-ham. Tinb huvb kxvq Buaj ninb, “apg-laa-ham aag.” apg-laa-ham tau, “oij! yia yem naaiq og.”

42.18: Tauj ta'faam Nxi, yo-sepq kxvq Buaj ninb kxj Bua, “yia se zavg Tinb huvb Eei myenb. sij kxvq meib Bua ziuj yia Eei waag zruj, meib Bua zyrug tu'q meib Bua Eei mcvg Zwrtq.
42.8: yo-sepq zia'q tu'q ninb kxj Bua Eei, mq paag ninb Eei kxj Bua zia'q maiq tu'q ninb.
42.33: “uaq nxm teib puv Eei zyruq kxvq, ‘yia Navq naaiq nx zruj seij mavg kaaj meib Bua za'kevb Hruq za'g fai maiq za'g. meib Bua xij zu'g pun taub Zauj yia yem naaiq. uaq teij txb Byaub Rwrnj mivb pun vxg Naavj Eei Mwavq txig Eang.
42.3: yo-sepq Eei zyepg taub kxj zyrug mivb i-yipq teib puv maaid Byaub a'q.
42.32: yetg zuvq maaib zyepg Eeig muab txn Jwavg taub tia. maaib taub yrud maiq yem a'q. yrub laai Zxg Zauj ninb Eei tia yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv.’
42.21: laanb kxvq Buaj laanb, “zinb Daavg Bua zruj to'g Bua Eei yrud. uaq zang Bua pwatg ninb Dovg haaij Kruq, ninb Fiag Qa'q Toq Bua, Bua yaag maiq mwavj. weig naaiq, Bua ib zang Zivj pwavb zu'g naaiq teij sig.”
42.35: ninb Bua toj Byaub Zwrtq uaq zang, kx'g myenb pwatg kx'g myenb Eei Eaanb peu yem uaq Byaub Bua'g ka'Euad. ninb Bua Zauj ninb Bua Eei tia pwatg Eaanb peu, ninb Bua zyrug kamb Riaj haig.
42.14: yo-sepq cvj tau, “za'kevb Navq yia kxvq nx. meib Bua taaib zaab teib puv Navq.
42.23: ninb Bua maiq hiuq tu'q yo-sepq mevb pc'g ninb Bua kxvq Eei waag weig zu'g ninb haiq zang Zauj ninb Bua kxvq waag maaib myenb Tevj faan.
42.6: yo-sepq zruj i-yipq teib puv Eei zuvj, maaig Byaub pun pc'g fivj. ninb Eei kxj Bua mivb Tauj uaq zyrug Pua'q Fiag Tauj Dau paaij yo-sepq.
42.34: xij zu'g txb meib Bua Eei yrub laai taaib pun yia mavg. yia zyrug hiuq tu'q meib Bua Hruq za'g Eei myenb, maiq zeid taaib zaab teib puv. yia zyrug puvj meib Bua Eei kxj pun meib Bua. meib Bua yem naaiq teib puv zruj scvb eij yaag tu'q Eei.’+”
42.2: yia haid kxvq i-yipq teib puv maaib Byaub Eei. meib Bua mivb maaid teij taaib Eang maa'b! Tevj Bua maiq zu'g vxg Naavj taig.”
42.36: ninb Bua Eei tia, yaa-Kopq, kxvq Buaj ninb Bua, “meib Bua xij zruj pun yia Eei fu'Jweiq maiq zevg yetg taub? maiq maaib yo-sepq a'q. yaag maiq maaib si-me-on. ib zang meib Bua cvj xij txb Ben-yaa-min mivb. haiq Euvg sig yaag Kuvj hxig yia tiaq Navq.”
42.20: mq paag meib Bua xij zu'g txb meib Bua Eei yrub laai taaib yia naaiq. Navq naaiq zyrug pun Ziv meib Bua Eei waag se zyen. meib Bua yaag maiq zu'g taig.” ninb Bua zyrug lcvd ei Jyenq zruj.
42.24: yo-sepq haid naaiq teij waag, ninb zyrug Zwrtq mivb Eyemq. Eyemq liud, ninb cvj pia'g mivb Zauj ninb Bua kxvq waag yaag zx'q si-me-on Zwrtq taaib txv Jyenq ninb Bua Dob Jyenq a'q.
42.28: ninb kxvq Buaj ninb Eei muab txig, “yia Eei Eaanb ninb Bua cvj pun Rwrnj taaib cj! yem naaiq yia Eei Bua'g Rwib.” ninb Bua haid Hruq waaig Revg, meib mavg yia, yia mavg meib, sin zinj Jyenq kxvq, “Tinb huvb Navq haiq nx zruj pun Bua mq pei?”
42.7: yo-sepq zia'q tu'q ninb Eei kxj Bua mq paag ninb zruj Navq maiq hiuq nx. ninb Zauj ninb Bua kxvq waag pe'q Eei naaig kaaj, “meib Bua yem haaij taaib?” ninb Bua tau, “yia Bua yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv taaib maaid Byaub.”
42.29: Rwrnj Tauj Kaa-naa-an teib puv, ninb Bua Eei tia, yaa-Kopq uaq, ninb Bua zweib yetq zweib Eeig Eei kxvq Revg ninb Bua pwavb Eei sig pun ninb mwavj.
42.19: meib Bua za'kevb Hruq za'g Eei myenb nx, xij zu'g pun taub wrnj Jyenq naaiq lob. uaq teij txb Byaub Rwrnj pun yem pyauq vxg Naavj Eei Mwavq txig Eang.
42.17: kxvq liud, yo-sepq zx'q ninb Bua txb mivb wrnj Jyenq lob pua Nxi.
42.38: mq paag yaa-Kopq kxvq, “yia Dovg haaij zuvq maiq pun yia Eei txn Zauj meib Bua mivb. ninb Eei kxj taig mig a'q. Kuvj zevg ninb kanb Navq. kamb Riaj Daamb Jauq pwavb zu'g haiq Euvg sig hxig ninb, meib Bua zyrug pun yia, ovb mGxvb pc'g, Raub tu'q taig Eei.”
42.31: yia Bua tau, ‘yia Bua maiq zeid taaib zaab teib puv. yia Bua se Hruq za'g Eei myenb.
42.30: ninb Bua kxvq, “uaq nxm teib puv Eei zyruq kxvq Zyruq Eei pun yia Bua, Navq yia Bua zruj zaab teib puv Eei myenb.
42.27: uaq mwrnd Tauj ninb Bua hitq Eei txvj, maaib taub Kxi ninb Eei Bua'g, xij zx'q teij Byaub wij lxb, yaag pwatg maaid Byaub Eei Eaanb yem uaq Bua'g Rwib.
42.11: yia Bua yetg zuvq penj yetg taub tia Eei txn. yia Bua yetg zuvq, meib Eei pru, Hruq zivj Eei myenb. yia Bua maiq zeid taaib zaab teib puv.”
42.5: yaa-Kopq Eei txn Bua Zauj Jyenq myenb Zamq mivb i-yipq teib puv maaid Byaub weig zu'g Kaa-naa-an teib puv yaag pwavb tomb vxg.
42.9: yo-sepq Javj zu'g ninb zinb Daavg Beij Eei Beij. ninb cvj kxvq, “meib Bua taaib Zaaiq Jua'q zaab mavg yia Bua Eei teib puv mau Eei txvj Navq.”
42.16: pun taub Rwrnj mivb txb meib Bua Eei yrub laai taaib. zevg Fiag naaiq teij, yia wrnj Jyenq zuaq Tauj yia Bua hiuq tu'q meib Bua Eei waag za'kevb zyen fai maiq zyen. sij kxvq meib Bua Eei waag maiq zyen, yia zyrug hiuq tu'q tivg, Dovg yia hiuq tu'q faa-lo huvb zyavb Jyenq nx, meib Bua za'kevb taaib zaab teib puv Navq.”
42.37: lu-Ben kxvq Buaj ninb Eei tia, “sij kxvq yia maiq tu'q txb Ben-yaa-min Rwrnj taaib pun meib, meib kunq zx'q yia Eei i taub txn taij kwavg tu'q Eei. kunq pun yia kruj Ben-yaa-min. yia cvj txb ninb Rwrnj taaib pun meib.”
42.4: mq paag yo-sepq Eei yrud, Ben-yaa-min, yaa-Kopq maiq pun kan ninb kxj Bua mivb. kamb Riaj haib pwavb zu'g haiq Euvg hxig ninb mq pei.
42.10: ninb Bua tau, “zyruq aa'b! kevb maiq zeid! yia Bua, meib Eei pru, taaib maaid Byaub Navq.
42.22: lu-Ben kxvq, “yia paaq meib Bua maiq tuvq zruj hxig uaq taub txn, mq paag meib Bua maiq mwavj. ib zang laaij taij ninb, Bua Zivj taaib xij zu'g syrug zwid Dovg naaiq Kruq.”
42.12: yo-sepq cvj kxvq, “maiq zeid a'q. meib Bua taaib samj mavg yia Bua Eei teib puv haiq nxm txvj Piaj Navq.”
42.15: yia Navq naaiq nx seij meib Bua. yia zyavq Jyenq faa-lo huvb Eei mcvg hruq waag. Zwrtq liud meib Bua Eei yrub laai taaib Tauj naaiq, meib Bua maiq tu'q Zwrtq naaiq nxm txvj.
42.13: ninb Bua kxvq, “yia Bua, meib Eei pru, yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv. yetg zuvq maaib zyepg Eeig muab txn Jwavg taub tia. yrub laai Zauj yia Bua Eei tia yem pyauq. cvj maaib taub yrud taig mig a'q.”
42.1: yaa-Kopq haid kxvq i-yipq teib puv maaib Byaub Eei. ninb zyrug Buaj ninb Eei txn, “meib Bua zruj haiq Euvg vib vxvb vxvd naaig? meib mavg yia, yia mavg meib Navq!
42.26: yo-sepq Eei kxj Bua Beng zyavj pun lxb Tx Jyenq Byaub zyrug Zwrtq Jauq Rwrnj.
42.25: yo-sepq heug myenb zx'q Byaub tapq pwavq ninb kxj Bua Eei Bua'g, cvj zx'q kx'g myenb maaid Byaub Eei Eaanb tapq kx'g myenb Eei Bua'g Rwib, cvj Tevj ninb Bua liug leid Daamb Jauq Eang Eei pyenb fwij pun ninb Bua. myenb zyrug ei Jyenq ninb Eei waag zruj.

28.18: ta'Eeig Dxm yaa-Kopq Jiad sin taaib Ryruq Eei, zx'q ninb Romd uaq nxm la'pyeiq lyepg Jiad taaib ton Jyenq zruj Javb hog. cvj zx'q yrub toj Jyenq la'pyeiq fuvj pun Tinb huvb.
28.8: e-saau zyrug zia'q tu'q ninb Eei tia, i-sakg, maiq a'Neiq Kaa-naa-an sia'q.
28.3: Toq nrnb Jiaj Eei Tinb huvb Zeij fu'q pun meib Yaavj taaib maaib fu'Jweiq Zamq, zyrug tu'q zruj Zamb fivj myenb Eei ovb Taaij.
28.21: yaag pun yia pcvb xn Eei Rwrnj yia Eei tia Eei pyauq nx, zyruq zyrug penj yia Eei Tinb huvb a'q.
28.14: meib Eei zeib fun xij Navq luvb Diaq Eei niab Buv Zamq. ninb Bua xij Yaavj Javq Jyenq mivb tov naamb fai pa'q. weig meib Zauj meib Eei zeib fun luvb Diaq maang fivj xij tu'q fu'q.
28.6: e-saau hiuq tu'q ninb Eei tia, i-sakg, pwav waag yaa-Kopq, Buaj ninb mivb patg-Daan-aa-lam lxd auq lovg. ninb yaag hiuq tu'q, pwav waag uaq zang i-sakg heug ninb maiq tuvq lovg Kaa-naa-an myenb Eei sia'q zruj auq.
28.2: meib xij zu'g mivb patg-Daan-aa-lam, meib Eei taa ov, Be-Tu-en, Eei pyauq. yem uaq lovg auq, lovg taub meib Eei maa Eei kxj, laa-Baan, Eei sia'q.
28.20: yaa-Kopq cvj lcvd vcvg waag. ninb kxvq, “sij kxvq Tinb huvb Zauj yia yem tovb ib zang yia mivb Eei Jauq, yaag kruj Jyenq yia, pun yia maaib Eang maaib hopq, maaib lwib hruj zu'q,
28.7: cvj pwatg yaa-Kopq mwavj ninb tiaj maag Eei waag za'kevb mivb patg-Daan-aa-lam mig a'q.
28.19: uaq nxm txvj ninb Zwrtq Buaj heug Betg-en. (zinb Daavg uaq nxm zivb Eei Buaj heug lutq.)
28.17: ninb za'kevb kamb Riaj haig cvj kxvq, “naaiq za'kevb yiaq haig Eei txvj. Navq haaij zuvq zruj Tinb huvb Eei ting, yaag zruj Tinb txvb Eei kcvb.”
28.11: mivb kau, Tauj nxm txvj pwatg Ba'Nxi mwrtq mig a'q, zyrug hitq uaq. ninb pweij uaq Romd Jyenq la'pyeiq mFxmb.
28.5: Navq naaig i-sakg zyrug heug yaa-Kopq mivb patg-Daan-aa-lam, mivb lxd aa-lam myenb, Be-Tu-en Eei txn, laa-Baan. laa-Baan yaag zruj yaa-Kopq Zauj e-saau Eei maa, le-Be-Kaa, Eei kxj.
28.9: ninb zyrug mivb lxd taub apg-laa-ham Eei txn, i-saa-maa-en, Eei sia'q, ne-Baa-yotq Eei muag, Buaj heug maa-haa-latq, lovg zruj aub faam.
28.16: yaa-Kopq Eia taaib kxvq, “zyruq za'kevb yem naaiq nxm txvj mq paag yia lyemb maiq hiuq.”
28.4: Toq ninb Zeij fu'q pun meib Zauj meib Eei zeib fun Navq zinb Daavg ninb Zeij fu'q pun apg-laa-ham uaq nx. yaag pun meib Bua tu'q meib ib zang yem Jyenq naaiq nxm teib puv penj meib Bua Eei pwrng, tovb zinb Daavg Tinb huvb Zeij pun apg-laa-ham Eei teib puv.”
28.10: yaa-Kopq Zwrtq Be-e-Qe-Baa, huvj Jyenq mivb haa-laan zivb.
28.22: yia lyepg naaiq nxm la'pyeiq taaib weig zruj Javb hog zyrug penj Tinb huvb Eei ting. ta'faanb meib pun haiq Euvg yia, yia xij zx'q zyepg kruq Eei yetg kruq fovg hxg meib.”
28.12: ninb Beij pwatg maaib zuv Tei yem ka'Diaq Dau lyepg faauj Tauj kub vwaaig luvb. yaag pwatg Tinb huvb Eei finb myenb faaub faauj Fiab Fiag Eei.
28.15: Javj Jyenq og. maiq kunq meib mivb Tauj haaij yia Zauj meib yem, xij kruj Jyenq meib. yia yaag xij txb meib cvj Rwrnj Tauj naaiq nxm teib puv. yia zuvq maiq leib Gxi meib, Tauj yia zruj zyavj ei yia lcvd Eei waag.”
28.13: yaag maaib zyruq sruq Jyenq Tei kub vwaaig kxvq Buaj ninb, “yia se zyruq, meib Eei ov, apg-laa-ham, Eei Tinb huvb, Zauj i-sakg Eei Tinb huvb. tovb meib ib zang pweij naaiq teij Dau yia xij Jiu pun meib Zauj meib Eei zeib fun.
28.1: i-sakg zyrug heug yaa-Kopq taaib yaag pwav waag pun ninb, zyrug hatg ninb, “meib maiq tuvq lovg Kaa-naa-an myenb Eei sia'q zruj auq.

29.18: yaa-Kopq Namq haig laa-sen zyrug kxvq Buaj laa-Baan, “sij kxvq tomb naud lcvd pun meib Eei sia'g faij, laa-sen, yia nx, yia lcvd Tevj meib zruj siag Havj kov.”
29.8: ninb Bua tau, “yia Bua maiq haib Navq naaig zruj. yia Bua xij zu'g zuaq kwanb kwanb pa'ki yuvb taaib Rxib Zivj Ryen Gxi la'pyeiq zaavb uam pun yuvb hopq.”
29.33: le-aa cvj maaib Jyenq sin, yuvd tu'q taub txn. ninb kxvq, “zyruq pun yia cvj tu'q naaiq taub txn weig zu'g ninb mwavj haid yia Eei Goj maiq Namq yia.” le-aa zyrug Zwrtq naaiq taub txn Eei Buaj heug si-me-on.
29.3: zuaq kwanb kwanb pa'ki yuvb Tauj Rxib, mavg yuvb Eei myenb zyrug Ryen Gxi la'pyeiq, zaavb uam taaib pun yuvb hopq. hopq liud, ninb Bua cvj zx'q uaq Kwaaiq la'pyeiq komq Jyenq uamb Kwrtq.
29.32: le-aa zyrug maaib Jyenq sin, yuvd tu'q taub txn. ninb kxvq, “se weig zu'g zyruq pwatg yia Eei Kruq naang. ib zang Riaj yia Eei Goj xij Namq yia mq pei?” ninb zyrug Zwrtq uaq taub txn Eei Buaj heug lu-Ben.
29.21: yaa-Kopq kxvq Buaj laa-Baan, “zyavb hog pwavq a'q. Toq pun yia Eei auq yia, weig pun yia tu'q pia'g mivb Zauj ninb pweij.”
29.35: ninb cvj maaib Jyenq sin, cvj yuvd tu'q taub txn. ninb kxvq, “naaiq Rung yia xij Zev zyruq. ” ninb Zwrtq Buaj heug yu-Daa. ninb tu'q liud naaiq taub txn zyrug maiq yuvd a'q.
29.14: laa-Baan zyrug kxvq, “meib za'kevb Zauj yia Jwavg Ryaamb fei Eei myenb.” yaa-Kopq Zauj laa-Baan yem yetg Laaj Eia'g.
29.23: mq paag uaq mwrnd laa-Baan fuvj ninb Eei sia'q, le-aa, mivb pun yaa-Kopq. yaa-Kopq yaag Zauj ninb pweij.
29.6: yaa-Kopq cvj naaig kaaj, “ninb lovj Eei saa'b?” ninb Bua tau, “ninb lovj Eei. uaq ni! ninb Eei sia'q, laa-sen, txb Jyenq laa-Baan Eei pa'ki yuvb taaib a'q lo'b!”
29.34: le-aa cvj maaib Rung sin, cvj yuvd tu'q taub txn. ninb kxvq, “yia yuvd tu'q pua taub txn. yia Eei Goj za'kevb! xij Namq yia.” ninb cvj Tevj uaq taub txn Zwrtq Buaj heug le-wi.
29.2: yem uaq ninb pwatg nxm uamb Kwrtq yem lomb Waav ka'Euad. maaib pua kwanb pa'ki yuvb pweij Jyenq uamb Kwrtq ka'Len weig zu'g kruj yuvb Eei myenb zaavb naaiq nxm uamb Kwrtq Eei uam pun yuvb hopq. pwav Jyenq uamb Kwrtq uaq Kwaaiq la'pyeiq yaag Lo Eei.
29.20: yaa-Kopq Tevj ninb Eei tomb naud zruj siag Havj kov weig pyetq laa-sen. ninb Namq haig laa-sen zyrug haid Navq i ziaj Nxi Navq.
29.24: (laa-Baan cvj pun taub ninb Eei nrub peid, Buaj heug sinj-paa, zruj le-aa Eei nrub peid.)
29.28: yaa-Kopq yaag lcvd a'q. zuaq naaiq nxm Zivb Jaab yinb Eei siag Nxi Jiaj liud, laa-Baan pun ninb Eei sia'g faij yaa-Kopq zruj auq.
29.7: yaa-Kopq naaig kaaj ninb Bua, “ib zang Ba'Nxi Zxg Lav Eei. maiq kcvb Tauj zyavb hog hxvb yuvb Rwrnj. meib Bua weig haiq tiug maiq zaavb uam pun pa'ki yuvb hopq cvj puvj ninb Bua mivb Eang miaq?”
29.29: (laa-Baan cvj pun taub ninb Eei nrub peid, Buaj heug Bin-haa, zruj laa-sen Eei nrub peid.)
29.19: laa-Baan kxvq, “puvj pun meib se kaub lovj puvj pun kanb taub. Navq naaig, kunq Zauj yia yem a'q.”
29.17: le-aa Eei mziv maiq navg Fav. laa-sen c'q, zyavb tu'q lovj, zyavb tu'q Rweig.
29.31: zyruq pwatg yaa-Kopq maiq Namq le-aa zyrug pun ninb haib maaib kub vwaad. laa-sen c'q, maiq haib maaib.
29.30: yaa-Kopq zyrug tu'q lovg laa-sen zruj auq yaag Namq laa-sen kaub Zamq le-aa. ninb cvj Tevj laa-Baan zruj siag Havj laavb.
29.27: meib xij zu'g zuaq naaiq nxm siag Nxi Eei yinb Jiaj liud, yia cvj pun sia'g faij meib lovg. mq paag meib xij zu'g cvj Tevj yia zruj siag Havj laavb.”
29.11: zaavb liud uam, yaa-Kopq zom laa-sen Eei Myen, a'Neiq kau, syavj Eyemq Eei.
29.5: ninb cvj naaig kaaj, “meib Bua hiuq tu'q naa-ho Eei fun, laa-Baan, Eei fai?” ninb Bua tau, “hiuq Eei og.”
29.9: yaa-Kopq Zauj naaiq teij myenb Zxg kxvq Jyenq waag uaq zang, laa-sen yaag hxvb Jyenq ninb Eei tia Eei pa'ki yuvb Tauj taaib, weig zu'g ninb kruj naaiq teij yuvb.
29.16: laa-Baan maaib i taub sia'q. sia'g Lo heug le-aa. sia'g faij heug laa-sen.
29.4: yaa-Kopq naaig kaaj kruj yuvb Eei myenb, “kxb yrud aag, meib Bua yem haaij taaib?” ninb Bua tau, “yia Bua yem haa-laan zivb taaib.”
29.10: yaa-Kopq pwatg ninb Eei maa Eei kxj, laa-Baan, Eei sia'q, laa-sen, hxvb Jyenq laa-Baan Eei pa'ki yuvb, ninb zyrug mivb uaq uamb Kwrtq Ryen Gxi la'pyeiq zaavb uam pun ninb Eei tomb naud Eei yuvb hopq.
29.22: laa-Baan zyrug Beng Zivb Jaab Naavj, Zivq uaq nxm txvj Eei zwavj myenb taaib.
29.12: ninb yaag Buaj laa-sen, “yia zruj meib Eei tia Eei Zyenb Ze'q, se zruj le-Be-Kaa Eei txn.” laa-sen zyrug Tiuj Rwrnj mivb Buaj ninb Eei tia.
29.15: laa-Baan kxvq Buaj yaa-Kopq, “meib maiq tuvq Namq laaij zruj Zyenb Ze'q muab txig xij zu'g pc'g pc'g Tevj yia zruj kov. meib xij lovg kovb zinb Bu'ziaj kunq Buaj yia.”
29.13: laa-Baan yetq haid kxvq ninb Eei muag Eei txn, yaa-Kopq, taaib, ninb zyrug Tiuj Jyenq mivb zipq, Qam Jyenq zom, yaag txb Jyenq Rwrnj pyauq mig a'q. yaa-Kopq kxvq Revg ninb Eei Jaub lrug pun laa-Baan mwavj.
29.1: yaa-Kopq cvj kan Jyenq Jauq mivb Tauj tov puv myenb Eei teib puv.
29.26: laa-Baan tau, “ziuj yia Bua yem naaiq, maiq maaib leid pun sia'g faij txv Jaa Daavg sia'g Lo.
29.25: Tauj luvb Fav, yaa-Kopq zia'q tu'q se le-aa, zyrug mivb txij laa-Baan kxvq, “meib weig haiq tiug Navq naaiq nx zruj pun yia? yia Tevj meib zruj kov pyetq laa-sen maiq zeid? meib weig haiq tiug Pyenj yia?”

30.18: le-aa kxvq, “weig zu'g yia pun yia Eei nrub peid yia Eei Goj lovg, Tinb huvb pun zivb Eeig yia.” ninb Zwrtq uaq taub txn Eei Buaj heug itg-saaj-Kaa.
30.8: laa-sen kxvq, “yia Zauj yia Eei txg Rcv tomb Jaaj yaag Rcv tu'q hivb.” ninb Tevj uaq taub txn Zwrtq Buaj heug napq-Taa-li.
30.33: Navq naaiq nx, Ga'haaq hivq yia zruj Hruq za'g fai maiq za'g, tia zyrug hiuq Eei. haiq zang mivb mavg yia Eei kovb zinb, pwatg haiq taub yuvb maiq pen yaag maiq maaib tyemq, fai pwatg haiq taub pa'ki yuvb txn maiq Jia'q nx, zyrug hiuq tu'q yia Pinj taaib a'q.”
30.3: laa-sen kxvq, “naaiq yia Eei nrub peid, Bin-haa. meib kunq Zauj ninb pweij maa'b! ninb haib yuvd kub vwaad pun yia, yia zyrug laaij ninb tu'q taub kub vwaad funj yia Eei pwrng.”
30.32: ib Nxi yia xij mivb timq mavg meib Eei yetg zuvq pa'ki yuvb Zauj yuvb kwanb. ta'faanb pa'ki yuvb maaib tyemq Zru, tyemq mwrng Eei, Zauj pa'ki yuvb txn Jia'q, Zauj taub taub yuvb maaib tyemq Zru fai tyemq mwrng Eei, yia lovg zruj yia Eei kovb zinb.
30.21: Ga'haaq le-aa cvj yuvd tu'q taub sia'q yaag Zwrtq Buaj heug Di-naa.
30.35: tovb uaq Nxi laa-Baan mivb timq mavg ninb Eei yuvb. yuvb kruq pen Eei, maaib tyemq Eei, ninb kinq Zwrtq. yuvb Eeid maaib tyemq Zru tyemq mwrng Zauj taub taub maaib pc'g zxpg Jyenq, Zauj yetg zuvq pa'ki yuvb txn Jia'q ninb yaag kinq Zwrtq. naaiq teij yetg zuvq ninb Jiu pun ninb kanb Eei txn Bua kruj,
30.43: yaa-Kopq kunq zruj kunq putq zxib. maaib yuvb, maaib pa'ki yuvb, maaib nrub kauq nrub peid, maaib lxb Txb, maaib lxb. Euvb Euvg zuvq maaib Zamq.
30.40: yaa-Kopq zx'q yuvb Zauj pa'ki yuvb txn pun Gxi kanb Za'levg an nxm txvj. pa'ki yuvb Zauj yuvb ninb pun huvj mivb laa-Baan Eei pa'ki yuvb Jia'q Zauj pen uaq puv. ninb Navq naaiq nx zruj pun kanb Eei pa'ki yuvb Yaavj. ninb Eei pwrng yuvb Zauj pa'ki yuvb kanb Za'levg an nxm txvj, maiq pun zxpg laa-Baan Eei.
30.14: kaatq Byaub witq Eei zyavb hog, lu-Ben mivb saau uaq Deig, pwatg zuvb Du-Daa-im Jiab. ninb zyrug txb taaib pun ninb Eei maa le-aa. laa-sen kxvq Buaj ninb Eei txg, “Toq pun teij txg Eei txn Eei Du-Daa-im Jiab yia maa'b!”
30.23: ninb zyrug maaib Jyenq sin, yuvd tu'q taub txn. ninb kxvq, “Tinb huvb pun taub txn yia, Tevj yia pwav Myen, maiq zu'g tiaq Eaiq.
30.6: laa-sen kxvq, “Tinb huvb syemq liud tivg pun yia, yaag haid yia Jrub Eei waag zyrug pun taub txn yia.” laa-sen zyrug Tevj uaq taub txn Zwrtq Buaj heug Daan.
30.34: laa-Baan tau, “lovj a'q. Navq meib kxvq nx zruj.”
30.2: yaa-Kopq Qiaj Jiad haig laa-sen. ninb kxvq, “yia maiq zeid Tinb huvb. Tinb huvb kanb pun meib maiq haib maaib kub vwaad.”
30.36: yaag hxvb Jyenq mivb leib yaa-Kopq pua Nxi Eei Jauq. yaa-Kopq c'q, Zxg kruj Jyenq laa-Baan zevg Fiag Eei pa'ki yuvb Zauj yuvb kwanb.
30.20: le-aa kxvq, “Tinb huvb pun lovj haig Eei zivb Eeig yia. ib zang yia Eei Goj Dovg haaij yaag xij Taaib yia weig zu'g yia yuvd tu'q Ju'q taub txn pun ninb.” ninb Zwrtq ninb Eei txn Eei Buaj heug sej-Bu-lun.
30.24: Toq Tinb huvb cvj pun taub txn yia.” ninb zyrug Zwrtq Buaj heug yo-sepq.
30.28: meib Eei kovb zinb xij lovg Bu'ziaj kunq kxvq Buaj yia maa'b! yia zyrug pun.”
30.7: laa-sen Eei nrub peid, Bin-haa, cvj maaib Jyenq sin, yuvd tu'q ta'Eeig taub txn pun yaa-Kopq.
30.29: yaa-Kopq tau ninb Eei ovb taa, “tia hiuq tu'q yia zruj Eei kov Dovg haaij lovj, yaag hiuq tu'q meib Eei scvb Kuq Dovg haaij Zamq.
30.19: le-aa cvj maaib Jyenq sin, yuvd tu'q ta'lua'g taub txn pun yaa-Kopq.
30.17: Tinb huvb tau le-aa Jrub ninb Eei waag. le-aa cvj maaib Jyenq sin, yuvd tu'q ta'Mmd taub txn pun yaa-Kopq.
30.38: ninb zyrug txb naaiq teij zruj pen Eei Dyavb Gwaab an Jyenq scvb Kuq Eei Ra'Myen, uamb zob ka'Euad. scvb Kuq scv Eei zyavb hog taaib hopq uam,
30.31: laa-Baan naaig kaaj ninb, “uaq Euvg, yia xij zu'g pun haiq Euvg meib?” yaa-Kopq tau, “tia maiq zu'g pun haiq Euvg yia. sij kxvq tia xij Navq naaiq nx Tevj yia, yia cvj kruj Jyenq meib Eei pa'ki yuvb Zauj yuvb kwanb mivb.
30.30: yia maiq kcvb taaib Eei zyavb hog, tia maaib teij paaq Navq. ib zang maaib Zamq haig a'q. yia zruj Tauj haaij, zyruq Zeij fu'q pun meib. mq paag Tauj haiq zang yia Zivj lyepg tu'q yia Eei Jaab tivb?”
30.27: mq paag laa-Baan kxvq, “sij kxvq meib pwavq Hruq, Toq cvj Zauj yia yem. yia samj tu'q Zwrtq, hiuq tu'q se weig meib, zyruq Zivj Zeij fu'q pun yia.
30.11: le-aa kxvq, “yia kevb mcvg lovj.” ninb zyrug Tevj uaq taub txn Zwrtq Buaj heug kaatg.
30.5: Bin-haa zyrug maaib Jyenq sin, yuvd tu'q taub txn pun yaa-Kopq.
30.9: le-aa hiuq tu'q ninb kanb maiq yuvd kub vwaad a'q. ninb zyrug pun ninb Eei nrub peid, sinj-paa, yaa-Kopq lovg zruj auq.
30.16: Mwavj teij, yaa-Kopq yem Deig Rwrnj, le-aa mivb zipq. ninb kxvq, “ib mwrnd meib xij zu'g Zauj yia pweij. yia txb yia Eei txn Eei Du-Daa-im Jiab yeng meib mig a'q.” uaq mwrnd yaa-Kopq zyrug Zauj le-aa pweij.
30.41: haiq zang henq Eei uaq teij scvb Kuq taapq zwavq ninb zx'q uaq teij Dyavb Gwaab ton Jyenq Ra'Myen mcvj, uamb zob ka'Euad. ninb Bua yem naaiq teij Dyavj Eei ka'Len taapq zwavq,
30.37: yaa-Kopq mivb Jamq pxpg-laab, an-man Zauj Pa'len Dyavb Gwaab Eyemd taaib Genj Qovj Gc'q Qovj Dyavb Dopq kwavg, pun Dyavb xq Zwrtq taaib pc'g Eei, pen Eei.
30.39: ninb Bua zyrug yem naaiq teij Dyavj Eei Ra'Myen mcvj taapq zwavq. ninb Bua yaag Fiag txn pen Eei, maaib tyemq Zru fai tyemq mwrng Eei.
30.4: laa-sen zyrug pun ninb Eei nrub peid, Bin-haa, ninb Eei Goj lovg zruj auq. yaa-Kopq yaag Zauj ninb pweij.
30.10: sinj-paa yaag yuvd tu'q taub txn pun yaa-Kopq.
30.22: zruj kau, Tinb huvb Javj Tauj laa-sen, cvj tau ninb Jrub Eei waag, pun ninb haib maaib kub vwaad.
30.12: le-aa Eei nrub peid, sinj-paa, cvj yuvd tu'q ta'Eeig taub txn pun yaa-Kopq.
30.42: mq paag maiq henq uaq teij taapq zwavq ninb maiq zx'q naaiq teij Dyavb Gwaab ton Ra'Myen mcvj. Navq naaig, maiq henq uaq teij penj laa-Baan Eei. henq uaq teij penj Revg yaa-Kopq Eei.
30.15: le-aa tau, “yia Eei Goj meib zuvq Rcv mivb a'q. Zxg maiq kcvb kauj? meib cvj xij Rcv yia Eei txn Eei Du-Daa-im Jiab?” laa-sen kxvq, “meib pun teij meib Eei txn Eei Du-Daa-im Jiab yia nx, ib mwrnd yia pun yaa-Kopq Zauj meib pweij.”
30.13: le-aa kxvq, “yia Fyenb yrub haig a'q. zwavj msia'q txn yaag xij kxvq yia Fyenb yrub haig.” ninb zyrug Tevj uaq taub txn Zwrtq Buaj heug aa-se.
30.1: laa-sen hiuq tu'q ninb kanb maiq haib yuvd kub vwaad pun yaa-Kopq, ninb zyrug mweig Jia'q ninb Eei txg. ninb kxvq Buaj yaa-Kopq, “meib pun yia tu'q fu'Jweiq maa'b! maiq zei c'q, yia taig a'q.”
30.26: tia hiuq tu'q yia taaib Tevj meib zruj kov pyetq Dutq yia Eei aub Jweiq mig a'q. Toq pun yia txb Jyenq Rwrnj a'q.”
30.25: laa-sen tu'q liud yo-sepq, Ga'haaq yaa-Kopq kxvq Buaj ninb Eei ovb taa, laa-Baan, “Toq pun yia Rwrnj yia Eei pwrnb teig txvj a'q og.
